\id MAT  
\h Matiu 
\toc1 Matiu 
\toc2 Matiu 
\toc3 Mat 
\mt2 Toto Thovuye Utuniye  
\mt1 Matiu  
\mt2 Le Rorori  
\imt1 Utu iviva  
\ip Matiu iye Jisas gharaghambu regha, na idae regha Livai. Matiu va ghakaiwo i mbana takis weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®, na va e ghakaiwoko ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiye. Matiu va i roriya bukuke iyake thiye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji.  
\ip Matiu le bukuke e t…®ne i woraŇčgiya weinda Jisas iye Ravavaghare, iye val…®kaiwae i vavaghareŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Loi le ghamba mbaro kaiwae. Le vavaghare vavana ra thuweŇčgi VaŇčgothiye 5 gheghad 7, VaŇčgothiye 10, VaŇčgothiye 13, VaŇčgothiye 18 na VaŇčgothiye 24 gheghad 25.  
\ip Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Matiu i vaghareinda Jisas iye Mesaiya iyava e Dagerawe Teuye t…®ne ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va th…®Ňča ne i mena. I woraŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lenji utuutu kaero iye ‚ÄúMesaiya‚ÄĚ iye vaŇča Hibru idaniye, ghathombe e vaŇča Grik iye ‚ÄúKrais.‚ÄĚ ‚ÄúMesaiya‚ÄĚ gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye ‚Äúiye th…® ruvuya bunama e umbaliye.‚ÄĚ The lolo thoŇčgo th…® ruvuya bunama e umbaliye iye tututhi loloniye. Iya kaiwae Matiu i woraŇčgiya weinda Jisas iye Mesaiya. Ko iyemaeŇčge Jiu th…® renuwaŇča th…® munjeva Mesaiya ne i mena na i vamidiya le ghamba mbaro e yambaneke na i varinjoŇčgiya Jiu ghanjith…®gh…®yaŇčgi. Jisas ghe mbaŇča e t…®ne Rom ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® mbaroŇča Jiu ghambanji.  
\ip Jiu mava th…® loŇčweghath…®gha Jisas, va th…® botewoyathu na th…® rokros. Matiu VaŇčgothiye 21 gheghad 27 i woraŇčgiya budakai va i yomara e wik…®ko iyako t…®ne ko amba th…® rokros. VaŇčgothiye 28 i utuŇča Jisas le thuweiru utuniye.  
\ip Matiu le bukuke i govun…®we Jisas i variyeŇčgiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu na veth…® utuŇča utuniye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye.  
\c 1  
\s1 Jisas orumburumbuye  
\r (Luk 3:23-28)  
\p
\v 1 Iyake Jisas Krais orumburumbuye utuutuninji. Jisas Krais iye Deivid rumbuye, Deivid iye Eibraham rumbuye.   
\p
\v 2 Eibraham nariya Aisake, Aisake nariya Jeikob, Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Juda na oghaghae,   
\p
\v 3 Juda le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Peres na Seal, t…®nanjiya Tama, Peres nariya Hes…®ron, Hes…®ron nariya Ram,  
\v 4 Ram nariya Aminadab, Aminadab nariya Nason, Nason nariya Salmon,  
\v 5 Salmon nariya Bowasa, t…®naya Reihab, Bowasa nariya Obedi, t…®naya Rut, Obedi nariya Jese,  
\v 6 Jese nariya KiŇč Deivid. Deivid nariya Solomon, t…®nae iye Uraiya va i vaŇčgukai,  
\v 7 Solomon nariya Rehobowam, Rehobowam nariya Abaija, Abaija nariya Asa,  
\v 8 Asa nariya Jehosapat, Jehosapat nariya Joram, Joram nariya Usaiya,  
\v 9 Usaiya nariya Jotam, Jotam nariya Eihas, Eihas nariya Hejekaiya,  
\v 10 Hejekaiya nariya Manase, Manase nariya Emon, Emon nariya Josaiya,  
\v 11 Josaiya le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Jekonaiya na oghaghae, mbaŇčaniye Babilon va th…® mena th…® kivwalaŇčgiya Isirel na th…® vaŇčguŇčgi vethiya yaku Babilon.   
\p
\v 12 Va th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Isirel na veth…® vaŇčguraweŇčgi Babilon na e ghereiye: Jekonaiya nariya Seyatiyel, Seyatiyel nariya Serubabol,  
\v 13 Serubabol nariya Abiyuda, Abiyuda nariya Ilaiyakim, Ilaiyakim nariya Eiso,  
\v 14 Eiso nariya Sedok, Sedok nariya Akim, Akim nariya Eliud…®,  
\v 15 Eliud…® nariya Eliyesa, Eliyesa nariya Meitan, Meitan nariya Jeikob,  
\v 16 na Jeikob nariya Josep Meri le gh…®moru, iyava i ghamba Jisas, iya raŇčake Mesaiya.   
\p
\v 17 I mena weya Eibraham ghaghad Deivid tha theyaworo na theghevar…®, Deivid na ghaghad va th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Isirel na th…® raka Babilon, tha theyaworo na theghevar…® na va e mbaŇčako iyako na gheghad Mesaiya i vir…® tha theyaworo na theghevar…®.   
\s1 Jisas le vir…® utuutuniye  
\r (Luk 2:1-7)  
\p
\v 18 Jisas Krais le vir…® va Ňčgora iyake. T…®nae Meri ghaghaivaun weiye Josep, ko ma vamba th…® ghe kaero i marabo Nyao Boboma le vur…®gheghe kaiwae.  
\v 19 Kaiwae Josep, Meri ghaghaivaun, iye ghathanavu va i thovuye, mava nuwaiya i vakatha na i monjina. Josep le renuwaŇča thuwele nuwaiya th…® yawo weiye.   
\p
\v 20 Ko le renuwaŇča thuweleko iyako e ghereiye Giya Loi le nyao thovuye i njawe ghenelolo e t…®ne na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúJosep, Deivid rumbuye, tha u mararu na u vaŇčgwa Meri na len wevo, maraboke iyake i mena weya Nyao Boboma.  
\v 21 Ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru na ne u uno idae Jisas, kaiwae ne i vamoruŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Thiyake th…® yomara na th…® vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Giya Loi va i utugiya weya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu,  
\v 23 ‚ÄúTh…®nabwethubwethuru nevole i marabo na i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru na nevole th…® rena idae Imanuwel.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Ais 7:14; 8:8,10\x* Imanuwel gharumwaru ‚ÄúLoi iye weinda‚ÄĚ.   
\p
\v 24 MbaŇča Josep i thuweiru, i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Giya Loi le nyao thovuye me dagemawe i vaŇčgwa Meri na levo.  
\v 25 Ko ma vamba i ndeloŇčga mun weiye Meri gheghada i ghamba Ňčgamako na Josep i rena idae Jisas.   
\c 2  
\s1 Rathimbathimba th…® mena e boimako  
\p
\v 1 Jisas va i vir…® Bet…®lehem Judiya e t…®ne, Herod ghambaŇča i mbaro. Jisas le vir…® e ghereiye rathimbathimba gh…®mogh…®moru e boimako th…® mena Jerusalem  
\v 2 na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAŇčga inae Jiu lenji kiŇč amba menda i vir…®ke? Mendava wo vaidiya ghagh…®tara e boimako na nuwameiya wo mena wo kururuwe.‚ÄĚ\fig Rathimbathimba thegheto na lenji kamel|alt="3 wisemen and camel following star" src="CN01628b.tif" size="span" copy="Cook" ref="2:1-2" \fig*   
\p
\v 3 MbaŇča KiŇč Herod i loŇčweya utuke iyake i vakatha ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye, na Jerusalem gharayakuyakuko wolagh…®ye.  
\v 4 Herod i kula vathavathaŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare, na i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMesaiya, aŇčga mbala i vir…®?‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBet…®lehem, Judiya e t…®ne, iyake kaiwae Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va i rori:  
\v 6 ‚ÄėKo ghen, Bet…®lehem, Judiya e thivathivaniye t…®ne, u lagh…®ye moli, kaiwae e ghen randeviva ne i yomara, na ne i ndeviva weŇčgiya lo ghar…®ghar…® Isirel.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Mai 5:2; 2Samu 5:2\x*   
\p
\v 7 Amba Herod i kula thuweleŇčgiya rathimbathimbama na th…® niva weinji na i vaitoŇčgi va thembaŇča vara gh…®tarako i yomara.  
\v 8 I variyeŇčgi Bet…®lehem na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa na vou tamwe wagiyawe Ňčgamana. ThembaŇča vou vaidi, hu mena hu giya yanawaŇčgu na ghino tembe ya wa na va kururuweva.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 MbaŇča th…® iteta Herod ma veth…® loŇčgaloŇčga na mbowo th…® vaidiva gh…®tarama mendava th…® vaidima e boimako, i viva e ghamwanji gheghad i mena i ndeghath…® Ňčgora Ňčgamama inawe e vwatae.  
\v 10 MbaŇča th…® thuweya gh…®tarako th…® warari lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 11 Th…® ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne na th…® vaidiya Ňčgamama weiye t…®nae Meri. Th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye na th…® kururuwe. Th…® tateŇčgiya lenji vethe nasiye na th…® bigiraŇčgiya lenji mwaewo, gol, preŇčkinisen…®s na mer.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft PreŇčkinisen…®s na mer umbwaumbwa thinji butinji thovuye na modanji lagh…®ye moli.\f*  
\v 12 Vanuwov…®r…® i mena weŇčgi ghenelolo e t…®ne, na thava te th…® njogha weva Herod. Vama th…® reŇčava e kamwath…® regha na th…® njogha e ghambanji.   
\s1 Th…® vo na th…® wa Ijipt  
\p
\v 13 MbaŇča vama rathimbathimbama th…® wareri amba Giya Loi le nyao thovuye i yomara weya Josep ghenelolo e t…®ne na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondo, Josep, u vaŇčguŇčgiya Ňčgamana na t…®nae na hu vowa Ijipt. Vou yaku gheko gheghad ne ya dage weŇčga amba hu njoghama, kaiwae Herod le ragagaith…® ne th…® tamweya Ňčgamana na nuwanjiya th…® un…®gh…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Josep i thuweiru i vaŇčguŇčgiya Ňčgamama na t…®nae gougouko iyako na th…® wa Ijipt.  
\v 15 Veth…® yaku ghaghad Herod i mare. Iyako i yomara na i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Giya Loi va i utugiya weya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu iŇča, ‚ÄúIjipt e t…®ne ya kularaŇčgiya naruŇčgu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Hos 11:1\x*   
\s1 Herod i gaboŇčgiya gamagai  
\p
\v 16 MbaŇča Herod i ghareghare rathimbathimbama th…® yaro, ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye moli. Amba i variyeŇčgiya le ragagaith…® na th…® gaboŇčgiya gamagai gh…®mogh…®moru Bet…®lehem na ele val…®vaŇčgako wolagh…®ye, thiye ghanjitheghathegha umboiwo na e raberabe. Va i vakatha Ňčgorako kaiwae va i gorugoru weya ŇčgoroŇčga rathimbathimbama lenji woraŇčgiya na gh…®tarama le yomara.  
\v 17 Va Ňčgorako na Jeremaiya le utu i tabo na emunjoru.  
\v 18 IŇča:  
\p ‚ÄúTh…® loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňča regha Ramae ele val…®vaŇčga, raŇčivetho weiye nuwathar…®. Reitiyel i raŇčiŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga, ma nuwaiya th…® vawarariŇča kaiwae kaero th…® mare.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:18 \xt Jer 31:15\x*   
\s1 Njoghamake Ijipt  
\p
\v 19 Herod va le mare e ghereiye, Giya Loi le nyao thovuye i yomarawe Josep e ghenelolo, Ijipt e t…®ne,  
\v 20 na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondo u vaŇčguŇčgiya Ňčgamana na t…®nae na hu wa Isirel e thivathivaniye kaiwae thiyema va th…® mando na th…® munjeva th…® un…®gha Ňčgamana kaero th…® mare.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Josep i thuweiru i vaŇčguŇčgiya Ňčgamama na t…®nae na th…® wa Isirel e thivathivaniye.  
\v 22 Ko mbaŇča Josep i loŇčweya Akiulas i meth…®gha ramae Herod Judiya e t…®ne, i mararu na i wa gheko. Loi i dagewe e ghenelolo na th…® wa Galili ele val…®vaŇčga,  
\v 23 na th…® wa na veth…® yaku e ghemba regha idae Nasaret. Iyake i vaemunjoruŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi va th…® utuŇča: ‚ÄúNe th…®Ňča rara Nasaret.‚ÄĚ   
\c 3  
\s1 Jon Rabap…®taiso le vavaghare  
\r (Mak 1:1-8; Luk 3:1-18; Jon 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 Va e mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako Jon Rabap…®taiso i mena Judiya e njamnjam…®niye na i vavagharewe  
\v 2 iŇča, ‚ÄúHu uturaŇčgiya lemi thar…® na hu roiteteŇčgi, kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro ghambaŇča maiyavara.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Jon iya utuniya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Aiseya va i utuŇčama, iyava iŇčake,  
\q1 ‚ÄúLolo regha i kulakula e njamnjam,  
\q1 ‚ÄėHu vivatha kamwath…® Giya kaiwae;  
\q1 hu varumwaru kamwath…® amalagh…®niye kaiwae na mbala i reŇčawe!‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 3:3 \xt Ais 40:3\x*   
\p
\v 4 Jon ghakwama va th…® vakatha kamel vulivuliye. Mborowae gheva thetheghan njimwae na i ghan…®Ňčgiya bibita na Ňčguyo.  
\v 5 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® rakamenawe, vavana th…® rakamena Jerusalem, vavana Judiya ele val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye na vavana th…® rakamena e vanautumako lagh…®ye e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan ghadidiye.  
\v 6 Th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na Jon i bap…®taisoŇčgi Jor…®dan.   
\p
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča i thuweŇčgiya Parisi na Sadusi th…® rakamenawe bap…®taiso kaiwae, i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi mwata raraithar…® ghemi! Thela i dage e ghemi na hu munjeva ne hu voiteta Loi le ghatemuruko vuyowae iya i menamenako?  
\v 8 Hu vaemunjoruŇča e lemi vakathana kaero hu uturaŇčgiya lemi thar…® na hu roiteteŇčgi.  
\v 9 Na thava lemi renuwaŇča hu munjeva ne hu voiteta vuyowoko iyako kaiwae huŇča, ‚ÄėGhime rumbuma Eibraham.‚Äô Ya dage e ghemi, Loi val…®kaiwae i mban…®Ňčgiya var…®var…®ke thiyake na i vakathaŇčgiya Eibraham orumburumbuye.  
\v 10 E mbaŇčake iyake kelumo kaero ina vara e umbwaumbwa r…®gher…®ghenji. Umbwa regha na regha ma i rau na thovuye ne i ikuyathu na i bigiyathu e nd…®ghe une.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúGhino ya bap…®taisoŇčga e mbwa na i vatomwe kaero hu uturaŇčgiya lemi thar…® na hu roiteteŇčgi, ko iya loloko i rereghamba e ghereiŇčguke, iye ne i bap…®taisoŇčga e Nyao Boboma na e nd…®ghe une. Ma elo thovuye na val…®kaiwaŇčgu ne ya bigiya gheghe ghae.  
\v 12 Le sav…®r…® wit kaiwae kaero ina e n…®mae, ne i ghatha mbombouyeko weiye wokiwokiniyeko. Ne i mbana mbombouyeko na i vathe e ghaŇčgolo na wokiwokiniyeko i Ňčambu e nd…®gheko iya ma mbaŇča regha ne i mareko.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jon i bap…®taiso Jisas  
\r (Mak 1:9-11; Luk 3:21-22)  
\p
\v 13 E mbaŇčako iyako e t…®ne Jisas i ri Galili na i wa Jor…®dan, na i bap…®taiso weya Jon.  
\v 14 Jon i munjeva ne i v…®va Jisas le renuwaŇča, i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen eŇčge mbala u bap…®taisoŇčgo, na ghen mo menava e ghino?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Ko Jisas i gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowo Ňčgoreiyako e mbaŇčake iyake, kaiwae e kamwath…®ke iyake ne ra vakatha Loi le renuwaŇča thovuye.‚ÄĚ Jon i wovathovuthovuyeŇča.  
\v 16 MbaŇča i bap…®taisovao na i voro e mbwako ghadidiye, e mbaŇčako iyako buruburu i mavu na i thuweya Nyao Boboma i njamawe Ňčgoreiya bunebune.  
\v 17 Amba ghal…®ghal…®Ňča i mena e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúLoloke iyake naruŇčgu moli gharegharethovuniye. I vakathaŇčgo ya warari lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ\fig Jisas le bap…®taiso walagh…®ta Jor…®dan|alt="Jesus baptized in the Jordan" src="Mk9.1.tif" size="span" copy="UBS (GNR)" ref="3:13-17" \fig*   
\c 4  
\s1 Seitan i vatanathethaŇča Jisas  
\r (Mak 1:12-13; Luk 4:1-13)  
\p
\v 1 Amba Nyao Boboma i yo vaŇčgwa Jisas e njamnjam vur…®vur…® vwatavwata na Seitan ve vatanathethaŇča.  
\v 2 Na kaiwae vama gheneyevar…® ve yaku e njamnjam na ve mbeya ghan…®Ňčga naŇčgo kaiwae, ko e mbaŇčako iyako amba bada i ghar…®.  
\v 3 Amba ratanathethama i menawe na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo Loi Nariya ghen, u ŇčaerambeŇčgiya var…®var…®ke thiyake th…® gharav…® na bred.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúBuk Boboma iŇča, ‚ÄėMa mbene bred eŇčge i ndewo lolo yawaliye, ko iyemaeŇčge budakaiya Loi i utuŇča iye i ndewo lolo yawaliye.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Mba 8:3\x*   
\p
\v 5 Amba Seitan i yovaŇčgu Jerusalem, i vaŇčgurawe vara e Ňägolo Boboma vwatae yavoro moli,  
\v 6 na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo Loi Nariya ghen, u pito ghena, kaiwae Buk Boboma iŇča,  
\p ‚Äú‚ÄėLoi ne i variyeŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye kaiwan, na th…® njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčge, ne th…® mwanavair…®Ňčge e n…®manji, mbala ma vo Ňčge gheghen e var…®.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Sam 91:11-12\x*   
\p
\v 7 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúBuk Boboma tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄėTha lolo regha i mando na i woraweya Giya le Loi mando e t…®ne.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Mba 6:16\x*   
\p
\v 8 Seitan mbowo i yovaŇčguva na ve vaŇčgurawe e ou vwatae yavoro moli, na i vatomwe weya ghamba mbaroke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke, lenji lagh…®lagh…®ye na lenji thovuye.  
\v 9 I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúIya vara ghamba mbaroko wolagh…®ye thiyako ne ya vatomwe e ghen thoŇčgo u ronja na u kururu e ghino.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Amba Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa Seitan! Buk Boboma iŇča, ‚ÄėU kururu weya Giya len Loi ghamberegha na ghamberegha moli u ghambu!‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:10 \xt Mba 6:13\x*   
\p
\v 11 Amba Seitan i itete na nyao thovuthovuye th…® mena th…® giya thalavuwe.   
\s1 Jisas i woraweya le kaiwo r…®ghe Galili  
\r (Luk 4:14-15)  
\p
\v 12 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčwe Jon utuniye kaero ina e thiyo, i njogha Galili,  
\v 13 na i iteta Nasaret i wa ve yaku Kapenaom. Ghembake iyake ina Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye, uu Sebulon na Nap…®talai e lenji val…®vaŇčga.  
\v 14 Va i vakatha Ňčgoraiyako na i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Aiseya, ghal…®Ňčae iya iŇčake,   
\q1
\v 15 ‚ÄúUu Sebulon na Nap…®talai e lenji val…®vaŇčga t…®ne, val…®vaŇčgako iya kamwath…®ko i wa e njigh…®ko, e val…®vaŇčga Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan i vorovoro e t…®ne, na Galili e t…®ne, thiye ma Jiu thiya yakuwe:   
\q1
\v 16 ghar…®ghar…®ko iya thiya yaku e momouwoko va th…® thuweya manjamanjala lagh…®ye,  
\q1 thiye thiya yaku mare e momouwowae t…®ne manjamanjala ne i woya weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:16 \xt Ais 9:1,2\x*   
\p
\v 17 MbaŇčaniye Jisas i woraweya le vavaghare r…®ghe, i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu uturaŇčgiya lemi thar…® na hu roitete, kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro maiyavara!‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i kula weŇčgiya raboroborogi theghevar…®  
\r (Mak 1:16-20; Luk 5:1-11)  
\p
\v 18 MbaŇča Jisas i Ňčgalai Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye, i vaidiŇčgiya raiwo na ghaghae, Saimon idae regha Pita na ghaghae Endru, th…® duda ghina kaiwae thiye raboroborogi.  
\v 19 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu mena hu ghambuŇčgo na ya vavaghareŇčga ghemi ghar…®ghar…® ghanjirakosi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 E mbaŇčako iyako th…® iteteŇčgiya lenji ghina na th…® ghambu.\fig Jisas i kula weŇčgiya Jemes na Jon na th…® ghambu|alt="Jesus calls James and John" src="CN01682B.TIF" size="span" copy="Cook" ref="4:21-22" \fig*   
\p
\v 21 I loŇčga ghaova seiwo, mbowo i vaidiŇčgiva raiwo na ghaghae, Jemes Sebedi nariye na ghaghae Jon, inanji e waŇčga weinji ramanji Sebedi, th…® vavanamweŇčgiya lenji ghina. Jisas i kula weŇčgi,  
\v 22 na e mbaŇčako iyako th…® iteta waŇčga na ramanji Sebedi, na th…® ghambu.   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghareŇča Toto Thovuye na  //  i thawariŇčgiya ghambweghambwera  
\r (Luk 6:17-19)  
\p
\v 23 Jisas i vagh…®liya Galili lagh…®yeko, i vavaghare e Ňčgolo kururu t…®nenji, i utuŇča Toto Thovuye Loi le ghamba mbaro utuniye na i thawariŇčgiya tomethi gida na ghambwera weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.  
\v 24 Toto amalagh…®niye utuutuniye i lalo Siriya lagh…®yeko na ghar…®ghar…® th…® bigimena weya Jisas ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye tomethi ghanjighambwera, thiye th…® ghataŇča v…®r…® lagh…®ye, thavala nyao raraithar…® ina weŇčgi, thavala th…® vaidiya vuyowo Ňčgoreiya riwanji i gheroro na kuvokuvoŇčgi, na i thawariŇčgi.  
\v 25 Iya kaiwae wabwi lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® rakambele. Vavana th…® rakamena Galili na e Ghembaghemba Ghembayaworo\f + \fr 4:25 \ft ‚ÄúGhembaghemba Ghembayaworo‚ÄĚ iye idanji regha th…® uno ghembaghemba ghembayaworo inanji Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro na th…® wabwi na regha. Thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lemoyo th…® yaku e ghembaghembako thiyako.\f*, vavana Jerusalem, vavana Judiya na vavana th…® rakamena Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro.   
\c 5  
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare e bobokulu vwatae  
\r (Luk 6:20-23)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas va i thuweŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye amba i voro e bobokulu regha, na mbaŇča i ronja gharaghambu th…® rakamenawe na th…® megh…®liŇča.  
\v 2 Amba i vavaghare weŇčgiya wabwiko lagh…®ye, iŇča:   
\s1 Thavala Loi ghare weŇčgi  
\q1
\v 3 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala mbinyembinyeŇčgu e unenji t…®ne, kaiwae le ghamba mbaro kaero ina weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 4 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala th…® numothar…®, kaiwae ne i gogonja nuwanji.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 5 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala th…® gharenja, kaiwae ne i wogiya yambaneke lagh…®ye weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 6 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala e yawalinjiko th…® badaŇča lagh…®ye na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya Loi le renuwaŇča, kaiwae Loi ne i vatabo na i vamboromboro lagh…®ye moli weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 7 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala th…® gharev…®r…® ghar…®ghar…® vavana kaiwanji, kaiwae ne i gharev…®r…® weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 8 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala gharenjiko lagh…®ye i th…®na, kaiwae ne th…® thuweya Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 9 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala th…® vevakathaŇča gharemal…®l…® weŇčgi, kaiwae ne iŇča thiye le ŇčgaŇčga.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 10 ‚ÄúLoi ghare weŇčgiya thavala th…® vaidiya vuyowo weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® kaiwae ghanjithanavu i rumwaru, kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro kaero ina weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúGhareŇčgu weŇčga ghemi mbaŇča ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® goviya ghamwami, mbaŇča th…® vakatha vuyowo weŇčga, na mbaŇča th…® utu kwan…®kwan kaiwami kaiwae hu ghambuŇčgo.  
\v 12 Mbe hu warari na nuwami i loghe kaiwae modami lagh…®ye mbe ina e buruburu. Kaiwae ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu gharautuŇčgi me vivako vambe th…® vakathava vuyowo ŇčgoranjiŇčgiya thiyako weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ghemi Ňčgoramiya njigh…® na manjamanjala  
\r (Mak 9:50; Luk 14:34-35)  
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúGhemi ghamithanavu e yambaneke Ňčgoreiya njigh…® le kaiwo. Iya kaiwae thoŇčgo njigh…® le vur…®gheghe iko na ma ma e gham…®gham…®nae, ma te kamwath…® reghava na val…®kaiwae ra vakatha na gham…®naeko i njogha. Kaero i thar…® na ma ma e ghathovuye, ra wokiyathu ghar…®ghar…® th…® vur…®gh…®ya.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúGhemi yambaneke ghamanjamanjala. ThoŇčgo th…® vakatha ghemba regha e ou vwatae ghar…®ghar…®ke taulagh…® ne th…® thuwe.  
\v 15 Ma mbaŇča regha lolo i r…®mba lemp na i wo uye na i woyabowe, ko ne i th…®n…®rawe e tebol vwatae na i vamanjamanjalaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e Ňčgoloko t…®ne.  
\v 16 Ghemi tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, lemi manjamanjalana i woya weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® mbala th…® thuweya lemi vakatha na thovuye na th…® taraweŇča Ramami iye ina e buruburu.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i mena na i vaemunjoruŇča Mosese le mbaro  
\p
\v 17 ‚ÄúThava lemi renuwaŇča huŇčava ya mena na ya rakayathu Mosese le mbaro na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lenji vavaghare. Ma ya mena rakayathu kaiwae, ya mena na ya vaemunjoruŇčaŇčgi.  
\v 18 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, gheghada buruburu na yambaneke ne th…®ko, mane utu nasiye regha ina e Mbaroko t…®ne ne iko gheghada wolagh…®yeko th…® tabo na emunjoru.  
\v 19 ThoŇčgo lolo regha i raka mbaroŇčgike thiyake na iŇča ma e ghanjithovuye, othembe mbaro nasiye regha ina e mbaroŇčgike t…®nenji, na i vaghareŇčgiya ghaune vavana na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye, iye ne i roreghamba moli Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne. Ko thela i ghambugha mbaro na i vaghareŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye, iye ne i roviva Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 20 Iya kaiwae, ya dage e ghemi, ghamithanavuna iya hu ghambugha Loi le mbarona thoŇčgo ma i kivwalaŇčgiya Mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi, ma val…®kaiwami ne hu ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare gaith…® kaiwae  
\r (Luk 12:57-59)  
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare Mosese le mbaro va i mena weŇčgiya orumburumbumi, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėTha u gabo. Thela i gabo ne i vaidiya vuyowae.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:21 \xt RaŇč 20:13; Mba 5:17\x*  
\v 22 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, thela ghare i gaith…®wana ghaghae ne i vaidiya vuyowae, thela i utuvathar…® ghaghae kaiwae ne ve kot Jiu e lenji mbaro lagh…®ye na thela ne iŇča, ‚ÄėKabaleya ghen!‚Äô val…®kaiwae ne vo nda e nd…®ghe Gehena.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae thoŇčgo u womena len mwaewo e Ňčgolo boboma t…®ne vowo kaiwae weya Loi, na amba u renuwaŇča vaidiya ghagha ghare va i gaith…® wanaŇčge bigi regha kaiwae,  
\v 24 u iteta len mwaewona e ghamba vowona ghadidiye na wo u njogha na vou vakatha na namoghamwami wein, amba u njogha na vo giya len mwaewona weya Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo regha i wonjoweŇčge bigi regha kaiwae na i yovaŇčguŇčge na vo kot, u yoruku na u vanamwe wonjoweko iyako wein amba muyai vou vutha e ghamba kot. ThoŇčgo nandere, ne i yovaŇčguŇčge na ve vaŇčguraweŇčge kot gharavakatha e marae na iye i vaŇčgugiyaŇčge weya thiyo gharanjimbunjimbu na ve vaŇčguruwoŇčge e thiyo.  
\v 26 Ya dage emunjoru e ghen, mane u raŇčgi ghaghada ne u vamodovao ghan…®ghagako iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare yathima kaiwae  
\p
\v 27 ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare Mosese le mbaro iŇča Ňčgoraiyake, ‚ÄėTha u yathima wein lolo regha levo.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:27 \xt RaŇč 20:14; Mba 5:18\x*  
\v 28 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, thoŇčgo thela i thuweya wevo regha na nuwaeko nuwaiya moli, iyako Ňčgoreiya kaero i yathima weiye ele renuwaŇčako t…®ne.  
\v 29 ThoŇčgo maran…®na iya e unena i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…® u vovavuthuyathu. I thovuye eŇčge u wokiyathu riwana Ňčginauye regha na thava ne th…® wokiyathu riwana lagh…®ye Gehena.  
\v 30 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, thoŇčgo n…®man…®na iya unena i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u kiten…®yathu. I thovuye moliya u kiten…®yathu riwana Ňčginauye regha na thava ne th…® wokiyathu riwana lagh…®ye Gehena.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare yawo kaiwae  
\r (Mat 19:9; Mak 10:1-12; Luk 16:18)  
\p
\v 31 ‚ÄúMosese le mbaro iŇča, ‚ÄėThela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i botewo levo, wo i rorinjoŇča le botewoko utuutuniye e peipa na i ligiya weya wevoko.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:31 \xt Mba 24:1\x*  
\v 32 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, thoŇčgo lolo regha i yawo weiye levo, othembe wevoko ma i yathima, thoŇčgo wevo i gheva, loloko le thar…® kaiwae wevoko i tabo na rayathiyathima. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, the loloko iya i vaŇčguko wevoko iye tembe i yathimava.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare tholo kaiwae  
\p
\v 33 ‚ÄúTembe hu ghareghareva Mosese le mbaro va th…® utugiya weŇčgiya orumburumbumi, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėTha u raka len tholona. U vakatha Ňčgoreiya len dagerawe weya Loi.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:33 \xt Legha 30:2; Liv 19:13\x*  
\v 34 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, tha mbaŇča regha u tholo na u uno buruburu idae kaiwae Loi le ghamba yaku iyako.  
\v 35 Thava u uno yambaneke, kaiwae gheghe ghaghambalirawe iyako. Thava u uno Jerusalem, kaiwae KiŇč lagh…®ye le ghamba yaku iyako,  
\v 36 na thava u tholo e umbal…®na, kaiwae ma val…®kaiwan ne uŇča na umbal…®na ndamwandamwa yaŇčgara i kaleva na uŇčana yaŇčgara i bwedi.  
\v 37 Ma huŇčaeŇčge, ‚ÄėŇägoreiye‚Äô o ‚ÄėNandere.‚Äô ThoŇčgo hu guva utu regha iyana i mena weya Seitan.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas iŇča tha u lith…®gha thar…®  
\r (Luk 6:29-30)  
\p
\v 38 ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare Mosese le mbaro iŇča Ňčgoreiyake, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo lolo regha i vakowana gheu regha marae vogh…®ra, modae tembe th…® vakowanava amalagh…®niye marae vogh…®ra. ThoŇčgo i tagabeba gheuko ŇčiŇčiye regha modae tembe th…® tagabebeva ŇčiŇčiye regha.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:38 \xt RaŇč 21:24; Liv 24:20; Mba 19:21\x*  
\v 39 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, thoŇčgo lolo regha i vakatha vathar…® e ghen, thava u lith…®. ThoŇčgo lolo regha i tagaleva galagalan…®na iya e unena, u vatomwe weya val…®galagalan…®na tembe i tagalevava.  
\v 40 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, thoŇčgo lolo regha i vaŇčguraweŇčge e kot na i munjeva i vakathaŇčge na u ligiya weya ghan…®kwamana iya riwana ghayaboyabo, tembe u ligiyaweva ghan…®kwamana ghayaboyabo.  
\v 41 ThoŇčgo ragagaith…® regha i vavur…®ghegheŇčaŇčge na u bigiya ghabigi le bwagabwaga Ňčgoreiye mael regha, u bigi na ma u waova na vewo mael theghewo.  
\v 42 U wogiya weya lolo regha thebigiya nuwaiya e ghen, na thoŇčgo lolo regha i naŇčgoya bigi regha e ghen na i vakaiwoŇča thava u vagharegharewe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Hu gharethovu weŇčgiya ghamith…®gh…®ya  
\r (Luk 6:27-28,32-36)  
\p
\v 43 ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare Mosese le mbaro iŇča Ňčgoreiyake, ‚ÄėU gharethovu weŇčgiya ghanune, u botewo moliŇčgiya ghan…®th…®gh…®ya.‚Äô\x - \xo 5:43 \xt Liv 19:18\x*  
\v 44 Ko ghino ya dage e ghemi, hu gharethovu weŇčgiya ghamith…®gh…®ya na thavala th…® vakatha vuyowo weŇčga hu naŇčgo kaiwanji,  
\v 45 mbala ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghareghare ghemi Loi ina e buruburu le ŇčgamaŇčgama ghemi. Kaiwae i vakatha varae na i mb…®le weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye na ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…®, na i vakatha uye i nja weŇčgiya thavala ghanjithanavu i rumwaru na thavala ghanjithanavu i thar…®.  
\v 46 Buda kaiwae Loi ne i giya modami thoŇčgo mbe hu gharethovu weŇčgi eŇčge thavala th…® gharethovu weŇčga? Takis gharamban tembe th…® vakathava Ňčgoreiyako othembe thiye ma ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuyaŇčgi.  
\v 47 ThoŇčgo mbe hu gharethovu weŇčgi eŇčge lemi bodaboda, lemi vakathana ma i kivwala ghar…®ghar…®ke taulagh…® lenji vakatha. Thavala ma th…® loŇčweghath…® tembe th…® vakavakathava iyako.  
\v 48 Ghemi ghamithanavuna wolagh…®ye i thovuye Ňčgoreiya Ramami e buruburu ghathanavu i thovuye moli.‚ÄĚ   
\c 6  
\s1 Thalavu i wa weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu  
\p
\v 1 ‚ÄúTha mbaŇča regha hu vakatha vakatha thovuye regha ghar…®ghar…® e maranji na huŇčava mbala th…® thuweya lemi vakathana. ThoŇčgo hu vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, mane hu vaidi modami thovuye weya Ramami e buruburu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 2 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae, mbaŇča ne u giya bigi regha weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu, tha u ghavwareyathu Ňčgoreiye rakwan lenji vakatha e Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne na e kamwath…®Ňčgiko kaiwae nuwanjiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® taraweŇčgi. Ya dage emunjoru e ghen, kaero th…® mban…®vao modanji.  
\v 3 Ko mbaŇča ne u giya bigi regha weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu, thava n…®man…®na iya moina i ghareghareya n…®man…®na iya unena le vakatha,  
\v 4 mbala ma lolo regha i ghareghare mo wogiya budakai. Rama e buruburu iye i thuweya iya len vakatha thuwelena, na iye ne i giya modan.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vavaghare naŇčgo kaiwae  
\r (Luk 11:2-4)  
\p
\v 5 ‚ÄúMbaŇča hu naŇčgo thava Ňčgoreiya rakwan lenji vakatha. Thiye nuwanjiya th…® ndeghath…® na th…® naŇčgo e Ňčgolo kururu na e kamwath…® ghavwaghavwalaŇčgi, kaiwae nuwanjiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuweŇčgi. Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, kaero th…® mban…®vao modanji.  
\v 6 Ko mbaŇča u naŇčgo, u ru e woluwolu t…®ne, u kiya th…®n…®mba na u naŇčgo weya Rama, iye ma ra thuwe. Rama e buruburu iye i thuwevao thebigiya u vakatha thuwelena ne i giya modan.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu naŇčgo, tha mbema hu vara dagedage eŇčge na hu gov…®gova dage ma e ghanjirumwaru Ňčgoreiya thavala ma th…® loŇčweghath…®gha Loi lenji vakatha. Thiye th…® munjeva Loi ne i loŇčweya lenji naŇčgoko na i vakatha Ňčgoreiye kaiwae lenji naŇčgoko i molao.  
\v 8 Tha hu vakatha Ňčgoraiyako, kaiwae thebigiya nuwamiya Ramami Loi kaero i ghareghare amba muyai hu naŇčgowe.  
\v 9 Mbala hu naŇčgo na Ňčgora iyake:  
\q1 ‚ÄėRamame e buruburu, wo yavwatatawana idan boboma,   
\q1
\v 10 len ghamba mbarona i mena weime, len renuwaŇčana wo vakatha e yambaneke Ňčgoreiya th…® vakavakatha e buruburu.   
\q1
\v 11 U giya weime noroke ghan…®Ňčganiye.   
\q1
\v 12 U numoten…®Ňčgiya lama thar…®, Ňčgoreiya ghime kaero wo numoyathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® weime.   
\q1
\v 13 Tha u vakathaime na wo ru tanathetha e t…®ne, ko u vamoruime eŇčge thar…® e t…®ne.  
\q1 Kaiwae ghen rambarombaro, ghen u vur…®gheghe na ghen giya lagh…®ye, mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako. Mbwana! Ňägoreiye!‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúKaiwae thoŇčgo hu numoyathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® weŇčga, ambane Ramami e buruburu i numoten…®Ňčgiya lemi thar…®.  
\v 15 Ko thoŇčgo ma hu numoyathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®, Ramami tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mane i numoten…®Ňčgiya lemi thar…®.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ra mbeya ghan…®Ňčga naŇčgo kaiwae utuniye  
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu mbeya ghan…®Ňčga naŇčgo kaiwae, tha ghamiyamoyamo i nuwanuwathar…®, Ňčgoreiya rakwan lenji vakatha. Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, kaero th…® mban…®vao modanji.  
\v 17 MbaŇča ne u mbeya ghan…®Ňčga naŇčgo kaiwae, u thavwiya ghamwan na u woraweya bunama e umbal…®n,  
\v 18 mbala ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® ghareghare u mbeya ghan…®Ňčga, ko mbe Rama eŇčge e buruburu ghamberegha, iye i rothuwele, iye i thuwevao bigi regha na regha u vakatha thuwele, ne i giya modan.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ra mban…®vatha gogomwau e buruburu  
\r (Luk 12:32-34)  
\p
\v 19 ‚ÄúTha hu mban…®vathavatha bigibigi kaiwami e yambaneke, thaŇčge ne i th…®n…®ten na i vwatha, na rakaiv…® ne th…® ru na th…® kaiv…®.  
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge hu mban…®vathavatha gogomwau kaiwami e buruburu, kaiwae thaŇčge mane i th…®n…®ten na i vwatha, na rakaiv…® mane th…® ru na th…® kaiv…®.  
\v 21 Kaiwae the bigithan i lagh…®ye e ghen, gharena tembe inaweva.   
\s1 Marandake Ňčgora riwandake ghamanjamanjala  
\r (Luk 11:33-36)  
\p
\v 22 ‚ÄúMarandake Ňčgora manjamanjala riwandake kaiwae. ThoŇčgo maramaramina th…® thovuye riwamina lagh…®ye tembe Ňčgoreiyeva manjamanjala i riyevanjara.  
\v 23 Ko thoŇčgo th…® thar…®, riwamina tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, momouwo i riyevanjara. ThoŇčgo manjamanjalana e gharemina i momouwo, o ma momouwo, i lagh…®ye yo!‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Giyagiya theghewo na Loi na bigibigi  
\r (Luk 16:13; 12:22-31)  
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae lolo regha ne i tabo na rakakaiwo weŇčgiya giyagiya theghewo. ThoŇčgo val…®kaiwae, ne i gharethovu weya regha na i botewoyathu reghava, o i botewoyathu regha na i gharethovu reghava. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ma mbaŇčara vara u kaiwo weŇčgiya Loi na mani.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae ya dage e ghemi, tha hu rerenuwaŇča budakai ne hu ghan o hu mun na i tubwe yawalimi. Tha hu rerenuwaŇča kwama kaiwae ne hu njimbo na i vakatha riwamina i dayagha. Yawal…® gharerenuwaŇča i lagh…®ye kivwala ghan…®Ňčga na riwandake gharerenuwaŇča i lagh…®ye kivwala kwama, Ňčgoreiye ae?  
\v 26 Wo hu rerenuwaŇča ma kaiwanji. Ma th…® kaiwo, ma th…® uloulo na ma th…® vathe; ko iyemaeŇčge Loi Rama e buruburu i njimbukikiŇčgi. Ghemi hu lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya ma ae?  
\v 27 Ghemi ma regha val…®kaiwae ne i rerenuwaŇča na seiwova i vakatha yawaliyeko na molao.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúNa buda kaiwae hu rerenuwaŇča kwama kaiwae? Wo hu thuweya jin inanji e njamnjam, ma th…® kaiwo na ma th…® Ňčgiya ghanjikwama.  
\v 29 Ko ya dage e ghemi, othembe KiŇč Solomon, le bigibigi va i ghanagha moli, ghakwamakwama thovuthovuye moli, mava ghanjiyamoyamo Ňčgoreiye vara jin…®ke thiyake regha.  
\v 30 Loi i vanjimboŇčgiya nana Ňčgoreiyako, na nanako iyako noroke i mbuthumbuthu, ko evole i mare na th…® Ňčambu e nd…®ghe une. Iya kaiwae hu ghareghare wagiyawe iye ne i vanjimboŇčga. Ghemi lemi loŇčweghath…® nasiye moli.  
\v 31 Iya kaiwae tha hu rerenuwaŇča na huŇča, ‚ÄėNe wo ghana budakai?‚Äô o ‚ÄėNe wo muna budakai?‚Äô o ‚ÄėNe wo njimbo budakai?‚Äô  
\v 32 Thavala ma th…® loŇčweghath…® th…® tamweŇčgiya bigibigi Ňčgoranjiyako, ko iyemaeŇčge Ramami e buruburu kaero i ghareghare ghemi nuwamiya bigibigiko thiyako.  
\v 33 Ko wo hu tamwekaiya Loi le ghamba mbaro na hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya le renuwaŇča, amba ne i giyava e ghemi iya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye.  
\v 34 Iya kaiwae tha hu rerenuwaŇča evole kaiwae, kaiwae budakai ne i yomara weŇčga evole, evole mbe kaiwae. MbaŇča regha na regha mbe ghavuyowo. Thava te hu vatabova vuyowoko iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\c 7  
\s1 Tha hu wovathar…®thar…®Ňča ghamune  
\r (Luk 6:36-38,41-42)  
\p
\v 1 ‚ÄúTha hu wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčgiya ghamune, ne iwaeŇčge Loi i wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčga.  
\v 2 Loi le wovathar…®thar…® weŇčga ne i mboromboro weiye lemi wovathar…®thar…® weŇčgiya ghamunena. Lemi vakathako ghar…®ghar…® weŇčgi tembene i vakathava Ňčgoreiye weŇčga.   
\p
\v 3 ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae u thuweya ŇčuthuŇčuthuna ghanuna e marae, ko iyemaeŇčge ma u thuweya umbwana lagh…®ye iya ghen e maran…®na?  
\v 4 ThoŇčgo umbwa lagh…®ye ina e maran…®na, ŇčgoroŇčgaeŇčge na u dage weya ghanuna, ‚ÄėNe ya woraŇčgiya ŇčuthuŇčuthuna e maran…®na?‚Äô  
\v 5 Taukwana ghen! I viva wo u woraŇčgiya umbwana ghen e maran…®na na maran…®na i manjamanjala amba val…®kaiwae ne u woraŇčgiya ŇčuthuŇčuthuna ghanuna e marae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúTha hu giya bigi boboma weŇčgiya mbughambugha, ne iwaeŇčge th…® ndev…® na th…® ghar…®Ňčga. Tha hu wokiyathu lemi bigi thovuye mbombo e ghamwanji, ne th…® vur…®gh…®ya.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 NaŇčgo, tamwe na d…®gh…®d…®gh…® utuninji  
\r (Luk 11:9-13)  
\p
\v 7 ‚ÄúHu naŇčgo weya Loi na i giya weŇčga; hu tamwe na hu vaidi; hu d…®gh…®d…®gh…® na th…®n…®mba i vu weŇčga.  
\v 8 Kaiwae thela thoŇčgo i naŇčgowe ne i wo, thela thoŇčgo i tamwe ne i vaidi, na thela thoŇčgo i d…®gh…®d…®gh…® th…®n…®mba ne i mavuwe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga, thoŇčgo ghemina regha nariye i naŇčgo ghan…®Ňčgawe, ne i wogiya var…®we?  
\v 10 O thoŇčgo i naŇčgo weya borogi, ne i giya mwatawe?  
\v 11 Othembe ghar…®ghar…® raraithara ghemi, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye hu giyagiya bigibigi thovuthovuye weŇčgiya lemi ŇčgaŇčga. Iya kaiwae ra ghareghare wagiyawe, Ramanda e buruburu i giya bigibigi thovuthovuye weŇčgiya thavala th…® naŇčgowe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúBudakaiya nuwamiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha e ghemi, hu vakathava weŇčgi kaiwae Mosese le mbaro na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lenji vavaghare Ňčgoreiya iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Kamwath…® theghewo  
\r (Luk 13:24)  
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúHu ru e ghamba runa iya i mb…®mb…®thana, kaiwae Gehena ghaghamba ru i magaga na ghakamwath…® i lagh…®ye, na ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® rakareŇčawe.  
\v 14 Ko yawal…® ghaghamba ru i mb…®mb…®tha na kamwath…®niye nasiye na thegheviye eŇčge th…® vaidi.‚ÄĚ\fig Yawal…® ghaghamba ru i mb…®mb…®tha na kamwath…®niye nasiye|alt="The life's gate is narrow and the road is small - wide and narrow" src="Mat7.13,14.tif" size="col" copy="UBS (GNR)" ref="7:13-14" \fig*   
\s1 Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan  
\r (Luk 6:43-44)  
\p
\v 15 ‚ÄúHu njimbukikiŇčga, ghar…®ghar…® vavana ne th…® utu kwan…®kwan, ne th…®Ňčava thiye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi. Ghanjiyamoyamo ne Ňčgoreiya sip udauda, ko iyemaeŇčge e gharenjiko Ňčgoreiya mbugha njamnjam.  
\v 16 Une tene hu thuweya ve raŇčgi e lenji vakathako. Waen une mane vo vu e tatata t…®net…®ne, ae? Kopi une mane vo vu e kavwala, ae?  
\v 17 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, umbwa thovuye ne i rau ne une thovuye na umbwa raithar…® i rau ne une raithar…®.  
\v 18 Umbwa thovuye ma val…®kaiwae une i thar…® na umbwa raithar…® ma val…®kaiwae une i thovuye.  
\v 19 The umbwa i rau na une ma i thovuye, th…® kiten…®yathu na th…® bigiŇčambu e nd…®ghe une.  
\v 20 Ambane hu ghareghareŇčgi e lenji vakathaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Th…®n…®vair…® weŇčgiya thavala ma th…® ghambu Loi  
\r (Luk 13:25-27)  
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúMa ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye iya th…® dageke e ghino, ‚ÄėGiya, Giya,‚Äô ne th…® rakaruvao Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne, ko thela i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Bwebwe e buruburu le renuwaŇča iye ne ve ru.  
\v 22 MbaŇča ele ghambako ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo ne th…®Ňča ‚ÄėGiya, Giya, e idan wo utuŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae, e idan woŇča na nyao raraithar…® th…® rakaraŇčgi na e idan wo vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele lagh…®lagh…®ye.‚Äô  
\v 23 Amba ne ya dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄėMa ya ghareghareŇčga. Hu roiteteŇčgo, ghemi thar…® gharavakatha.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ňägolo gharavatavatad theghewo  
\r (Luk 6:47-49)  
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae thela i loŇčweya lo utuke na i vakatha Ňčgoreiye, iye Ňčgoreiya amalama le renuwaŇčama va i thovuye na i vatada le Ňčgoloma e var…® vwatae.  
\v 25 Uyevwelagh…® i nja, ŇčgonuŇčgo i voru na ndewendewe i rowo vur…®gheghe e Ňčgoloko iyako, ko iyemaeŇčge mava i mambun kaiwae va i vatad e var…® vwatae.  
\v 26 Ko thela i loŇčweya lo utuke na ma i vakatha Ňčgoreiye, iye Ňčgoreiya amalama le renuwaŇčama mava i thovuye na i vatada le Ňčgoloma e kerakera vwatae.  
\v 27 Uyevwelagh…® i nja, ŇčgonuŇčgo i voru na ndewendewe i rowo vur…®gheghe e Ňčgoloko iyako, i mambun na laiye lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 MbaŇča Jisas i utuvao utuutuke thiyake, le vavaghareko kaiwae i wo ghar…®ghar…® nuwanji.  
\v 29 Le vavaghare ma Ňčgoreiya mbaro gharavavaghare, kaiwae i vavaghare weiye mbaro.   
\c 8  
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala i ghataŇča lepelo  
\r (Mak 1:40-45; Luk 5:12-16)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Jisas i njama e ouko ghadidiye, wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakambele.  
\v 2 Amala i ghataŇča lepelo\f + \fr 8:2 \ft Lepelo gharumwaru ina Utu Gharumwaru e t…®ne Buk Boboma Toghake iyake ele ghambako t…®ne.\f* i mena na i ronja e gheghe vuvuye Jisas e ghamwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúGiyana, thoŇčgo nuwaniya, u vakathaŇčgo na ya thovuye.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Jisas i livamomoya n…®mae na i v…®ghath…®gha amalama amba iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguke nuwaiya, riwana i thovuye!‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako lepeloma iko.  
\v 4 Jisas i dagewe, ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇčeŇčgo! Ne u ndeutuŇča iyake weya lolo regha. U wawe vara ravowovowo na ve thuweŇčge. U bigiya ma manyiwo na vo vowo weya Loi Ňčgoreiya Mosese le mbaro na ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghareghare emunjoru riwana kaero i thovuye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariya Rom lenji ragagaith…®  //  gharandeviva le rakakaiwo  
\r (Luk 7:1-10)  
\p
\v 5 MbaŇča Jisas i ru Kapenaom, Rom lenji ragagaith…® gharandeviva i mena weya Jisas na i naŇčgowe thalavu kaiwae.  
\v 6 IŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, lo rakakaiwo i ghambwera, mbe ina e Ňčgolo i ghenaghena. Riwaeko i kuvokuvo na i v…®r…® lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Jisas i dagewe, ‚ÄúRa wao na va thawari.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Ragagaith…®ma lenji randeviva i gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúThava, Amalana. Ma elo thovuye ya vaŇčguŇčge na u mena elo Ňčgolo. Mbema uŇčaeŇčge na lo rakakaiwoko kaero riwae i thovuye.  
\v 9 Ya ghareghare ghen val…®kaiwan kaiwae ya yaku randeviva lagh…®lagh…®ye e lenji mbaro t…®ne na ghino ragagaith…® mbe inanjiva e raberabeŇčgu. ThoŇčgo ya dage weya regha, ‚ÄėU wa,‚Äô ne i wa, na ya dage weya regha, ‚ÄėU mena,‚Äô ne i mena, na thoŇčgo ya dage weya lo rakakaiwoko, ‚ÄėU vakatha iyake,‚Äô ne i vakatha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčweya iyake, ghare i yo na i dage weŇčgiya thiyeko th…® rereghambakowe, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, ma ya ndevaidi mun lolo regha le loŇčweghath…® le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ňčgoraiyake Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji.  
\v 11 Ya dage e ghemi, th…® ghanagha ne th…® mena yavorowoko na bodeoko weinjiyaŇčgiya Eibraham, Aisake na Jeikob, thiya yaku e lenji ghamba yaku Loi ele thaga, ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 12 Ko Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye lemoyo, thiye Loi va i vivathaŇča le ghamba mbaro kaiwanji, ne th…® bigiyathu raŇčgiyaŇčgi eto e momouwoko na th…® randa na th…® r…®gh…®mbiya ŇčiŇčinji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Amba Jisas i dage weya ragagaith…®ma lenji randeviva, iŇča, ‚ÄúU njogha! Ne Ňčgoreiya iya len loŇčweghath…®na.‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako le rakakaiwoma riwae i thovuye.   
\s1 Jisas i thawariŇčgiya Pita mboriyae na ghar…®ghar…®  
\r (Mak 1:29-34; Luk 4:38-41)  
\p
\v 14 MbaŇča Jisas i ru Pita ele Ňčgolo, i vaidiya Pita mboriyae i ghambwera na mbe ina vara e ghambae riwae i dayagha na i ghena.  
\v 15 I v…®ghath…®gha n…®mae na dayaghama ikowe, amba i thuweiru na i vaŇčamweŇčgi.   
\p
\v 16 Varae vama ve ronja amba th…® bigimenaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo nyao raraithar…® va inanji weŇčgi weya Jisas. Vambema i dage eŇčge nyaoko raraithar…® kaero th…® rakaraŇčgi na i thawariŇčgiya ghambweghambwera.  
\v 17 I vakatha Ňčgoraiyako na i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Aiseya le utu, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄúIye i vaŇčguraŇčgiyainda ghambwera e t…®ne na i woraŇčgiya ghandagida.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 8:17 \xt Ais 53:4\x*   
\s1 Ghar…®ghar…® thenjighewo th…®Ňča th…® ghambugha Jisas  
\r (Luk 9:57-62)  
\p
\v 18 MbaŇča i thuweya wabwi lagh…®ye th…® megh…®liŇča, i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu na th…® womalawa e val…®vaŇčga regha.  
\v 19 Mbaro gharavavaghare regha i menawe na i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, aŇčga ne u reŇča mbene ya ghambuŇčge vara.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbugha lavalavar…® mbe e lenji goga, na ma mbe e unyiunyinji. Ko Lolo Nariye ma e ghambaghambae na ne i vatowoŇča riwaewe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Lolo reghava, iye Jisas gharaghambu regha, i dage weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúGiyana, wo u vatomweŇčgo na va beku bwebwe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Jisas i gonjoghawe, ‚ÄúU ghambuŇčgo. Ramaremare tembe th…® bekuŇčgiya lenji ramaremare.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i dage weya ndewendewe na i mare  
\r (Mak 4:35-41; Luk 8:22-25)  
\p
\v 23 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® tha e waŇčga na th…® wareri.  
\v 24 Ma mbaŇča molao ndewendewe lagh…®ye i rowo e njigh…®ko t…®ne i vakatha bagodu i vana e waŇčga na i nja e waŇčga t…®ne. Ko Jisas va i ghenelaŇča.  
\v 25 Gharaghambuma th…® wa veth…® yavair…®, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, u vamoruime! Noroke woya munja.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu mararu? Lemi loŇčweghath…® ma i lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ Amba i thuweiru na i dage weya ndewendewe na bagodu th…® towo na mbaŇčara tad lagh…®ye i ghagha.   
\p
\v 27 Ghar…®ghar…®ma weiyaŇčgima gharenji i yo na th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThe loloke, othembe ndewendewe na bagodu th…® loŇčweghath…® ghal…®Ňčae?‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariŇčgiya amaamala thenjighewo  //  nyao raraithar…® nanjiwe  
\r (Mak 5:1-20; Luk 8:26-39)  
\p
\v 28 MbaŇča Jisas vama i wamalawa val…®mbwa na i tan e val…®vaŇčganiye iya Gadala ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yakukowe. Gheko i vaidiŇčgiya amaamala thenjighewo nyao raraithar…® ina weŇčgi th…® raŇčgima e ghabughabubuko. Ghanjithanavu va i thar…® moli na i vakatha ghar…®ghar…® ma th…® rakarakareŇča e kamwath…®ko iyako.  
\v 29 E mbaŇčako iyako th…® kulawe na ghal…®Ňčanji i lagh…®ye, ‚ÄúLoi Nariye ghen. Nuwaniya u vakatha budakai weime? Nuwaniya u lith…® weime, ko iyemaeŇčge amba ma lith…® ghambaŇča?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 30 Mbombo naura mava inanji bwagabwaga weŇčgi, va thiya nuve.  
\v 31 Nyaoma raraithar…® th…® naŇčgowe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo u variye raŇčgiyaime, u variyeime na voru weŇčgiya mbomboko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 32 I dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄúHu raka!‚ÄĚ Th…® raŇčgi na veth…® ru weŇčgiya mbomboma. Mbomboma mbe naura vara th…® rakanjaniya dagedagema, mbaŇčara e njigh…®, na vethiya munja.  
\v 33 Mbomboma gharanjimbunjimbu th…® rakavo na veth…® vutha e ghemba. Veth…® utugiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva budakai me yomara weŇčgiya amaamalama nyaoma raraithar…® inanji weŇčgi.  
\v 34 Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne th…® rakaraŇčgi weya Jisas. MbaŇča th…® thuwe, th…® naŇčgowe na i iteteŇča lenji val…®vaŇčgako iyako.   
\c 9  
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala i kuvokuvo  
\r (Mak 2:1-12; Luk 5:17-26)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas i tha e waŇčga na i wamalawa, i njogha e ghambae.  
\v 2 Amba ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® womena thegha reghawe i kuvokuvo na vambe i ghena vara e ghambae ghavwarara. MbaŇča i thuweya lenji loŇčweghath…®ko, i dage weya thegha i kuvokuvoma, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, ghen gharena i matuwo! Len thar…®na kaero ya numoten.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Mbaro gharavavaghare vavana th…® veutu weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalake iyake i munjeva iye Loi. Mbema i utuvathar…® vara weya Loi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Jisas i ghareghareya lenji renuwaŇčako, iya kaiwae i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae thar…® gharerenuwaŇča ina e gharemina?  
\v 5 IyaŇčganiya ghautuutu i maya, ‚ÄėLen thar…®na kaero ya numoten,‚Äô o yaŇča, ‚ÄėU yondovir…® na u loŇčga‚Äô?  
\v 6 Ya vaemunjoruŇča e ghemi, Lolo Nariye ele vur…®gheghe e yambaneke na val…®kaiwae i numotena thar…®.‚ÄĚ Amba i dage weya theghako kuvokuvoko, ‚ÄúU yondo, u bigiya ghambana ghavwarara na u wa e len Ňčgolo!‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Amba theghama i yondovir…® na i wa ele Ňčgolo.  
\v 8 MbaŇča wabwima th…® thuwe, i wo nuwanji na th…® taraweŇča Loi kaiwae i giya mbaro Ňčgoranjiyako weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.   
\s1 Jisas i kula weya Matiu na i ghambu  
\r (Mak 2:13-17; Luk 5:27-32)  
\p
\v 9 Jisas i iteta ghembako iyako na ma ve loŇčgaloŇčga amba i vaidiya amala regha idae Matiu; iye takis gharamban, ina ele ghamba kaiwo. I dagewe, ‚ÄúU ghambuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ Matiu i yondovir…® na i ghambu.   
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča Jisas i ghan…®Ňčga Matiu ele Ňčgolo, takis gharamban na ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…®\f + \fr 9:10 \ft ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® raraithar…®‚ÄĚ iyake i meth…® ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako thiye ma th…® ghambugha Jiu lenji mbaro.\f*, th…® rakamena na thiya yaku weinjiyaŇčgiya Jisas na gharaghambu na thiya ghan…®Ňčga.  
\v 11 Parisi vavana th…® thuwe iyake, th…® dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae lemi ravavaghare i ghan…®Ňčga weiyaŇčgiya takis gharamban na ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…®?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčwevaidi utuke iyake amba iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala riwanji thovuye ma nuwanjiya rathawathawari, mbe ghambweghambweraeŇčge nuwanjiya.  
\v 13 Hu wa na vou tamweya utuke iyake gharumwaru; iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėGhino nuwaŇčguiya gharenja ko ma nuwaŇčguiya vowo.‚Äô\x - \xo 9:13 \xt Hos 6:6\x* Kaiwae mava ya mena na ya kula weŇčgiya thavala th…® rumwaru, ya mena thar…® gharavakatha kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Th…® vaito Jisas ghan…®Ňčga ghambe kaiwae  
\r (Mak 2:18-22; Luk 5:33-39)  
\p
\v 14 Jon Rabap…®taiso gharaghambu th…® mena th…® vaito Jisas th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghime weimaŇčgiya Parisi wo mbeya ghan…®Ňčga mbaŇča vavana, ko ghan…®raghambu nandere?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae ghe gharaghaghayawo ne thiya randa mbaŇča ragheghe gh…®moru mbe inawe vara weiyaŇčgi? Nandere! Ko mbaŇča tene i mena ambane th…® vaŇčgu weŇčgiya ragheghe gh…®moru ko amba th…® mbeya ghan…®Ňčga.   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúMa lolo regha ne i liya kwama nasiye togha na i Ňčgiyagana kwama teuyewe i bowotu, kaiwae mbaŇča ne i thavwi na i livamo toghako i mwanavatha ma i vakathaeŇčge na i bowotu lagh…®ye.  
\v 17 Ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha i liŇčgiya waen togha e variye teuye th…® vakatha thetheghan njimwae. ThoŇčgo Ňčgoreiye, waen…®ko ne le vur…®gheghe kaiwae na i topo amba waen…®ko i maliŇčgi na variyeko i thar…®. Ko waen togha i liŇčgi e variye togha na mbe theghewoko vara th…® thovuye.‚ÄĚ\fig Waen variye th…® vakatha e thetheghan njimwae|alt="wine container made of animal skin" src="lb00145c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="9:17" \fig*   
\s1 Jairas yawarumbuye na ela i ghataŇča voruvoru  
\r (Mak 5:21-43; Luk 8:40-56)  
\p
\v 18 Jisas vamba i utuutu, Jiu lenji randeviva regha i mena i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúYawarumbuŇčguno amba me mare eŇčge. U mena. U liraweya n…®man…®na e riwae na yawaliye i njogha.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Jisas i yondovir…® na i ghambu weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu.   
\p
\v 20 Ela eunda i ghataŇča voruvoru theghathegha hoyaworo na umboiwo, i mena Jisas e ghereiye na i v…®ghath…®gha ghakwama mbothiye.  
\v 21 Le renuwaŇča va iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo mbema ya v…®ghath…® eŇčge gha kwamako, woghambwerake ne iko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Jisas i ndevagh…®le na i thuwe amba iŇča, ‚ÄúYawarumbuŇčgu, gharena i matuwo! Len loŇčweghath…®na i vamoruŇčge.‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako ghambwerama ikowe.   
\p
\v 23 MbaŇča Jisas i ru randevivama ele Ňčgolo, i thuweŇčgiya igo gharawiwi na wabwi lagh…®ye thiya raŇči karere i lagh…®ye,  
\v 24 amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTaulagh…®na ghemi hu rakaraŇčgi. Wevona ma i mare, mbema i ghena eŇčge.‚ÄĚ Taulagh…®ko th…® vav…®r…®.  
\v 25 Ko mbaŇča th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko eto, Jisas i ru wevoko ele ghamba ghena, i yalawe e n…®mae na i thuweiru.  
\v 26 Totoko iyako i lalo val…®vaŇčgako iyako.   
\s1 Amaamala thenjighewo maramaranji  //  i kwaghe na amala ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae  
\p
\v 27 Jisas i iteta ghembako iyako na ma ina e loŇčga mborowa, amba amaamala thenjighewo th…® kulakula reghambawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúDeivid rumbuye, gharen i nja weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 MbaŇča i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne, amaamalama maranjima i kwaghe th…® menawe na i vaitoŇčgi, ‚ÄúThare hu loŇčweghath…® val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya vamoruŇčga?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye amalana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 Amba i v…®ghath…®gha maramaranji na iŇča, ‚ÄúNe i yomara e ghemi Ňčgoreiya lemi loŇčweghath…®na.‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 Kaero val…®kaiwae th…® thuwe, Jisas i dage vavur…®gheghe weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu ndeutuŇča weya lolo regha.‚ÄĚ  
\v 31 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča th…® wa, veth…® utuŇča Jisas utuutuniye e val…®vaŇčgako iyako.   
\p
\v 32 Vama th…® wareri vara, ghar…®ghar…® vavana kaero th…® womenava amala regha weya Jisas. Nyao raithar…® va inawe na i vakatha ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae.  
\v 33 MbaŇča Jisas i dage weya nyaoko raithar…® na i raŇčgi, amalama kaero i utuutuva. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye gharenji i yo, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa mbaŇča regha ra thuweya bigi regha Ňčgoreiya iyake Isirel e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 34 Ko Parisi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNyao raraithar…® lenji randeviva i giya vur…®gheghewe iya i variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyaona raraithar…®.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Rakakaiwo ma th…® ghanagha  
\p
\v 35 Jisas i vagh…®liya ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiyeko wolagh…®ye. I vavaghare Jiu e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne na i utuŇča Toto Thovuye Loi le ghamba mbaro kaiwae, na i thawariŇčgiya gida na ghambwera tomethi.  
\v 36 MbaŇča i thuweŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye ghare i nja weŇčgi kaiwae riwanji i karavovo na ma e ghanjirathalavu, Ňčgoranjiya sip ma e ghanjiranjimbunjimbu.  
\v 37 Amba i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke thiyake Ňčgoranjiya uma lagh…®ye kaero i tara ko rakakaiwo ma th…® ghanagha.  
\v 38 Iya kaiwae hu naŇčgo weya Giya, iye umako tanuwagae na i variyeŇčgiya rakakaiwo na th…® uloulo.‚ÄĚ   
\c 10  
\s1 Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® theyaworo na theghewo  
\r (Mak 3:13-19; Luk 6:12-16)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas i kula vathavathaŇčgiya gharaghambu theyaworo na theghewo na i giya mbaro weŇčgi na val…®kaiwanji th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® na th…® thawariŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghataŇča tomethi gida na ghambwera.  
\v 2 Ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® theyaworo na theghewoko thiyako: iviva, Saimon, idae regha Pita, na ghaghae Endru; Jemes Sebedi nariye na ghaghae Jon;  
\v 3 Pilip na Batolomiu; Tomas na Matiu iye takis gharamban; Jemes Alipiyos nariye na Tadiyas;  
\v 4 Saimon iye i mena e wabwi regha idanji Jilot na Judas Isakariyot, iye Jisas ghaliliva.   
\s1 Jisas i variyeŇčgiya theyaworo na theghewo  //  na th…® kaiwo kaiwae  
\r (Mak 6:7-13; Luk 9:1-6)  
\p
\v 5 Jisas i variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke theyaworo na theghewoke thiyake. I giya vavur…®gheghe weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúThava ne hu wa thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye e lenji val…®vaŇčga o Sameriya ghar…®ghar…®niye e ghambaghambanji.  
\v 6 Ko, mbe hu wa eŇčge weŇčgiya sip raghaweghawe, thiye Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\v 7 Hu wa vou utu weŇčgi, huŇča, ‚ÄėLoi le ghamba mbaro ghe mbaŇča maiyavara.‚Äô  
\v 8 Hu vamoruŇčgiya ghambweghambwera, huŇča na ramaremare th…® thuweiru, hu thawariŇčgiya th…® ghataŇča lepelo na hu variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…®. Kaero hu wo ma e modamodae, ko ghemieŇčge hu wogiya bwaga ma e modamodae.  
\v 9 Tha hu bigiya gol, silva o kopa mani e lemi vethe nasiye t…®ne;  
\v 10 tha hu bigiya bigibigi ghanjinambo lemi loŇčgaloŇčgana kaiwae, tha hu liya ghamikwama ghayaboyabo yaŇčgarava, o ghemi ghae, o lemi pwasike. Tha hu rerenuwaŇča bigi regha kaiwae, kaiwae rakakaiwo ghambaro iye ne th…® njimbukiki.   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu ru e ghemba o ghemba nasiye regha, hu tamweya lolo thovuye regha e ghembana t…®ne. Hu yaku weimi gheghada hu iteta ghembana iyana.  
\v 12 MbaŇča ne hu ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne, huŇča ‚ÄėLoi i mwaewo weŇčga.‚Äô  
\v 13 ThoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® e Ňčgolona iyana th…® warari kaiwami, lemi dage mwaewoko yakuyaku thovuye kaiwae i meghabana gheko. Ko thoŇčgo ma th…® warari kaiwami lemi dage mwaewona mbe ghemieŇčge hu vaidiya ghathovuye na thiye nandere.  
\v 14 ThoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® e Ňčgoloko o e ghembako iyako ma th…® kula vathaŇčga o ma th…® loŇčweya lemi utuna, hu iteta Ňčgolona o ghembana iyana na hu tagavughethu vugha e gheghemina.  
\v 15 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, mbaŇča Loi le ghatha ghambaŇča ne i giya vuyowo lagh…®ye weŇčgiya Sodoma na Gomora ko iyemaeŇčge lagh…®ye moli ghar…®ghar…® ghembana iyana ne th…® vaidi.   
\s1 Jisas ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo  
\r (Mak 13:9-13; Luk 21:12-17)  
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúYa variyeŇčga Ňčgoreiya sip th…® rakaru mbugha lavalavar…® e t…®nenji. Ghemi mbe hu thimba Ňčgoreiya mwata na mbe ghamithanavu i ghenenja Ňčgoreiya bunebune.  
\v 17 Hu njimbukikiŇčga ghamimberegha, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® vavana ne thiya laweŇčga na th…® vaŇčguŇčga vohu kot. Ne th…® liya thiyo i vur…®gheghe na th…® yab…®b…®Ňčgawe e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne.  
\v 18 IdaŇčgu kaiwae ne th…® vaŇčguŇčga na th…® vaŇčguraweŇčga rambarombaro na kiŇč e maranji na hu utuŇča Toto Thovuye weŇčgi na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye weŇčgi.  
\v 19 MbaŇča ne th…® vaŇčguŇčga kot kaiwae, thava hu rerenuwaŇča ŇčgoroŇčga ne vohu utu na huŇča o ŇčgoroŇčga ne vohuŇča. Kaiwae ne e mbaŇčako iyako the utu nuwamiya ne hu utuŇča Loi ne i woveŇčga.  
\v 20 Kaiwae utuŇčgina iya ne hu utuŇčaŇčgina ma ghamimberegha lemi utu, Ramami e buruburu ghamberegha Une ina e ghemi iya ne i utuna.   
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúAmaamala vavana ne th…® vaŇčgugiya oghaghanji weŇčgiya rambarombaro na th…® gaboŇčgi, na gamagai oramanji ne th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye weŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga. Gamagai vavana ne th…® ndeghereiye wanaŇčgiya otatanji na oramanji na th…® vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya rambarombaro na th…® gaboŇčgi.  
\v 22 IdaŇčgu kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® botewoyathuŇčga, ko thela thoŇčgo i vur…®gheghe na i ghataŇčaghath…® ne le ghambako Loi i vamora yawaliye.  
\v 23 MbaŇča ne th…® vakatha vuyowo weŇčga e ghemba regha, hu vo na ma hu wava e ghemba regha. Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, amba mane hu vakathavao ghamikaiwo Isirel e ghembaghembaniyeko wolagh…®ye kaero Lolo Nariye i mena.  
\v 24 Ma ravavaona regha ne i kivwala le ravavaghare; ma rakakaiwo ne i kivwala ghagiyako.  
\v 25 I thovuye eŇčge ravavaona i tabo na Ňčgoreiya le ravavaghare na rakakaiwo Ňčgoreiya ghagiya. Ňägolo tanuwagae ghino, thoŇčgo th…® uno idaŇčgu Bil…®sabul\f + \fr 10:25 \ft Idae regha Seitan.\f* ghemi lo Ňčgoloko ghar…®ghar…®niye ghemi, ne th…® rena ida raraithar…® moli na ghemi idaidami.   
\s1 Tha ra mararuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® ra mararu eŇčge Loi  
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúTha hu mararuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, kaiwae budakaiya i rothuwele tene Loi i woraŇčgiya e manjamanjala, na budakaiya e ghayaboyabo tene i tatethewo.  
\v 27 Budakai ya utuŇča weŇčga e momouwo, hu utuŇča e manjamanjala; budakai ya vaŇčaewiŇča weŇčga hu utuŇča na ghal…®Ňčami lagh…®ye.  
\v 28 Tha hu mararuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, mbene th…® tagavamareŇčge lolo riwae, ko ma val…®kaiwanji th…® tagavamare lolo une. Hu mararu eŇčge Loi, iye val…®kaiwae i vakowana lolo riwae na une Gehena.  
\v 29 Toeya geth…®ra val…®kaiwae th…® vamodo ma nanasiye manyiwo, Ňčgoreiye? Ko iyemaeŇčge mane manda i dobu e thelau vwatae na Ramanda ma i ghareghare.  
\v 30 Na ghemi mbe Ňčgoreiyeva, umbalimina ndamwandamwae wolagh…®ye kaero i vaonavao.  
\v 31 Iya kaiwae tha hu mararu. Ghemi hu lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya make nanasiye wolagh…®ye.   
\p
\v 32 ‚ÄúThela thoŇčgo i woraŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e maranji na iŇča iye woraghambu, ghino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ne ya vakatha Ňčgoreiye weya Bwebwe e buruburu.  
\v 33 Ko thela thoŇčgo iŇča ma i ghareghareŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® e maranji, ghino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ne yaŇča ma ya ghareghare Bwebwe e buruburu e marae.   
\s1 Jisas ma i womena vanevane  //  ko i womena gaith…® ghaghalith…®  
\r (Luk 12:51-53; 14:26-27)  
\p
\v 34 ‚ÄúThava lemi renuwaŇča huŇčava ya mena e yambaneke na ya womena vanevane. Nandere. Ma ya womena vanevane, ko iyemaeŇčge ya mena na mbala gaith…® i yomara.  
\v 35 Ya mena na ya vakatha wabwi, gh…®moru i ndeghereiyewana ramae, wevo i ndeghereiyewana t…®nae, na gh…®moruko levo i ndeghereiyewana yawanyiye.  
\v 36 Gh…®moru ghath…®gh…®yaŇčgi lagh…®ye moli, iye mbe le bodabodaŇčgi.\x - \xo 10:36 \xt Mai 7:6\x*  
\v 37 Thela i mwaewo lagh…®ye weŇčgiya t…®nae na ramae na ma i mwaewo lagh…®ye weŇčgo iye ma val…®kaiwae i tabo na woraghambu. Thela i mwaewo lagh…®ye weya nariye, gh…®moru o wevo, na ma i mwaewo lagh…®ye weŇčgo iye ma val…®kaiwae i tabo na woraghambu.  
\v 38 ThoŇčgo thela ma i wo ghamberegha ghakros na i ghambuŇčgo, iye ma val…®kaiwae i tabo na woraghambu.  
\v 39 Thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i vamora yawaliye, ne i th…®vai. Thela thoŇčgo i vatomweya yawaliye ghino kaiwaŇčgu, ne i vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye.   
\s1 Modamodanji  
\p
\v 40 ‚ÄúThela i kula vathaŇčga, Ňčgoreiya i kulavathaŇčgo, na thela i kulavathaŇčgo Ňčgoreiya i kulavatha thela va i variyeŇčgo.  
\v 41 Thela i kulavatha Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, kaiwae iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, ne i vaidiya modae Ňčgoreiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu modae; na thela i kulavatha lolo ghathanavu thovuye kaiwae loloko iyako iye lolo thovuye, ne i vaidiya modae Ňčgoreiya lolo ghathanavu thovuye modae.  
\v 42 Thela i th…®n…®giya mbwa weya nanasiyeŇčgike thiyake regha na i mun kaiwae iye woraghambu, ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, ne e modamodae.‚ÄĚ   
\c 11  
\s1 Jisas na Jon Rabap…®taiso  
\r (Luk 7:18-35)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Jisas i giya vavur…®gheghe weŇčgiya gharaghambu theyaworo na theghewo na e ghereiye, i iteta ghembako iyako na i wa Jiu e ghambaghambanji vavana ve vavaghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® gheko.   
\p
\v 2 Jon Rabap…®taiso i loŇčweya Krais le vakatha utuniye e thiyo t…®ne, i variyeŇčgiya gharaghambu  
\v 3 weya Jisas na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhen mbema iya Jon va i utuŇča iŇča tene i mena o wo roroghaghaweva lolo regha?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njogha na vohu utugiya weya Jon, budakaiya kaero hu thuwe na hu loŇčwe:  
\v 5 maramaranji i kwaghe kaero th…® thuwe, kuvokuvo kaero th…® loŇčga, thavala th…® ghataŇča lepelo kaero riwanji i thovuye, yanawanji i kule th…® loŇčwe, ramaremare th…® thuweiru na mbinyembinyeŇčgu th…® loŇčweya Toto Thovuye iya th…® vavaghare weŇčgi.  
\v 6 Na tembe hu utugiyaweva iyake: Loi ghare weya lolo iya ma i roiteta ghino kaiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 MbaŇča Jon gharaghambu th…® rakarakanjogha, Jisas i utu weŇčgiya wabwiko Jon kaiwae. IŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča va hu wa weya Jon e njamnjam, va nuwamiya hu thuweya budakai? Va hu wa gheko na vambema nuwamiya eŇčge hu thuweya ndewendeweko i uvathawo wuŇčgiwuŇčgiko?  
\v 8 ThoŇčgo nandere, va hu wa eŇčge na vohu thuweya budakai? Amala regha i njimbo kwama ghayamoyamo i thovuye? Nandere, thavala th…® njimbo kwama thovuye th…® yaku kiŇč e lenji Ňčgolo.  
\v 9 Ko va vohu thuwe eŇčge budakai? Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu? Ňägoreiye, ya dage e ghemi, va vohu thuweya lolo regha iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu na ma e vwatanjiwova.  
\v 10 Amalagh…®niye kaiwae iyava ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha i rorina, iya iŇčake Loi iŇča, ‚ÄėNe ya variya ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu gharautu e ghamwan, iye i vivatharaweya kamwath…® ghen kaiwan.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 11:10 \xt Mal 3:1\x*   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, iya vara taulagh…®yake th…® yomara e yambaneke mamba regha i lagh…®ye kivwala Jon Rabap…®taiso. Ko thela idae nasiye moli Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne, iye i lagh…®ye kivwala Jon.  
\v 12 I ri e mbaŇčaniye Jon va i utuŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae na gheghada mbaŇčake noroke, ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® th…® munjeva th…® vakaiwoŇča lenji vur…®gheghe na th…® mando na th…® wo Loi le ghamba mbaro.  
\v 13 Mosese le Mbaro na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va th…® utuŇča Loi le ghamba mbaro utuniye i mena gheghada Jon ghambaŇča.  
\v 14 ThoŇčgo nuwamiya hu loŇčweghath…®gha iyake, mbema Jon utuniye iyava gharautu regha iŇča Ilaija ne i njoghama.  
\v 15 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami hu vandeŇče wagiyawe ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ne yaŇča thake noroke kaiwanji? Ya dage e ghemi, thiye Ňčgoranjiya gamagai thiya yaku e ghamba maket, th…® kulakula weŇčgiya ghanjiune, th…®Ňča,   
\p
\v 17 ‚Äú‚ÄėWo wiya ghe ghaigo, ko ma hu thari. Wo wothuŇča nuwathar…® wothuniye ko iyemaeŇčge ma hu randa.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® thake noroke Ňčgoranjiya gamagaiko thiyako tavwa gh…®thaŇčgi kaiwae mbaŇča Jon va i mena, mbaŇča vavana i mbeya ghan…®Ňčga naŇčgo kaiwae na mava i muna waen na ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėNyao raithar…® inawe.‚Äô  
\v 19 Ko mbaŇča Lolo Nariye i mena, i ghan…®Ňčga na i munumu, na ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėLoloke iyake ŇčgaŇčganir…® na waen gharamun; iye takis gharamban na thiye ma Jiu ghanjiu.‚Äô Ko thimba i mena weya Loi ne ra thuweya ghar…®ghar…® lenji vakatha i woraŇčgiya na ra wovaemuemunjoruŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ghembaghemba ma th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roitete  
\r (Luk 10:13-15)  
\p
\v 20 Jisas va i wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e ghembaghembako iyava i vakatha vara vakathako i ghanagha weŇčgi, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® mava th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roitete.  
\v 21 ‚ÄúAleu! Korasin, nevole hu thovuyaona! Aleu! Bet…®saida, nevole hu thovuyaona! ThoŇčgo vakathaŇčgike ghamba rotaele iyava ya vakathaŇčgina weŇčga ya vakathaeŇčge Taiya na Saidon weŇčgi, mbala vambe teuye, th…® njimbo kwama th…® vakatha thetheghan vulivuliye na th…® vavughe riwanji e vugha na i woraŇčgiya kaero th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roiteteŇčgi na Loi i numoten…®Ňčgi.  
\v 22 Ko ya dage e ghemi, mbaŇča Loi ne ghambaŇča ghatha Taiya na Saidon ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo seiwo ko ghemi ne hu vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 23 Na ghen Kapenaom, thava hu renuwaŇča Loi ne i yavwatata wanaŇčga e buruburu. Loi ne i wokiyathuŇčga vohu nja Hedesi. ThoŇčgo vakathaŇčgike ghamba rotaele iyava ya vakathaŇčgina weŇčga va th…® vakatha Sodoma, mbala mbe inawe e mbaŇčake noroke.  
\v 24 Ya dage e ghemi, mbaŇča ele ghambako, Loi ne i lith…® e ghemi vuyowo lagh…®ye moli, ko va i lith…® weŇčgiya Sodoma ma vuyowo lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas iye ghamba towo thovuye  
\r (Luk 10:21-22)  
\p
\v 25 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúYa taraweŇčaŇčge, Bwebwe, Giya ghen e buruburu na e yambaneke, kaiwae u wothuwela bigibigike thiyake weŇčgiya rathimbathimba na thavala lenji ghareghare i lagh…®ye na kaero u woraŇčgiya weŇčgiya thavala amba lenji renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiya gamagai.  
\v 26 Ňägoreiye Bwebwe, kaiwae len renuwaŇčana va Ňčgoreiyako iya u vakathako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 ‚ÄúBwebwe vama i giyavao weŇčgo ghareghareke wolagh…®ye. Ma lolo regha i ghareghare Nariye, mbe Bwebwe eŇčge, na ma lolo regha i ghareghare Bwebwe, mbe Nariyeke eŇčge ghino, na thavala ya tuthiŇčgi na ya woraŇčgiya weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúGhemi hu mena weŇčgo thavala riwami i bane na ghamibigi i vuyowo, na ya vatowoŇčaŇčga.  
\v 29 Bigike iya ya woveŇčgake, hu wo! Na hu varevareŇčgo! Kaiwae ghino wothanavu i ghenenja na i udauda na hu vaidiya towowe.  
\v 30 Bigike iya ya woveŇčgake i maya na doweke iya ne ya giyake e ghemi ma e vuyovuyowae.‚ÄĚ   
\c 12  
\s1 Jisas iye Sabat ghagiya  
\r (Mak 2:23-28; Luk 6:1-5)  
\p
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako, Sabat regha Jisas i ghathara wit e ghauma. Bada i ghar…®Ňčgiya gharaghambu, amba th…® vugha wit uneune na th…® ghan.  
\v 2 MbaŇča Parisi th…® thuweŇčgi amba th…® dage weya Jisas, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, ghan…®raghambu ma th…® ghambugha Sabat ghambaro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ma hu ndevaona mun Deivid utuutuniye, mbaŇča va weiyaŇčgiya ghaune na bada i ghar…®Ňčgi?  
\v 4 Va ve ru Loi ele Ňčgolo t…®ne na ravowovowo i giya bred bobomawe, i raŇčgi na th…® ghan weiyaŇčgiya ghauneko. Bred…®ko iyako va th…® ghan othembe mbaro i dageten weŇčgi, mbe ravowovowo eŇčge kaiwanji.  
\v 5 O ma hu vaona Mosese le Mbaro, iya iŇčake Sabat regha na regha ravowovowo th…® kaiwo e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne? Iyako kaero th…® raka Sabat ghambaro iyemaeŇčge ma th…® vakatha thar…®.  
\v 6 Ya dage e ghemi, bigi regha ina gheke, iye i kivwala Ňägolo Boboma.  
\v 7 Ma hu ghareghare utuutuke thiyake ghanjirumwaru, iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėGhino nuwaŇčguiya gharenja thanavuniye, ma nuwaŇčguiya vowo.‚Äô\x - \xo 12:7 \xt Hos 6:6\x* ThoŇčgo hu ghareghare wagiyawe utuutuke thiyake ghanjirumwaru mbala ma hu wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke thiya ma th…® vakatha thar…®ke.  
\v 8 Kaiwae Lolo Nariye iye Sabat ghagiya.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariya amala n…®mae i kuvokuvo  
\r (Mak 3:1-6; Luk 6:6-11)  
\p
\v 9 Jisas i iteta iyako na ve ru e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne,  
\v 10 na gheko, amala regha inawe, n…®mae i kuvokuvo. Ghar…®ghar…® vavana va inanji gheko, nuwanjiya th…® wonjoweya Jisas le vakatha vathar…® kaiwae. Th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga, la mbaro i vatomwe na i thovuye eŇčge ra vamora lolo Sabat e t…®ne o nandere?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 I dage weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ghemi regha le sip regha i dobu e goga Sabat e t…®ne, ma i thovuyewe ne i yalawe na i wovoreŇča?  
\v 12 Emunjoru sip bigi lagh…®ye, ko iyemaeŇčge lolo iye bigi lagh…®ye moli. Iya kaiwae la Mbaro i vatomweŇčge weinda ra vakatha vakatha thovuye Sabat e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Amba i dage weya amalama, iŇča ‚ÄúU livamomoya n…®man…®na.‚ÄĚ I livamomoya n…®maeko na kaero i thovuyeva Ňčgoreiya reghako.  
\v 14 Parisi th…® rakaraŇčgi na veth…® rerenuwaŇča ŇčgoroŇčga ne th…®Ňča na th…® un…®gh…®.   
\s1 Jisas iye Loi le rakakaiwo  
\p
\v 15 Jisas vama i ghareghare lenji renuwaŇčako, i iteta ghembako iyako na ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo th…® ghambu. Ghambweghambwerako wolagh…®ye va inanji e wabwiko t…®ne, i thawarivaoŇčgi,  
\v 16 i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi na thava th…® utuŇča utuniye thela amalagh…®niye.  
\v 17 Va i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Loi va iŇča weya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Aiseya.  
\v 18 IŇča:  
\q1 ‚ÄúLo rakakaiwo iyake. Iye va ya tuthi. Ya gharethovu na ya warari lagh…®ye kaiwae.  
\q1 Ne ya wogiya uneŇčgukewe, na iye ne i utuŇča lo renuwaŇča thovuye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye.   
\q1
\v 19 Mane i wogaith…® weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na mane i kulakula. Mane i utu na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®lagh…®ye.   
\q1
\v 20 Mane i yanji wanaŇčgiya thavala th…® njavovo, na thavala riwanji ma ele vur…®gheghe mane i vakowanaŇčgi.  
\q1 Ne i kaiwo gheghada Loi le ghamba mbaro thovuye i kivwalaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye.   
\q1
\v 21 Amalagh…®niye e idae ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye lenji vareminje ne inawe.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:21 \xt Ais 42:1-4\x*   
\s1 Ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča Jisas iye nyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya  
\r (Mak 3:20-30; Luk 11:14-23)  
\p
\v 22 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® womena amala regha maramara th…® kwaghe na ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae, kaiwae nyao raithar…® va inawe. Jisas i thawari ambama ghal…®Ňčae i mavu na kaero i thuweva.  
\v 23 Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye gharenji i yo na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwata iye Deivid Rumbuye, ae?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Ko mbaŇča Parisi th…® loŇčweya iyako, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúI variyeraŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® kaiwae nyao raraithar…® ghanjigiya Bil…®sabul i giya vur…®gheghewe na i vakatha Ňčgoreiye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 Jisas i ghareghare lenji renuwaŇčako na i dage weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúGhamba mbaro regha thoŇčgo th…® vakatha wabwi na wabwi na th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi, ghamba mbaroko iyako mane i wo mbaŇča molao. Na ghemba regha o Ňčgolo regha, thoŇčgo th…® vakatha wabwi na wabwi na th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi ne th…® dobu moli.  
\v 26 ThoŇčgo Seitan i variyeraŇčgiya le nyao raithar…® na i vakatha wabwi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne amba th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi, le ghamba mbaroko ne i ko moli.  
\v 27 Ghemi huŇča ya variyeraŇčgiya nyao raraithar…® kaiwae Seitan i giya vur…®gheghe e ghino, na thela i giya vur…®gheghe weŇčgiya ghamiraghambu na th…® variye raŇčgiyaŇčgiya nyao raraithar…®? Ghamiraghambu lenji vakatha i woraŇčgiya lemi kwan…®na.  
\v 28 Ko thoŇčgo Loi Une le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne na ya variyeraŇčgiya nyao raraithar…®, iyake i vaemunjoruŇča Loi le ghamba mbaro kaero i mena weŇčga.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae lolo regha i ru amala vur…®gheghe regha ele Ňčgolo na i kaiva le bigibigi thoŇčgo iviva ma i yalawekai na i Ňčgar…®ghath…® e thiyo, amba muyai i kaiva le bigibigiko e Ňčgoloko t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 30 ‚ÄúThela ma weiŇčgu iye woth…®gh…®ya, na thela ma weiŇčgu wo mbanvathavatha ghar…®ghar…® iye i vagevagegeyathu.  
\v 31 Iya kaiwae ya dage e ghemi, thela i vakatha thar…® na i utuvathar…® weya Loi, ne i numoten, ko thela thoŇčgo i utuvathar…® weya Nyao Boboma, Loi mane i numotena le thar…®ko iyako.  
\v 32 Thela thoŇčgo i utuvathar…® weya Lolo Nariye, Loi ne i numoten, ko thela thoŇčgo i utuvathar…® weya Nyao Boboma, Loi mane i numoten e mbaŇčake iyake o mbaŇča i menamenako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo umbwa thovuye, une tembe thovuyeva. ThoŇčgo umbwa raithar…®, une tembe raithar…®va. Umbwa, uneko i woraŇčgi, umbwa thovuye o raithar…®.  
\v 34 Ghemi Ňčgoramiya mwata! Ma val…®kaiwami hu utuŇča utu thovuye kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® raraithara ghemi! Kaiwae budakaiya i riyevanjara gharendake, iya ve raŇčgi e ghaendake.  
\v 35 Lolo thovuye i woraŇčgiya bigi thovuye kaiwae thovuyeko iyako i mena e ghare. Lolo raithar…® i woraŇčgiya bigi raithar…® kaiwae thar…®ko iyako i mena e ghare.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 36 ‚ÄúYa dage e ghemi, mbaŇča Loi ne ghambaŇča i ghathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, lolo regha na regha ne ve kot weya Loi utuko raraithar…® wolagh…®ye iya i utuŇčaŇčgiko kaiwanji.  
\v 37 ThoŇčgo e ghal…®Ňčamina lemi utu i thovuye Loi ne i wovathovuthovuyeŇčaŇčga. ThoŇčgo e ghal…®Ňčamina lemi utu raraithar…® Loi ne i wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčga.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Randeviva nuwanjiya th…® thuweya  //  vakatha ghamba rotaele regha  
\r (Mak 8:11-12; Luk 11:29-32)  
\p
\v 38 Amba Parisi na Mbaro gharavavaghare vavana th…® dage weya Jisas, th…®Ňča ‚ÄúRavavaghare, nuwameiya u vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele regha na wo thuwe mbala wo ghareghare u mena weya Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 39 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTha raraithara ghemi na hu roiteta Loi ghathanavu. Nuwamiya ya vakatha nono ghamba rotaele. Ko mane ya vakatha nono regha kaiwami. Nono ghamba rotaele mbe reghaeŇčge Loi ne i giya weŇčga, iyava i vakatha weya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Jona.  
\v 40 Kaiwae Jona va ina borogi e Ňčgamoiye mbaŇča thegheto na gougou thegheto, tembene Ňčgoreiyeva Lolo Nariye, mbaŇča thegheto na gougou thegheto ne ve yaku e thelau t…®ne.  
\v 41 MbaŇča Loi ghambaŇča i ghathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, Ninive ghar…®ghar…®niye ne th…® rakayondo th…® wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčgiya thake iyake, kaiwae va th…® loŇčwe Jona le vavaghare, th…® uturaŇčgiya lenji thar…® na th…® roitete, na mbaŇčake lolo regha ina gheke iye i lagh…®ye kivwala Jona.  
\v 42 MbaŇča Loi ne ghambaŇča i ghathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, kwin i mena e yaghalako ne i yondo na i wovathar…®thar…®ŇčaŇčga, kaiwae i ri e ghemba bwagabwaga moli na i mena i vandeŇče Solomon le thimba. Na mbaŇčake lolo regha ina gheke i lagh…®ye kivwala Solomon na thake iyake ma th…® goruwe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Nyao raithar…® le njogha  
\r (Luk 11:24-26)  
\p
\v 43 ‚ÄúMbaŇča nyao raithar…® i raŇčgi weya lolo regha, i wa ve loŇčgatakwa njamnjam…®ko t…®ne ma mbwaniye, i tamweya le ghamba towo, ko iyemaeŇčge ma i vaidiya regha.  
\v 44 Amba iŇča, ‚ÄėWo ya njogha Ňčgora lo ghamba yakuma ma rimawe.‚Äô MbaŇča i njogha, i thuweya le ghamba yakuko kaero th…® wanji wagiyawe na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e t…®neko th…® vakatha wagiyawe, ko iyemaeŇčge kokowae.  
\v 45 Amba i wa na ve vaŇčguŇčgiva nyao thenjighepir…®, th…® thar…® moli, th…® kivwala amalagh…®niye. Th…® ru na th…® yaku gheko. Loloko iyako le yakuyaku va i viva i thar…®, ko e mbaŇčako iyako i thar…® lagh…®ye moli. Iyake ne Ňčgoreiye weŇčga, ghemi thake raraithar…® iyake.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas le bodabodaŇčgiya thavala  
\r (Mak 3:31-35; Luk 8:19-21)  
\p
\v 46 Jisas vamba i utuutu weŇčgiya wabwi, t…®nae na oghaghae ma inanji eto th…® ndeghath…®, th…® tamwetamwewe kaiwae nuwanjiya th…® utuwe.  
\v 47 Amba lolo regha i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, t…®na na oghagha iya th…® ndeghath…® etoke, nuwanjiya th…® utu e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 48 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKo nava thela na oghaghaŇčguŇčgiya thavala?‚ÄĚ  
\v 49 I liya n…®mae na i th…®vatomweŇčgiya gharaghambu, na iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Thiyake, nava na oghaghaŇčgu.  
\v 50 Thela thoŇčgo i vakatha Bwebwe e buruburu le renuwaŇča iye ghaghaŇčgu, louŇčgu na t…®naŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\c 13  
\s1 Jisas i goghaimba weiwo gharayathu kaiwae  
\r (Mak 4:1-9; Luk 8:4-8)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇčako iyako e t…®ne, Jisas i raŇčgi e Ňčgoloko t…®ne, i wa e njigh…®ko ghadidiye na ve yakuwe.  
\v 2 Wabwi lagh…®ye moli th…® rakavathavatha na th…® rovagh…®liya, iya kaiwae i tha e waŇčga regha na i yakuwe, ko ghar…®ghar…®ko va thiya ndeghath…® e njigh…®ko ghadidiye.   
\p
\v 3 Mbe i goghaimbaeŇčge na i utuŇča bigibigi i ghanagha weŇčgi. IŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča regha amala regha i wa ele uma na ve yathu weiwo.  
\v 4 MbaŇča i yathu vavana th…® unja e kamwath…® mara, ma th…® mena th…® ghan…®Ňčgi.  
\v 5 Vavana veth…® unja e thelau ele var…®var…® ko ghanjithelauko mava i poku. Va th…® maya e mbuthu, kaiwae ghanjithelauko mava i poku.  
\v 6 Ko mbaŇča varae i yovoro na i mb…®le, dayaghawae kaiwae i ŇčambuŇčgi na i mareyawowo kaiwae wathelilinji ma vamba ina bwagabwaga.  
\v 7 Weiwo vavana veth…® unja Ňčgora nana raraithar…® kaero inanjiwe, nanako thiyako lenji mbuthu i maya na th…® vwariŇčgiya wit…®ma.  
\v 8 Mbombouye vavana va veth…® unja e thelau thovuye na th…® rau. Tomethi uneunenji, vavana uneunenji vogh…®thaŇčar…® (100), vavana vogh…®yewona (60) na vavana vogh…®yeto (30).  
\v 9 ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami hu vandeŇče wagiyawe ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ\fig Weiwo gharayathu|alt="The seed sower" src="Lk8.4.tif" size="col" copy="UBS (GNR)" ref="13:1-9" \fig*   
\s1 ŇägoroŇčga goghaimba ghanjirumwaru  
\r (Mak 4:10-12; Luk 8:9-10)  
\p
\v 10 Gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mbe u goghaimbaeŇčge mbaŇča u utu weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro gharerenuwaŇča va i rothuwele kaero i woraŇčgiya weŇčga, ko ma vamba i woraŇčgiya weŇčgi.  
\v 12 Thela ele ghareghare Loi ne i vatabowe na Loi ghaghareghare i lagh…®ye moliwe; ko thela ma Loi ghaghareghare inawe, othembe seiwo moli ele ghareghare, Loi ne i woraŇčgivaowe.  
\v 13 Lo r…®ghe iya ya utu na mbe ya goghaimbake eŇčge weŇčgi, kaiwae th…® ghaghayawo, ko iyemaeŇčge ma th…® ghewovaidi, na th…® vandeŇče, ko iyemaeŇčge ma th…® loŇčwe wagiyawe na th…® ghareghare.  
\v 14 Thiyeke weŇčgi, Aiseya, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu ghal…®Ňčae i tabo na emunjoru, iya iŇčake,  
\q1 Mbe hu vandevandeŇča, ko iyemaeŇčge ma hu ghareghare, mbe hu ghaghayawo, ko iyemaeŇčge ma hu ghewovaidi.   
\q1
\v 15 Kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake gharenji i vur…®gheghe, th…® vowiya yanawanji, na th…® k…®k…®mare kaiwae th…® botewo ghathuwathuwa.  
\q1 Th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye mbala ma th…® thuwe e maranji, ma th…® loŇčwe e yanawanji o th…® ghareghare e gharenji, na th…® numonjogha e ghino na ya thawariŇčgi.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 13:15 \xt Ais 6:9-10\x*   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúKo ghemi, i thovuye moli kaiwae marami i manjamanjala na yanawami i bowotu.  
\v 17 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi na ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghambugha Loi ghathanavu va nuwanjiya moli th…® thuwe budakaiya kaero hu thuwe na th…® loŇčwe budakaiya kaero hu loŇčwe, ko mava val…®kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i vamanjamanjalaŇča rayathu weiwo ghagoghaimba  
\r (Mak 4:13-20; Luk 8:11-15)  
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče ya vamanjamanjalaŇča rayathu weiwo ghagoghaimba na hu loŇčwe.  
\v 19 MbaŇča lolo regha i loŇčweya Loi le ghamba mbaro utuniye na ma i ghareghare gharumwaru, Seitan ne i mena na i mbana budakai va th…® kabu e ghareko. Weiwoke iyake iyava veth…® unja e kamwath…®ma mara.  
\v 20 Weiwoma iyava veth…® unja e thelauma ele var…®var…®ma, thiyake Ňčgoreiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweya utu thovuye na e mbaŇčako iyako th…® wo utuko iyako weiye lenji warari,  
\v 21 ko iyemaeŇčge ma th…® rerenuwaŇča kaiwae na mbe mbaŇča ubotu eŇčge i yaku kaiwae watheliliye ma i nja bode. MbaŇča th…® vaidiya vuyowo o ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® vakathaŇčgi na th…® vaidiya v…®r…® utuko thovuye kaiwae, e mbaŇčako iyako kaero th…® dobu.  
\v 22 Weiwoma iyava veth…® unja Ňčgora nanama raraithar…® inanjiwe, thiyake Ňčgoranjiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweya utu thovuye ko iyemaeŇčge yambaneke renuwaŇčaniye i vagaghala nuwanji na nuwanjiko i ghaŇčgo weya gogomwau na nuwanjiya lemoyo, iyake kaiwae, mane th…® mbuthu na th…® rau.  
\v 23 Weiwoma iyava veth…® unja e thelauma thovuye, thiyake Ňčgoranjiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweya utu thovuye na th…® ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga gharumwaru; th…® rau, vavana uneune vogh…®thaŇčar…® (100), vavana vogh…®yewona (60) na vavana vogh…®yeto (30).‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Goghaimba nana raithar…® kaiwae  
\p
\v 24 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava goghaimba regha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya iyake. Amala regha i yathu wit mbombouye thovuthovuye ele uma.  
\v 25 Gougou regha ghar…®ghar…®ko va thiya ghena amba amalama ghath…®gh…®ya i mena i ru e umama t…®ne na i yathu nana raithar…® mbombouye e wit…®ma t…®nenji na i wa.  
\v 26 MbaŇča wit…®ma i mbuthu na kaero i woraweya le rau r…®ghe, nanama raraithar…® kaero th…® yomarava.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 ‚ÄúAmalama le rakakaiwo th…® menawe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėAmalana, va u yathu wit mbombouye thovuye e len umako t…®ne, na nanako raraithar…® aŇčga th…® mena?‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúI dage weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄėWoth…®gh…®ya regha nuwaiya i vakatha thar…® e ghino iya i vakatha iyana.‚Äô Rakakaiwoma th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėThare nuwaniya ghime wo wa na vo mutuyathu?‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúIŇča, ‚ÄėThava, kaiwae mbaŇča ne vou muta nanana raraithar…® ne hu ther…®vair…®thavwi weiye wit…®na.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 30 ‚ÄúWo th…® mbuthu na regha weiye wit…®na gheghada mbaŇča wit…®na ne i mweghe na ra vugh…®. Ne e mbaŇčako iyako ya dage weŇčgiya ravathevatheko, ‚ÄėHu mutukaiya nanana raraithar…® na hu yavathaŇčgi, tene ra ŇčambuŇčgi, ko amba hu mbana wit…®na na hu vathe e ghaŇčgolona.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Mas…®ted mbouye ghagoghaimba  
\r (Mak 4:30-32; Luk 13:18-19)  
\p
\v 31 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava goghaimba regha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya umbwa regha idae mas…®ted mbouye\f + \fr 13:31 \ft Mas…®tedke iyake ghar…®ghar…® th…® kabu e lenji uma na th…® vakaiwoŇča kaiwae i giya ghaniŇčga gham…®nae thovuye, Ňčgoreiye th…® vakaiwoŇča njigh…®. Iyake ma ndiya th…® ghawi weiye gh…®leth…®.\f*, amala regha va i wo na i wokabu ele uma t…®ne.  
\v 32 Mbouyeke iyake weiwoke wolagh…®ye mbombounji nasiyeninji moli. Ko mbaŇča i mbuthu na lagh…®ye, i kivwalaŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e umako t…®ne. I tabo na umbwa regha na make wolagh…®ye th…® mena th…® vakatha unyinji e yaŇčgayaŇčgako.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Is…®t ghagoghaimba  
\r (Luk 13:20-21)  
\p
\v 33 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava goghaimba regha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya is…®t. Wevo eunda i th…®n mbe nasiye eŇčge na i basi weiye pwalawa, uye vwarato, is…®t…®ko i kaiwo na i ruvao e pwalawako lagh…®ye t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Buda kaiwae Jisas i goghaimba  
\r (Mak 4:10-12; Luk 8:9-10)  
\p
\v 34 Jisas i goghaimba mbaŇča me utuŇča bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®. Mava te i reŇčava e kamwath…® regha na i utuŇča bigi regha weŇčgi mbe goghaimbaeŇčge.  
\v 35 Iyake i vaemunjoruŇča ŇčgoroŇčga Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va iŇča ne i yomara, iya iŇčake:  
\q1 Ne ya utu mbene ya goghaimbaeŇčge, mbe goghaimbaeŇčge ne ya woraŇčgiya weŇčgi the bigiya i rothuwele mbaŇča va i vakatha yambaneke na ghaghada noroke.\x - \xo 13:35 \xt Sam 78:2\x*   
\s1 Jisas i vamanjamanjalaŇča nana raithar…® ghagoghaimba  
\p
\v 36 Jisas i iteteŇčgiya wabwima na i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne. Gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU vamanjamanjalaŇča weime nanama raraithar…® i mbuthu e umama t…®ne ghagoghaimba.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 37 I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLoloko iya i yathu wit…®ko mbombouye thovuye iye Lolo Nariye.  
\v 38 Uma iye yambaneke, na weiwo thovuye thiye Loi le ghamba mbaro ghar…®ghar…®niye. Nana raraithar…® thiye Seitan le ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgi,  
\v 39 na loloko iya nuwaiya i vakatha thar…®ko, iya i kabu nanako raraithar…® iye Seitan. Vathe ghambaŇča iye mbaŇča le ghambako, na ravathevathe thiye nyao thovuthovuye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 40 ‚ÄúKaiwae th…® muta nana raraithar…® na th…® Ňčambu e nd…®ghe, nevole Ňčgoreiya iyako mbaŇča ne ele ghambako.  
\v 41 Lolo Nariye ne i variyeŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye na th…® mutuyathuŇčgiya thavala th…® vakathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana na th…® vakatha thar…® na thanavu raraithar…® gharavakathaŇčgi. Taulagh…®Ňčgiko ne th…® mutuyathuŇčgi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 42 Ne th…® bigiyathuruwoŇčgi e nd…®ghe lagh…®ye moli une na veth…® randa na th…® r…®gh…®mbiye ŇčiŇčinji.  
\v 43 Amba thavala ghanjithanavu i thovuye, manjamanjalawanji ne Ňčgoreiya varae manjamanjalawae Ramanji ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne. ThoŇčgo e yanayanawami hu vandeŇče ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Bigibigi thovuthovuye th…® wole e uma t…®ne ghagoghaimba  
\p
\v 44 ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya gogomwau thovuye th…® wole e uma t…®ne na th…® mareitete. Amala regha i vaidi na mbowo i wolenjoghava. Weiye le warari lagh…®ye moli gogomwauko iyako kaiwae, amba i wa na ve vakuneŇča le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, i mbana mani na i vamodo umakowe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ňägile thovuye moli ghagoghaimba  
\p
\v 45 ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro tembe Ňčgoreiyeva iyake. Bigibigi gharakune regha i tamweŇčgiya Ňčgile thovuye moli.  
\v 46 MbaŇča regha i vaidiya regha, i thovuye moli na modae i lagh…®ye moli, amba i wa, ve vakuneŇčaŇčgiya le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye na i vamodo Ňčgileko iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ghina ghagoghaimba  
\p
\v 47 ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghina th…® lirawe e njigh…®ko t…®ne, na th…® wo borogi tomethi.  
\v 48 MbaŇča i riyevanjara, th…® momod…®voreŇča e njigh…®ko ghadidiye, thiya yaku amba th…® ghatha. Borogi thovuthovuye th…® mban…®Ňčgi e kwaekwae na raraithar…® th…® bigiyathu.  
\v 49 Nevole Ňčgoreiyako mbaŇča ne ele ghambako. Nyao thovuthovuye ne th…® rakamena na th…® ghatha raŇčgiyaŇčgiya raraithar…® thovuthovuyeko e t…®nenji,  
\v 50 na th…® bigiyathuruwoŇčgi e nd…®ghe lagh…®ye moli une na veth…® randa na th…® r…®gh…®mbiye ŇčiŇčinji.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Vavaghare togha na vavaghare teuye  
\p
\v 51 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúThare nuwami i manjamanjala bigibigike thiyake kaiwanji?‚ÄĚ Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 52 I dage weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúIya kaiwae mbaro gharavavaghare, iya thiye kaero th…® tabo na Loi le ghamba mbaro gharaghambuŇčgi, thiye Ňčgoranjiya Ňčgolo tanuwagae i bigiraŇčgiya bigibigi totogha na teteuye ele woluwolu t…®ne na i bigirawe eto.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Nasaret ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® botewo Jisas  
\r (Mak 6:1-6; Luk 4:16-30)  
\p
\v 53 MbaŇča Jisas i utuvaoŇčgiya goghaimbaŇčgike thiyake amba i iteta ghembako iyako.  
\v 54 I njogha e ghambae na i vavaghare e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne. Gharenji i yo le vavaghareko kaiwae na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLe ghareghareko aŇčga i mena? ŇägoroŇčga na val…®kaiwae i vakatha vakathaŇčgike ghamba rotaele thiyake?‚ÄĚ  
\v 55 ‚ÄúMbema kapentama nariya iyako, ae? T…®naya Meri, ae? OghaghaeŇčgiya Jemes, Josep, Saimon na Judas.  
\v 56 Oloulouye mbe ra yaku gheke weindaŇčgi, Ňčgoreiye ae? AŇčga mendava i wo le ghareghareko na le vur…®ghegheko?‚ÄĚ  
\v 57 Iya kaiwae gharenji i gaith…®wana na th…® botewoyathu.  
\p Jisas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® th…® yavwatatawana Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu e ghembaghembako wolagh…®ye, ko ghambae ghar…®ghar…®niye na le bodaboda ma th…® yavwatatawana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 58 Ma i vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele lemoyo gheko kaiwae ma th…® loŇčweghath…®.   
\c 14  
\s1 Th…® kitena Jon Rabap…®taiso numwe  
\r (Mak 6:14-29; Luk 9:7-9)  
\p
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako, Herod, iye Galili gharambarombaro i loŇčweya Jisas le vakatha utuutuniye.  
\v 2 I dage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwo e raberabe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoloko iyako mbema emunjoru Jon Rabap…®taiso, i thuweiru na tembe e yawayawaliyeva. Iya kaiwae val…®kaiwae i vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele Ňčgoranjiyako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3-4 Kaiwae Herod va i viwe ghagha Pilip levo Herodiyas na i ghe weiye, Jon vambe i vathivalaŇča wevara, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhanda Mbaro ma i vatomwe e ghen na u vaŇčgwa Herodiyas!‚ÄĚ Iyako kaiwae, Herod va iŇča na th…® yalawe Jon, th…® Ňčgar…® na th…® woruwo e thiyo.  
\v 5 Herod va nuwaiya iŇča na Jon i mare, ko va i mararuŇčgiya Jiu kaiwae va th…®Ňča Jon iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.   
\p
\v 6 MbaŇča Herod i vakatha le vir…® gharenuwaŇčakiki ghan…®Ňčganiye, Herodiyas yawarumbuye i thari wabwiko e maranji, i vakatha Herod i warari lagh…®ye,  
\v 7 na i tholo e maranji iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dagerawe e maran, the bigiya ne u naŇčgo e ghino ne ya woveŇčge.‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Ňägoreiya t…®nae me le woraŇčgiyawe, i dage weya Herod iŇča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake u woraweya Jon Rabap…®taiso umbaliye e gaeba t…®ne na u woveŇčgoma.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 KiŇč…®ma nuwae i thar…®, ko kaiwae kaero me tholo na i dagerawe le val…®giyagiyako e maranji, iŇča na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya wevoko le renuwaŇča.  
\v 10 I variyeŇčgiya le rakakaiwo na veth…® kitena Jon numwe e thiyo t…®ne.  
\v 11 Th…® th…®n…®mena umbaliye e gaeba na th…® th…®n…®giya weya wevoma na i yoth…®n weya t…®nae.  
\v 12 Jon gharaghambu th…® rakamena th…® wo Jon riwae na th…® wobeku; amba th…® wa veth…® utugiya utuniye weya Jisas.   
\s1 Jisas i vaghan…®Ňčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye paeb tausan  
\r (Mak 6:30-44; Luk 9:10-17; Jon 6:1-14)  
\p
\v 13 MbaŇča Jisas i loŇčweya Jon utuutuniye, i tha e waŇčga ghamberegha na i iteta ghembako iyako, i wa e val…®vaŇčga ma ghar…®ghar…®niye. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčweya toto Jisas kaero me wa, th…® rakaiteteŇčgiya ghambaghambanji, th…® loŇčga e gheghenji na th…® rakareghambawe.  
\v 14 Jisas i nja e waŇčgama na mbaŇča i thuweya wabwiko lagh…®ye, ghare i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli kaiwanji na i thawariŇčgiya lenji ghambweghambweraŇčgi.   
\p
\v 15 MbaŇča vama yegh…®yegh…®ye, gharaghambu th…® rakamenawe na th…® dagewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVanatherowoke, na kaero yegh…®yegh…®ye moli. U variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na na tembe thiye veth…® vamodo ghanji e ghembaghemba.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúThava th…® raka. Ghemi hu giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgi na th…® ghan.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Th…® dagewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBred…®ma mbe mbumbulima eŇčge na borogi umboiwo ina weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 IŇča, ‚ÄúHu bigimena gheke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 I dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na thiya yaku e nanako vwatavwata, amba i mbana bred…®ma mbumbulimama na borogima umboiwo, i gh…®mara voro e buruburu na i vata ago weya Loi ghan…®Ňčgako kaiwae. I njiviyaviya bred…®ma, i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuma na th…® giya weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma.   
\p
\v 20 Taulagh…®ko thiya ghan…®Ňčga na val…®kaiwanji. Amba gharaghambuko th…® mbana ghan…®Ňčgama vaŇčgovaŇčgothiye na th…® mban…®vanjaraŇčgiya nambonambo Ňčgamwayaworo na Ňčgamwaiwo.  
\v 21 Iya vara taulagh…®ko va thiya ghan…®Ňčgako gh…®mogh…®moru lenji ghanaghanagha paeb tausan na wanakau na gamagai e vwatanjiva.   
\s1 Jisas i loŇčga e njigh…® vwatae  
\r (Mak 6:45; Jon 6:15-21)  
\p
\v 22 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu na th…® rakatha e waŇčgama th…® viva e ghamwae Galili Njigh…®niye ele val…®vaŇčga regha, na i variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® rakanjogha e ghambanji.  
\v 23 I variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na e ghereiye ghamberegha i voro e ou ghadidiye na i naŇčgowe. Vama i gou na Jisas ina gheko ghamberegha;  
\v 24 na e mbaŇčako iyako waŇčgama vama ina eto na bagodu i vauneuneŇča kaiwae th…® womana i ghemba ndewendeweko marae.   
\p
\v 25 Igh…®viya rakaraka Jisas i loŇčga e njigh…® vwatae i mena weŇčgiya gharaghambu.  
\v 26 MbaŇča th…® thuweya i loŇčga e njigh…®ko vwatae th…® mararu lagh…®ye moli. Th…®Ňčava, ‚ÄúKaka!‚ÄĚ na th…® yaro weiye lenji mararu lagh…®ye.\fig Jisas i loŇčga e njigh…® vwatae|alt="Jesus walking on the water" src="IB04126bw.tif" size="span" copy="Faadil" ref="14:22-26" \fig*   
\p
\v 27 Jisas i dage weŇčgi e mbaŇčako iyako, iŇča, ‚ÄúTha huya mararu! Ghino! Ghino!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 Amba Pita i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, thoŇčgo emunjoru ghen, u dage na ya nja ya loŇčga ghaona e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 Jisas i gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena!‚ÄĚ Pita i ghaenja na i loŇčga ghemba Jisas e njigh…®ko vwatae.  
\v 30 Ko mbaŇča i thuweya ndewendeweko le vur…®gheghe i mararu na mbalama i munja amba i goyawaru, iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana! U thalavuŇčgo!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 31 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i tagavamomoya n…®man…®mae i yalawe, i vikiki amba i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúLen loŇčweghath…® i nasiye. Buda kaiwae mo numoghegheiwo?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 32 Vambe thenjighewoko vara th…® vana e waŇčgama na ndewendewema i mare.  
\v 33 Amba gharaghambuko e waŇčgako th…® kururu weya Jisas na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru Loi Nariya ghen!‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariya ghambweghambwera Genesaret  
\r (Mak 6:53-56)  
\p
\v 34 Th…® golawa Galili Njigh…®niye e ghereiye na th…® mena th…® goru Genesaret.  
\v 35 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuwe na th…® ghareghare amalagh…®niye Jisas, amba th…® variya toto e ghembaghemba e val…®vaŇčgako iyako na th…® bigimenaŇčgiya ghambweghambwera.  
\v 36 Th…® naŇčgowe na thoŇčgo i vatomwe, ghambweghambwerako ma th…® v…®ghath…® eŇčge ghakwamako mbothiye, na taulagh…®ko iyava th…® v…®ghath…®ko riwanji i thovuye.   
\c 15  
\s1 Budakai i vamb…®gh…®yainda  
\r (Mak 7:1-23)  
\p
\v 1 Parisi na mbaro gharavavaghare vavana th…® ri Jerusalem, th…® wa weya Jisas na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča  
\v 2 ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghan…®raghambuke ma th…® ghambugha budakaiya orumburumbunda va th…® valawe weinda? Kaiwae mbaŇča th…® ghan…®Ňčga ma th…® thavwiya n…®man…®manji, Ňčgoreiya la kururu le woraŇčgiya weinda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNa ghemi buda kaiwae ma hu ghambugha budakaiya Loi va i dage weinda na ra vakatha Ňčgoreiye, ko mbe hu ghambu eŇčge mbe ghemi ghamithanavu?  
\v 4 Kaiwae Loi iŇča, ‚ÄėMbe hu yavwatata wanaŇčgiya rama na t…®na.‚Äô\x - \xo 15:4 \xt RaŇč 20:12; 21:17; Mba 5:16; Liv 20:9\x* Na tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄėThela i utuvathar…® ramae na t…®nae weŇčgi, th…® tagavamare.‚Äô  
\v 5 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi lemi vavaghare Ňčgoreiyake: huŇča thoŇčgo lolo le bigibigi lemoyo val…®kaiwae i thalavuŇčgiya t…®nae na ramae, ko mbe i thovuye eŇčge thoŇčgo ma i giya weŇčgi na ma i yavwatata wanaŇčgi. Na tembe huŇčava val…®kaiwae ne i dage weŇčgi na iŇča, ‚ÄėBigibigi mendava ya bigirawe kaiwami, kaero mendava ya dagerawe Loi kaiwae, mane ya giya weŇčga.‚Äô  
\v 6 Hu utu Ňčgoreiyako kaero hu kivwala Loi le mbaro na mbe hu goruweŇčge lemi vavagharena iya i mena weŇčgiya o rumburumbumina.  
\v 7 Taukwana ghemi! Aiseya, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, va i utuŇča emunjoru, ghemi utunimi:  
\v 8 Loi iŇča,  
\q1 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake e ghaenjike njimwae th…® yavwatata wanaŇčgo, ko gharenjiko i bwagabwaga moli e ghino.   
\q1
\v 9 Lenji kururu weŇčgo Ňčgoreiya bigi bwabwaga, th…® vavaghareŇča ghar…®ghar…® lenji renuwaŇča na th…®Ňčava Loi le mbaro.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 15:9 \xt Ais 29:13\x*   
\p
\v 10 Jisas i kula vathavathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vandeŇčeŇčgo na nuwamina i rumwaru.  
\v 11 Budakai i ru e ghaendake ma i vamb…®gh…®yainda, ko budakai i raŇčgima e ghaendake, iyake i vamb…®gh…®yainda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare u ghareghare, Parisi gharenji me gaith…® len utuna kaiwae?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBigibigike wolagh…®ye iya Bwebwe e buruburu ma va i kabuŇčgi ne th…® mutuyathuŇčgi.  
\v 14 Tha hu rerenuwaŇča kaiwanji! Thiye Ňčgoranjiya ghar…®ghar…® maranji i kwaghe na th…® mando na th…® viva weŇčgiya ghanjiune vavana. ThoŇčgo lolo regha marae i kwaghe i viva weya tembe marae i kwagheva, mbene thenjighewoko vara th…® dobu e goga.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Pita i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúU vamanjamanjalaŇča goghaimbake iyake weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Jisas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúKo woraghambuke ghemi nuwami mbe ma i manjamanjalava?  
\v 17 Ma hu ghareghare? Budakai i ru e ghaendake i nja e Ňčgamoinda na ve raŇčgi ele kamwath…®.  
\v 18 Ko budakai i raŇčgima e ghaendake i mena e gharenda. Iyake i vamb…®gh…®yainda.  
\v 19 Kaiwae i raŇčgima e gharenda Ňčgoranji: renuwaŇča raraithar…®, gabo, yathima, dubwara, kaiv…®, utu kwan…®kwan na ra liya ghandau ghautu.  
\v 20 Thiyake th…® vamb…®gh…®yainda, ko ma ra thavwiya n…®manda na ra ghan…®Ňčga ma i vamb…®gh…®yainda.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 T…®nan Kenani le loŇčweghath…®  
\r (Mak 7:24-30)  
\p
\v 21 Jisas i iteta ghembako iyako na i wa Taiya na Saidon e lenji val…®vaŇčga.  
\v 22 Kenani wevoniye eunda, i yaku e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, i mena weya Jisas. I kulakula, iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, Deivid Rumbuye, gharen i njaweŇčgo! Nyao raithar…® ina weya yawarumbuŇčguno, i vakatha na i v…®r…® lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Ko Jisas ma va i ndegonjogha mun. Gharaghambu th…® mena evasiwae na th…® naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU variyeyathu wevoko, kaiwae i kulakula reghamba weinda.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi va i variyeŇčgo mbe wabwi Isirel eŇčge kaiwanji. Thiye Ňčgoranjiya sip ma e ghanjiranjimbunjimbu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 Elako i mena i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, u thalavuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 I gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae ra wo gamagai ghanji na ra wokiyathu weŇčgiya mbughambugha. Mbwata ma val…®kaiwae ya thalavuŇčge.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 Elama iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye amalana. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbughambugha th…® ghana ghan…®Ňčga murimuriye th…® dobu tanuwaganji ele ghamba ghan…®Ňčga raberabe. Iya kaiwae val…®kaiwae u thalavuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 Amba Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúElana, len loŇčweghath…®na i lagh…®ye. Kaero Ňčgoreiya len renuwaŇčana.‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako yawarumbuyema riwae i thovuye.   
\s1 Jisas i thawariŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo  
\p
\v 29 Jisas i iteta ghembako iyako na i Ňčgalai Galili Njigh…®niye ghadidiye. I voro e ou vwatae na i yaku.  
\v 30 Wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakamenawe, th…® bigimenaŇčgiya ghambweghambwera, thiye th…® kuvokuvo, maranji i kwaghe, ghenji na n…®manji i thar…®, thiye ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčanji na vavanava. Th…® bigiraweŇčgi Jisas e ghamwae na i thawariŇčgi.  
\v 31 Ghar…®ghar…®ma gharenji i yo lagh…®ye kaiwae th…® thuweya ghal…®Ňčanjima i thar…® kaero th…® utu, ghenji na n…®manji i thar…® riwanji i thovuye, kuvokuvo th…® loŇčga wagiyawe na maranji i kwaghe kaero th…® thuwe. Iya kaiwae th…® taraweŇča Isirel lenji Loi.   
\s1 Jisas i vaghan…®Ňčgiya ghar…®ghar…® po tausan  
\r (Mak 8:1-10)  
\p
\v 32 Jisas i kula vathaŇčgiya gharaghambu, amba iŇča, ‚ÄúGhareŇčgu i v…®r…® ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake kaiwanji, kaiwae mbaŇča mbaŇčato kaero ra yaku weindaŇčgi na kaero ma e ghanji. Ma nuwaŇčguiya ya variyenjoghaŇčgi mbe ŇčgamoŇčgamoinji eŇčge, ne iwaeŇčge ghare thavwathavwavo i nja weŇčgi e kamwath…® mborowa.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 Gharaghambu th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVanatherowoke; aŇčgane ra vaidiya ghan…®Ňčga i ghanagha na ra vaghan…®Ňčgiya wabwike lagh…®ye?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 34 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúBred mbumbuviye na weŇčga?‚ÄĚ Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbumbupir…® na borogi nanasiye umboviye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 35 I dage weŇčgiya wabwima na thiya yaku e thelauko vwatae,  
\v 36 amba i mbana bred…®ma mbumbupir…®ma na borogima, i vata ago weya Loi, i njiviyaviya na i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuma na thiye th…® giya weŇčgiya wabwima.  
\v 37 Taulagh…®ko thiya ghan…®Ňčga na val…®kaiwanji. Amba gharaghambuko th…® mban…®Ňčgiya meth…® ghan…®vareŇčgima na th…® mban vanjaraŇčgiya nambonambo Ňčgamwapir…®.  
\v 38 E ghan…®Ňčgako iyako t…®ne gh…®mogh…®moru lenji ghanaghanagha po tausan, ko wanakau na gamagai ma va th…® vaonaŇčgi.  
\v 39 Amba Jisas i variyeŇčgi na th…® raka. Amalagh…®niye i tha e waŇčga na i wa Magadan ele val…®vaŇčga.   
\c 16  
\s1 Parisi nuwanjiya Jisas le vakatha  
\r (Mak 8:11-13; Luk 12:54-56)  
\p
\v 1 Parisi na Sadusi vavana th…® mena weya Jisas na nuwanjiya th…® mando. Amba th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo u vakatha vakatha ghamba rotaele regha na mbala i vaemunjoruŇča emunjoru Loi le vur…®gheghe ina e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 2 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča varaeko ve ronja, kaero huŇča, ‚ÄėEvole mara thovuye kaiwae buruburuko i soro,‚Äô  
\v 3 na mbaŇčambaŇča moli huŇča, ‚ÄėNoroke i uye kaiwae buruburuko i soro na i bwedi.‚Äô Val…®kaiwae mbema hu thuweŇčge buruburuko ghayamoyamo kaero hu ghareghare budakai ne i yomara, ko iyemaeŇčge ma val…®kaiwami hu vamanjamanjalaŇča budakai th…® yoyomara e mbaŇčake iyake.  
\v 4 Ghemi thake iyake raraithar…® ghemi, na hu roiteta Loi ghathanavu. Nuwamiya ya vakatha nono ghamba rotaele kaiwami. Ko mane ya vakatha nono regha kaiwami. Nono ghamba rotaele mbe iyaeŇčge Loi ne i giya weŇčga, iyava i vakatha weya Jona.‚ÄĚ Jisas i iteteŇčaŇčgi na i wa.   
\s1 Jisas i utu vavur…®gheghe weŇčgi gharaghambu  //  Parisi na Sadusi lenji vavaghare kaiwae  
\r (Mak 8:14-21)  
\p
\v 5 Vama inanji val…®mbwa, ko gharaghambu va th…® renuwaŇča vaghalawe, ma va th…® bigiya bred.  
\v 6 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njimbukiki wagiyawe! Hu njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčga Parisi na Sadusi lenji is…®t kaiwae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Gharaghambu th…® veutu weŇčgi, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMeŇča Ňčgoraiyako kaiwae ma mara ndewo mun bred.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Jisas vama i ghareghareya lenji utuko amba i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúLemi loŇčweghath…®na ma i lagh…®ye! Buda kaiwae hu veutu weŇčga bred kaiwae?  
\v 9 Ko nuwamina mamba i rumwaru? Thare hu renuwaŇčakiki bred…®ma mbumbulima, va ya njiviyaviya na gh…®mogh…®moru paeb tausan th…® ghan, na th…® ghan…®vareŇčgi e nambonambo Ňčgamwaviye hu mban…®vanjaraŇčgi?  
\v 10 Na thare hu renuwaŇčakikiya bred…®ma mbumbupir…®ma, va ya njiviyaviya na po tausan gh…®mogh…®moru th…® ghan, na th…® ghan…®vareŇčgi e nambonambo Ňčgamwaviye hu mban…®vanjaraŇčgi?  
\v 11 ŇägoroŇčgaeŇčge na ma nuwamina i rumwaruŇča, ghino ma, ma utuutu weŇčga bred kaiwae? Hu njimbukikiŇčga Parisi na Sadusi lenji is…®t kaiwae!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Gharaghambu ambama nuwanji i rumwaru Jisas ma iŇča th…® njimbukikiŇčgi bred ghais…®t kaiwae, ko iŇča eŇčge th…® njimbukikiŇčgi Parisi na Sadusi lenji vavaghare kaiwae.   
\s1 Pita iŇča Jisas iye Mesaiya  
\r (Mak 8:27-30; Luk 9:18-21)  
\p
\v 13 MbaŇča Jisas i wa Sisariya Pilipai ele val…®vaŇčga amba i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča thela Lolo Nariye?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Th…® gonjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVavana th…®Ňča Jon Rabap…®taiso, vavana th…®Ňča Ilaija, na vavana th…®Ňča Jeremaiya o Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu regha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 I vaitoŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúKo naka ghemi? HuŇča thela ghino?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Saimon Pita i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Krais ghen, Loi e yawayawaliye Nariye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi i mwaewo weŇčge, Saimon Jona nariye! Kaiwae renuwaŇčana iyana ma i mena weya rameyambaneke regha, Bwebwe e buruburu i woveŇčge.  
\v 18 Ya dage weŇčge, ghen Pita, na e var…®ke iyake vwatae ya vatada lo ekelesiya wabwi na Seitan le wabwi ma e lenji vur…®gheghe na ne th…® kivwala.  
\v 19 Ya th…®n…®giya Loi le ghamba mbaro gheki e ghen na e len vur…®gheghe. The vakatha ne u dageten e yambaneke Loi ne i dageten e buruburu, na the vakatha ne u vatomwe e yambaneke Loi ne i vatomwe e buruburu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Amba i dage vavur…®gheghe weŇčgiya gharaghambu na thava th…® utugiya weya lolo regha na th…®Ňča iye Krais.   
\s1 Jisas i vaghareŇčgi le mare kaiwae  
\r (Mak 8:31‚Äď9:1; Luk 9:22-27)  
\p
\v 21 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i utukai vara weŇčgiya gharaghambu iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ya wa Jerusalem na randeviva, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® vakatha vuyowo lagh…®ye e ghino. Ne th…® vakathaŇčgo na ya mare na mbaŇča theghetoninji e t…®ne kaero ya thuweiruva.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Pita i vaŇčgwa Jisas na mbe thiye eŇčge amba i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, Loi thava i vatomwe na Ňčgoreiye! Bigike iyake thava ne i yomara e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Jisas i ndevagh…®le na i dage weya Pita, iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena e ghereiŇčguke, Seitan! Ghen Ňčgorana ghamba thalat…®va e ghino, len renuwaŇčana ma i reŇča Loi ele renuwaŇča, i reŇča ghar…®ghar…® e lenji renuwaŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu, iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo thela nuwaiya i ghambuŇčgo, tembe ghamberegha i botewo iya nuwaeko nuwaiya i vakatha na i wovaira ghakros na i wo na i ghambuŇčgo.  
\v 25 Iya kaiwae thela tembe ghamberegha nuwaiya i vamora yawaliye, ne i th…®vaghawa yawaliye, na thela ne i th…®vaghawa yawaliye ghino kaiwaŇčgu ne i vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye.  
\v 26 ŇägoroŇčga ghathovuye thoŇčgo lolo regha i wo yambaneke lagh…®ye na i mbaroŇča, ko iyemaeŇčge i th…®vaiya yawal…® memeghabananiye? Ne i wo budakai na i vamodanjogha yawaliyekowe?  
\v 27 Kaiwae Lolo Nariye ne i mena weiye Ramae le vur…®gheghe, weiyaŇčgiya le Nyao Thovuthovuye, na i vamodo lolo regha na regha Ňčgoreiya le kaiwo.  
\v 28 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, ghar…®ghar…® vavana inanji gheke thiye wo ne th…® thuweya Lolo Nariye i mena weiye le mbaro e yambaneke amba muyai th…® mare.‚ÄĚ   
\c 17  
\s1 Jisas ghayamoyamo i ghenevaghagh…®le  
\r (Mak 9:2-13; Luk 9:28-36)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča theghewona e ghereiye Jisas i vaŇčguŇčgiya Pita, Jemes na ghaghae Jon, i viva weŇčgi na th…® voro e ou molao regha mbe thiye eŇčge vara.  
\v 2 E maranji Jisas ghayamoyamo i ghenevagh…®le, ghamwae i ndalandala Ňčgoreiye varae mara mbouye na ghakwama kakaleva na marambwelambwelawae.  
\v 3 Amba Mosese na Ilaija th…® yomara na th…® thuweŇčgi e maranji th…® utu weinji Jisas.  
\v 4 Pita i dagewe Jisas, iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, i thovuye inanda gheke! ThoŇčgo nuwaniya ne ya vatada yoŇčathowathowa Ňčgoloto gheke, Ňčgolora ghen, Ňčgolora Mosese, na Ňčgolora Ilaija.‚ÄĚ\fig Jisas i utu weiyaŇčgiya Mosese na Ilaija|alt="Jesus at transfig with Moses and Elijah" src="IB04115bw.tif" size="col" copy="Faadil" ref="17:1-4" \fig*   
\p
\v 5 MbaŇča i utuutu Ňčgal…®l…® marambwelambwelawae i ghavo tomuŇčgi na Loi i dage e Ňčgal…®l…®ko, iŇča, ‚ÄúIyake NaruŇčgu val…®ghareghareŇčgu, i vakathaŇčgo ya warari lagh…®ye moli. Hu vandeŇče wagiyawe!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 MbaŇča gharaghambuko thenjighetoko th…® loŇčweya ghal…®ghal…®Ňčako th…® mararu lagh…®ye moli, th…® dobu na ghamwanji i nja e thelauko vwatae.  
\v 7 Jisas i mena weŇčgi i v…®ghath…®Ňčgi na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu thuweiru, tha hu mararu!‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Th…® gh…®mara voro na ma th…® vaidi eŇčge Jisas ghamberegha.   
\p
\v 9 Jisas na gharaghambuma thenjighetoma th…® njama e ouko, i dage vur…®gheghe weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbala hu ravunyivunyiya bigiko mohu thuwe e ouko vwatae. Ne hu utuŇča weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thembaŇča Lolo Nariye ne le mare na le thuweiru e ghereiye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Amba gharaghambu th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mbaro gharavavaghareŇčgi th…®Ňčava Ilaija ne i menakai amba muyai Mesaiya i mena?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru Ilaija ne i menakai na i vanamwe bigibigike wolagh…®ye.  
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge, ya dage e ghemi, Ilaija kaero mendava i mena na mava th…® ghareghare thela amalagh…®niye, ko va th…® vakatha thambo renuwaŇča nuwanjiya th…® vakathawe. Tembene th…® vakathava v…®r…® Ňčgoreiyako e ghino, Lolo Nariye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Amba gharaghambu nuwanji i manjamanjala na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKo ana me utuuta Jon Rabap…®taiso utuniye iya meŇčake, ‚ÄėIlaija kaero mendava i mena.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariya thegha regha nyao raithar…® inawe  
\r (Mak 9:14-29; Luk 9:37-43)  
\p
\v 14 MbaŇča th…® njogha weŇčgiya wabwima lagh…®ye, amba amala regha i mena weya Jisas, i ronja e ghe vuvuye e ghamwae  
\v 15 na iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, u gharev…®r…® naruŇčguko kaiwae, kaiwae umbaliye e ghagida na mbaŇča i ghanagha maramara th…® ndeghath…® na i dobu e nd…®ghe une o e mbwa t…®ne na i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 16 Ma vaŇčgumena weŇčgiya ghan…®raghambuke, ko ma val…®kaiwanji meth…® thawari.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi thake iyake ma e lemi loŇčweghath…® na ghamithanavu raraithar…®. ŇägoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao ne ya yaku weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi? ŇägoroŇčga mbaŇča le molamolao ne ya ghataŇčaghath…®Ňčga? Hu vaŇčgumena weŇčgo!‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Jisas i dage vur…®gheghe weya nyaoma raithar…® na i raŇčgi weya theghama, na e mbaŇčako iyako riwae i thovuye.   
\p
\v 19 Amba gharaghambu mbe th…®ye eŇčge th…® menawe na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghime ma me val…®kaiwame wo dagewe nyaoko raithar…® na i raŇčgi?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae lemi loŇčweghath…®na ma i lagh…®ye. Ya dage emunjoru weŇčga, thoŇčgo e lemi loŇčweghath…®, othembe nasiye moli Ňčgoreiya umbwama mas…®ted…®ma mbouye\f + \fr 17:20 \ft Mas…®tedke iyake ghar…®ghar…® th…® kabu e lenji uma na th…® vakaiwoŇča kaiwae i giya ghaniŇčga gham…®nae thovuye, Ňčgoreiye th…® vakaiwoŇča njigh…®. Iyake ma ndiya th…® ghawi weiye gh…®leth…®.\f*, val…®kaiwami hu dage weya ouke iyake, ‚ÄėU roiteta ghambana u wa gheko,‚Äô ne i vakatha Ňčgoreiye. ThoŇčgo e lemi loŇčweghath…® ma bigi regha ne i vuyowo weŇčga.  
\v 21 Ko nyao raithar…® Ňčgorako mane i raŇčgi bwaga, mbene ra naŇčgo na ra ghataŇčaghath…®gha bada naŇčgoko kaiwae ambane Ňčgoreiye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas mbowo i utuŇčava le mare utuutuniye  
\r (Mak 9:30-32; Luk 9:43b-45)  
\p
\v 22 MbaŇča gharaghambu th…® mevathavatha Galili amba Jisas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča nasiye th…® vaŇčguraweya Lolo Nariye ghar…®ghar…® e n…®manji,  
\v 23 na th…® tagavamare, ko mbaŇča theghetoniye e t…®ne kaero i thuweiruva.‚ÄĚ Gharaghambu va th…® loŇčweya iyako nuwanji i thar…® lagh…®ye.   
\s1 Ňägolo Boboma ghatakis kaiwae  
\p
\v 24 MbaŇča vama th…® mena Kapenaom, Ňägolo Boboma ghatakis gharamban th…® mena th…® vaito Pita, ‚ÄúLemi Ravavagharena thare i vamodo takis Ňägolo Boboma kaiwae?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 Pita iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye.‚ÄĚ  
\p MbaŇča Pita ve ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne, Jisas i dagekaiwe iŇča, ‚ÄúSaimon, ŇčgoroŇčga len renuwaŇča? MbaŇča yambaneke ghakiŇč th…® mbana takis, ŇčgoroŇčga th…® mban weŇčgiya onanarinji o ghar…®ghar…® ma lenji bodaboda weŇčgi?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 Pita iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…® ma lenji bodaboda weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúOnanarinji mane th…® vamodo takis. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ghino mbala mbe ma ya vamodova Bwebwe le Ňčgolo ghatakis.  
\v 27 Ko ma nuwandaiya ra vakatha Ňägolo Boboma ghatakis gharamban na gharenji i gaith…® weinda, ma u wa eŇčge e njigh…® na vo liyathu len thiyo. The borogiya u kosikai vara, u wo na u tate ghaena na u vaidiya mani, i ghanagha na ne val…®kaiwae ghen na ghino la takis Ňägolo Boboma kaiwae. U mban na vo vamodowe.‚ÄĚ   
\c 18  
\s1 Thela idae i lagh…®ye Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne  
\r (Mak 9:33-37; Luk 9:46-48)  
\p
\v 1 Va e mbaŇčako iyako Jisas gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThela idae i lagh…®ye Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 2 I kula weya Ňčgama nasiye regha na i ndeghath…® gharaghambu e t…®nenji,  
\v 3 amba iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, thoŇčgo ma hu v…®va ghamithanavu na Ňčgoramiya Ňčgama nasiye, mane vohu ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 4 Thela thoŇčgo ghathanavu i ghenenja Ňčgoreiya Ňčgamake iyake, iye idae i lagh…®ye Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 5 Na thela thoŇčgo i kulavatha Ňčgama regha Ňčgora iyake e idaŇčgu, Ňčgoreiya i kulavathaŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Tanathetha i vaŇčgwa lolo na i vakatha thar…®  
\r (Mak 9:42-48)  
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ra wo var…® lagh…®ye na ra Ňčgara loloko iyako e numwe na ra wokiyathu e Ňčambuwoko t…®ne, lith…®ko iyako i lagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi ne i giya lolo regha ghalith…® i lagh…®ye moli thoŇčgo i vakatha Ňčgama Ňčgoreiyake regha i vakatha thar…® na ma i loŇčweghath…®Ňčgo.  
\v 7 O, yambane! Yambaneke i thar…® kaiwae bigibigi lemoyo inanji e yambaneke i vakathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha thar…®. Emunjoru bigibigike thiyake th…® yoyomara, ko loloko iya i vakathaŇčgi na th…® yoyomarako Loi ne i lith…®we lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo gheghen…®na o n…®man…®na i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u kiten…®yathu. I thovuye eŇčge thoŇčgo ma e gheghen na n…®man…®man na u vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye. Thava n…®man…®man…®na theghewona na gheghen…®na theghewona th…® wokiyathuruwoŇčge e nd…®gheko iya i meghabanako e t…®ne.  
\v 9 Na thoŇčgo maran…®na regha i vakathaŇčge na u vakatha thar…®, u vovavuthuyathu na u wokiyathu. I thovuye moli maran mbe vogh…®ra eŇčge na u vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye, na thava maramaran…®na vogh…®wona th…® wokiyathuruwoŇčge Gehena, iya nd…®ghe memeghabananiye e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Sip regha i ghawe utuniye  
\r (Luk 15:1-7)  
\p
\v 10 ‚ÄúHu njimbukikiŇčga, tha hu njimbunjoŇčanjoŇčaŇčgiya gamagai Ňčgoreiye reghake iyake. Ya dage e ghemi lenji nyao thovuthovuye e buruburu, mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye thiya yaku Bwebwe e ghamwae e buruburu.  
\v 11 Lolo Nariya Ghino ya mena ya vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thiya ghawe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga lemi renuwaŇča? ThoŇčgo lolo regha ele sip hothaŇčar…® na regha i ghawe, ne i vakatha budakai? Ne i iteteŇčgiya iyesiwo na umbosiwo e ou vwatae na i wa ve tamweya iya me ghaweko.  
\v 13 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, mbaŇča ne i vaidi, le warari i lagh…®ye moli i kivwala le warari iyesiwo na umbosiwo kaiwanji iya ma th…® ghaweko.  
\v 14 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Ramami e buruburu ma le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiya nanasiyeke Ňčgoranjiyake regha i ghawe.‚ÄĚ\fig Sip i ghawe|alt="The lost lamb" src="bk00005c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Knowles-Bass)" ref="18:12-14" \fig*   
\s1 U thalavu ghaghan i vakatha thar…® weŇčge  
\p
\v 15 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ghagha i vakatha thanavu raithar…® e ghen, u wawe na mbe themighewona eŇčge, na u woraŇčgiya le thar…®na. ThoŇčgo i wovatha len utuna, kaero ghamwami vanaorava wein.  
\v 16 Ko thoŇčgo ma i wovatha ghal…®Ňčana, u vaŇčgwa lolo reghava o theghewo, weinaŇčgi, mbala the bigibigi u woraŇčgiyawe themighewoko o themigheto hu vaemunjoruŇča, iyake Ňčgoreiya Mosese le Mbaro i woraŇčgiya weinda.\x - \xo 18:16 \xt Mba 19:15\x*  
\v 17 ThoŇčgo ma i goru weya ghal…®Ňčanji, u wa vo woraŇčgiya weŇčgiya ekelesiya, na thoŇčgo ma i wovatha ekelesiya lenji renuwaŇča, hu vakathawe Ňčgoreiya iye lolo raithar…® o takis gharamban regha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, the vakatha ne hu dageten e yambaneke Loi ne i dageten e buruburu, na the vakatha ne hu vatomwe e yambaneke Loi ne i vatomwe e buruburu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 ‚ÄúMbowo ya dageva e ghemi, e yambaneke thoŇčgo themighewo lemi renuwaŇča regha na hu naŇčgo bigi regha kaiwae, Bwebwe e buruburu ne i vakatha kaiwami.  
\v 20 Kaiwae thoŇčgo themighewo o themigheto hu mevathavatha e idaŇčgu, ghino mbe inaŇčguwe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ra nuwoyathu ghandau le thar…® utuniye  
\p
\v 21 Amba Pita i mena weya Jisas na i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, thoŇčgo ghaghaŇčgu i vakatha thar…® e ghino, mbaŇčaviye ne ya nuwoyathu le thar…®ko? Mbe mbaŇčapir…® eŇčge?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúThava mbe mbaŇčapir…® eŇčge, mbaŇčathaŇčar…® na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgora iyake: KiŇč regha va nuwaiya i tamweya le rakakaiwo ghanjighaga.  
\v 24 MbaŇča i woraweya le tamweko r…®ghe, th…® vaŇčgumena gh…®moru reghawe, gheghaga i lagh…®ye moli Ňčgoreiya miliyon Kina.  
\v 25 Ma va val…®kaiwae i vamodo, ghagiyama iŇča na amalagh…®niye, levo na le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, th…® vavakuneŇčaŇčgi na th…® tabo na rakakaiwobwaga, i mbana maniko na i vamodo gheghagakowe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúRakakaiwoma i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na i naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe iŇča, ‚ÄėU ghataŇčaghath…® na wo u roroghagha, tene ya vamodonjoghavao.‚Äô  
\v 27 Ghagiyama i gharev…®r…® kaiwae amba i rakayathu gheghagama na i dagewe ma tene i vamodova.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúKo mbaŇča rakakaiwoko iyako i raŇčgi, i vaidiya mbe le val…®rakakaiwo reghava. Va i ghaga weya amalagh…®niye, iya me raŇčgima, ko mava i lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Kina gh…®viyeŇčge. I yalawe e numwe na iŇča, ‚ÄėU vamodo manina va u ghagana weŇčgo!‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúLe val…®rakakaiwoma i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na i naŇčgo vur…®gheghewe iŇča, ‚ÄėU ghataŇčaghath…® na wo u roroghagha, tene ya vamodonjoghavao.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 30 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge va i botewo na iŇča na th…® vaŇčguruwo e thiyo gheghada i vamodo ghaghagako.  
\v 31 Rakakaiwoma vavanava th…® thuweya ghanjiuko le vakatha weya gheuko na nuwanji i thar…® lagh…®ye kaiwae. Th…® wa weya giyama na veth…® utugiya bigibigiko wolagh…®yewe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 32 ‚ÄúAmba ghanjigiyama i kula ruwo rakaiwoma na iŇča, ‚ÄėGhen rakakaiwo raithara ghen. Ghan…®ghagama wolagh…®ye e ghino kaero ya nuwoyathu Ňčgoreiya me len naŇčgo ma e ghino.  
\v 33 Mbala gharen me nja weya ghanuna Ňčgoreiya ghino, ghareŇčgu me njaweŇčge.‚Äô  
\v 34 Ghagiyama ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye, i vaŇčgugiya na ve yaku e thiyo gheghada i vamodavao gheghagako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 35 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe e buruburu ne i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako weŇčga, taulagh…®na ghemi, thoŇčgo ma hu numoyathuŇčgiya ghamunena lenji thar…® e gharemina.‚ÄĚ   
\c 19  
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča ghe na yawo utuniye  
\r (Mak 10:1-12)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Jisas i utuvao utuutuke thiyake, i iteta Galili le val…®vaŇčga na i wa Judiya ele val…®vaŇčga, e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro.  
\v 2 Wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakambele na i thawariŇčgiya ghambweghambwera e wabwiko iyako t…®ne.   
\p
\v 3 Parisi vavana th…® menawe na th…® munjeva th…® mando, th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare la mbaro i vatomwe na val…®kaiwae lolo regha i yawo weiye levo na r…®ghe mbe amalagh…®niye i ghareghare?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe hu vaona Buk Boboma iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėVa i rikowe Ravakavakatha i vakathaŇčgiya gh…®moru na wevo.‚Äô\x - \xo 19:4 \xt R…®gh 1:27\x*  
\v 5 Tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄėIyake kaiwae gh…®moru i iteteŇčgiya ramae na t…®nae, i tubwe weiye levo, na thenjighewoko Ňčgoranjiya ririwo regha.‚Äô\x - \xo 19:5 \xt R…®gh 2:24\x*  
\v 6 Ma meth…® tabona ghar…®ghar…® thenjighewo, nandere. Kaero th…® tabona ririwo regha. Iya kaiwae budakaiya Loi vama i tubwe, thava te lolo reghava i rakayathu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Parisi mbowo th…® vaitova, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhen mo utuna Ňčgorana, buda kaiwae eŇčge Mosese va i woraweya mbaro, thoŇčgo gh…®moru nuwaiya i botewo levo, wo i vakathakaiya botewo ghapeipa na i ligiya weya levo, amba muyai i variyeyathu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 19:7 \xt Mba 24:1\x*   
\p
\v 8 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi, iŇča ‚ÄúMosese va i vatomweya yawo kaiwae gharemi i vur…®gheghe. Ko va i rikowe ma va Ňčgoreiye.  
\v 9 Ya dage e ghemi, thoŇčgo lolo regha i yawo weiye levo, othembe wevoko ma i yathima, na kaero i vaŇčguva wevo togha, amalagh…®niye i yathima.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Gharaghambu th…® dagewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ghe ghambaro Ňčgoreiyako, i thovuye moli thava ra ghe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Jisas i dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄúLemi renuwaŇčana iyena ma ghar…®ghar…®ke taulagh…® kaiwanji, ko mbe iyaeŇčge thavala Loi kaero i giya weŇčgi.  
\v 12 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana ma val…®kaiwae th…® ghe kaiwae vambe th…® vir…®ghamb…®. Vavana ma th…® ghe kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakathaŇčgi na ma val…®kaiwanji. Vavana ma th…® ghe kaiwae tembe ghanjimberegha th…® dageten…®Ňčgi Loi le ghamba mbaro kaiwae. Thela thoŇčgo val…®kaiwae i wo renuwaŇčake iyake, amba i wo.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas ghare weŇčgiya gamagai  
\r (Mak 10:13-16; Luk 18:15-17)  
\p
\v 13 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® bigimenaŇčgiya gamagai weya Jisas, na i bigirawe n…®man…®mae weŇčgi na i naŇčgo kaiwanji, ko iyemaeŇčge gharaghambu th…® Ňčael…®mbiya weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko.  
\v 14 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vatomweŇčgiya gamagai na th…® rakamena weŇčgo, thava hu dageten…®Ňčgi, kaiwae Loi le ghamba mbaro ina weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoranjiya thiyena.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 I bigirawe n…®man…®mae e riwanji na i naŇčgo weya Ramae ghare weŇčgi amba i iteta ghembako iyako.   
\s1 Ravwenyevwenye regha i vaito Jisas  
\r (Mak 10:17-31; Luk 18:18-30)  
\p
\v 16 MbaŇča regha amala regha i mena weya Jisas na i vaito, iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, thambo vakatha thovuye ne ya vakatha na ya vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Jisas i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae u vaitoŇčgo thovuye kaiwae? Mbe lolo reghaeŇčge vara iye i thovuye. ThoŇčgo nuwaniya u vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye, u ghambuŇčgiya Loi le mbaro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 Amalama i vaito, iŇča, ‚ÄúThe mbaroŇčgi?‚ÄĚ Jisas i gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u gabo, tha u yathima, tha u kaiv…®, tha u wonjowe bwagabwaga,  
\v 19 u yavwatata wanaŇčgiya rama na t…®na,\x - \xo 19:19 \xt RaŇč 20:12-16; Mba 5:16-20; Liv 19:18\x* na u gharethovu weya ghanu Ňčgoreiya u gharethovu e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Amalama i dagewe, ‚ÄúMbaroŇčgike wolagh…®ye thiyake kaero ya ghambuvaoŇčgi. Budakai mbowo i kwarava e ghino?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Jisas i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo nuwaniya u rumwaru moli, u wa vo vakuneŇčaŇčgiya len bigibigina, u giya manina weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu; amba ne u vwenyevwenye e buruburu, na u mena u ghambuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 MbaŇča i loŇčweya utuko iyako, i wa weiye le nuwathar…® lagh…®ye, kaiwae le gogomwau i lagh…®ye moli.   
\p
\v 23 Jisas i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu, iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, ravwenyevwenye le ru ne i vuyowo Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.  
\v 24 Mbowo ya dageva e ghemi, i vuyowo moli weya kamel na i komughathara e nyil…® yathiye, ko i vuyowo lagh…®ye moli weya ravwenyevwenye le ru Loi ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 MbaŇča gharaghambuko th…® loŇčweya iyake, gharenji i yo lagh…®ye moli na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThela eŇčge ne i vaidiya vamoru?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 Jisas i vonjimbughath…®Ňčgi na iŇča, ‚ÄúIyake, ghar…®ghar…® ma val…®kaiwanji, ko Loi iye val…®kaiwae bigibigike wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 Pita i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, wo iteteŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye na wo ghambuŇčge. Budakai ne ina gheko kaiwame?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi ne e yambane togha, mbaŇča Lolo Nariye ne i yaku ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye ghemi woraghambu themiyaworo na themighewona, ne hu yaku e ghamba yaku theyaworo na theghewo na hu mbaroŇčgiya uu theyaworo na theghewo Isirel e t…®ne.  
\v 29 Na thela i iteta le Ňčgolo, oghaghae, oloulouye, ramae, t…®nae, le ŇčgaŇčga, na le thelau idaŇčgu kaiwae, ne i vaidiya bigibigiko thiyako lagh…®ye moli na e vwataeva, na i vaidiya yawal…® memeghabananiye.  
\v 30 Ko thavala noroke th…® lagh…®ye na th…® viva ne th…® muyai na thavala noroke th…® nasiye na th…® muyai ne th…® viva.‚ÄĚ   
\c 20  
\s1 Waen ghauma gharakakaiwo ghagoghaimba  
\p
\v 1 Loi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiyake. Amala regha, vambe mbaŇčambaŇča ma i raŇčgi na i tamweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, i naŇčgoŇčgi na th…® kaiwo ele waen…®ko ghanjiuma.  
\v 2 Amalama iŇča ne i vamodaŇčgi Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča regha modae, silva geth…®ra. Ghar…®ghar…®ma lenji renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye amba i variyeŇčgi waen…®ma e ghauma t…®ne.   
\p
\v 3 MbaŇča ghalughawoghawo Ňčgoreiya naen klok amalama mbowo i raŇčgiva, i wa e ghamba maket. I vaidiŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana thiya yaku bwaga ma e ghanjikaiwo,  
\v 4 i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi Ňčgoreiye, vou kaiwo elo waen…®ko ghanjiuma. Ne ya vamodo wagiyaweŇčga Ňčgoreiya renuwaŇča iŇča na mane ya vakatha vathar…® weŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Kaero th…® wa.  
\p Ghararagh…®ye mboro na t…®ri klok i wa na tembe ve vakatha va Ňčgoreiye.  
\v 6 Mbala vama i wo paeb klok, amalama mbowo i wava e ghamba maket…®ma na ve vaidiŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® ndendeghath…®. I vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae huya ndeghath…® ghena? MbaŇčake lagh…®ye mohuya ndebwagabwaga moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Th…® gonjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKaiwae ma lolo regha me giya kaiwo weime.‚ÄĚ  
\p I dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄúHu wa na vou kaiwo elo waen…®ko ghanjiuma.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Vama yegh…®yegh…®ye moli amba umama tanuwagae i dage weya rakakaiwoko ghanjiranjimbunjimbu iŇča, ‚ÄúU kula weŇčgiya rakakaiwoko na u giya modanji. U giyakai weŇčgiya ma kula reghambama na vo giyavun weŇčgiya ma kulakaiŇčgima.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Thiye meth…® kaiwo reghambama, Ňčgoreiya paeb klok ele val…®vaŇčga, th…® mena na i giya modanji Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča regha modae, silva geth…®ra iya.  
\v 10 MbaŇča thiyema meth…® kaiwokaima th…® mena, th…® munjeva ne modanji i divoro, ko iyemaeŇčge th…® mban tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mbaŇča regha modae, silva geth…®ra iya lolo regha.  
\v 11 MbaŇča th…® mbana modanji, th…® liya umama tanuwagae ghautu,  
\v 12 th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke iya mo vaŇčguŇčgike muyai, meth…® kaiwo mbaŇča ubotu moli na mo giya modanji mboromboro weimaŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge ghime mo vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye, mo vakatha mbaŇča regha ghakaiwo na wo ghataŇčaghath…®gha varae le vur…®gheghe weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Ko umama tanuwagae i dage weya ghanjiu regha iŇča, ‚ÄúWou, ma ma vakatha vathar…® e ghen. Mo warariŇča u kaiwo mbaŇča regha na modan silva geth…®ra.  
\v 14 U mbana modana na u wa. NuwaŇčguiya ya giya loloke iya ma vaŇčgureghambake modae mboromboro weiye ma giyana e ghen.  
\v 15 Ko ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu wombereghake ya vakatha lo manike Ňčgoreiya lo renuwaŇčake? Ma val…®kaiwae u yamwanja kaiwae ghino ya mwaewo weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Iya kaiwae Jisas i govun, iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala noroke th…® viva ne th…® rereghamba na thavala noroke th…® rereghamba ne th…® viva.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča le mare utuniye mbaŇčatoniye  
\r (Mak 10:32-34; Luk 18:31-34)  
\p
\v 17 Jisas i loŇčgaloŇčga Jerusalem kaiwae, i vaŇčguŇčgiya gharaghambu na mbe thiye eŇčge na i layo utuutu weŇčgi iŇča,  
\v 18 ‚ÄúKaero ra loŇčgaloŇčga Jerusalem kaiwae, na gheko ne th…® vaŇčgugiya Lolo Nariye weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare. Ne th…® vakatha ghambaro na i mare,  
\v 19 na th…® vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya thiye ma Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® utuvathar…® kaiwae, th…® yab…®b…® na th…® Ňčge e kros vwatae. Ko mbaŇča ne theghetoniye e t…®ne kaero i thuweiru na ma e yawayawaliyeva.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jemes na Jon t…®nanji i naŇčgo weya Jisas  //  lenji ghamba yaku kaiwae  
\r (Mak 10:35-45)  
\p
\v 20 Amba Sebedi le ŇčgaŇčgama thenjighewoma t…®nanji i mena weya Jisas weiyaŇčgi, i ronja e gheghe vuvuye e ghamwae na i naŇčgowe.   
\p
\v 21 Jisas i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaniya budakai?‚ÄĚ  
\p IŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguiya u dagerawe e ghino, mbaŇča ne inan e len ghamba mbaro t…®ne, lo ŇčgaŇčgake thenjighewoke thiyake; regha ne i yaku e unena na regha e moina.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Jisas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúMa hu ghareghare, hu naŇčgo weya budakai. Val…®kaiwami ne hu mun e v…®r…®ke ghakom iya ghino ne ya mun…®kewe?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…® gonjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, val…®kaiwame eŇčge.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 I dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru, tene hu mun e wokomuke, ko ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu yaŇča thela i yaku e uneŇčguke na thela e moiŇčguke. Ghamba yakuke thiyake Bwebwe va i vivatharawe, thavala i tuthiŇčgi kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 MbaŇča gharaghambuma theyaworoma th…® loŇčweya iyake gharenji i gaith…®wanaŇčgiya ghewoko na ghaghae.  
\v 25 Jisas i kula vathaŇčgi, mbema taulagh…®ko vara na iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare, thiye ma Jiu lenji rambarombaro th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgi na lenji randeviva lenji vur…®gheghe i varinjoŇčaŇčgi.  
\v 26 Ko ghemi, thava Ňčgoramiya iyako. Thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya iye lolo lagh…®ye e t…®nemina, iye wo i tabo na lemi rakakaiwo.  
\v 27 Thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i ndeviva weŇčga wo i tabo na lemi rakakaiwobwaga,  
\v 28 Ňčgoreiya Lolo Nariye, mava i mena na mbala th…® kaiwo kaiwae, ko i mena na i kaiwo ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji na i vatomwe yawaliye i vamodonjoghaŇčgi e lenji thar…® t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i thawariya ghar…®ghar…® thenjighewo maranji i kwaghe  
\r (Mak 10:46-52; Luk 18:35-43)  
\p
\v 29 MbaŇča Jisas na gharaghambu th…® iteta Jeriko, wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rakareghamba weŇčgi.  
\v 30 E mbaŇčako iyako, ghar…®ghar…® thenjighewo, maranji i kwaghe, th…® yaku e kamwath…®ko ghadidiye. MbaŇča th…® loŇčweya Jisas i mena na ma i vaiteteŇčgi, th…® kula th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, Deivid Rumbuye, gharen i nja weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 31 Wabwima th…® ŇčaevwaŇčaŇčgi na th…® dage weŇčgi th…® rokubaro. Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® kula na ghal…®Ňčanji ma lagh…®ye eŇčge, ‚ÄúAmalana, Deivid Rumbuye, gharen i nja weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 32 Jisas i ndeghath…® na i kula weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwamiya ya vakatha budakai kaiwami?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 Th…® gonjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, nuwameiya u vakatha maramarameke th…® thovuye na kaero wo thuweva.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 34 Jisas ghare i nja weŇčgi na i v…®ghath…®gha maramaranji. E mbaŇčako iyako kaero th…® thuweva na th…® ghambu.   
\c 21  
\s1 Jisas i ru Jerusalem  
\r (Mak 11:1-11; Luk 19:28-40; Jon 12:12-19)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas na gharaghambu vama th…® vur…®thaiya Jerusalem, th…® mena Betepage, Oliv…® ghanji Ou ghembaniye regha; amba i variyeŇčgiya gharaghambu thenjighewo e ghamwanji,  
\v 2 iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa na vou ru e ghembana e ghamwamina. Ne hu thuweya doŇč…®ki regha th…® Ňčgar…®ghath…® weiye nariye. Hu raka ghathiyona na hu vaŇčguma weiye nariyena.  
\v 3 ThoŇčgo lolo regha i vaitoŇčga, hu dagewe huŇča, ‚ÄėGiya nuwaiya,‚Äô na tene i variyeŇčgi e mbaŇčako iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Iyake va i yomara na i vaemunjoruŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu ghal…®Ňčae iya iŇčake:   
\q1
\v 5 Hu giya Saiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye yanawanji:\x - \xo 21:5 \xt Ais 62:11; Sak 9:9\x*  
\q2 Wo hu thuwe, lemi kiŇč maiya i ghaona weŇčga.  
\q1 Iye ghathanavu i ghenenja, i tha e doŇč…®ki, i tha doŇč…®ki nariye e vwatae.   
\p
\v 6 Gharaghambuma th…® wa na veth…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya me dagema weŇčgi.  
\v 7 Th…® vaŇčgumenaŇčgiya doŇč…®kima na nariye, th…® bigiraweya ghanjikwama ghayaboyabo nariye e vwatae na Jisas i tha.  
\v 8 Wabwi lagh…®ye th…® tateŇčgiya ghanjikwama e kamwath…®ko mara na vavana th…® ten…®Ňčgiya umbwaumbwa ndamwandamwae na th…® bigirawe.  
\v 9 Ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava th…® rakavivako na thiyeko iyava th…® rakareghambako th…® kula, th…®Ňča:  
\q1 Hosana! Ra taraweŇča Deivid Rumbuye!  
\q1 Loi gharewe iya i mena Giya e idae!  
\q1 Hosana! Ra taraweŇča Loi, iye i mevoro moli!\x - \xo 21:9 \xt Sam 118:25-26; 148:1\x*   
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča Jisas i ru Jerusalem, ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye gharenji i tagath…®n na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThelako?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Wabwima th…® gonjogha weŇčgi, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLoi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Jisas, i mena Nasaret, Galili ghembaniye regha.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i ru e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne  
\r (Mak 11:15-19; Luk 19:45-48; Jon 2:13-22)  
\p
\v 12 Jisas i ru e Ňägolo Boboma ghayayao t…®ne na i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya rakunekune, i mwanavevewoŇčgiya yao gharaten lenji tebol na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thiye va th…® vakuneŇčaŇčgiya bunebune, lenji ghamba yaku.  
\v 13 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTh…® rori Buk Boboma e t…®ne Loi iŇča, ‚ÄėLo Ňčgoloke ne th…® una idae Ňčgolo ghamba naŇčgo,‚Äô\x - \xo 21:13 \xt Ais 56:7; Jer 7:11\x* ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya rakaiv…® lenji ghamba kubaro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Ghar…®ghar…® maramaranji i kwaghe na vavana gheghenji thiya thar…® th…® rakamenawe e Ňägolo Bobomako t…®ne na i thawariŇčgi.  
\v 15 Ko mbaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na mbaro gharavavaghare th…® thuwe vakathako thovuye i vakathaŇčgi na gamagai th…® kulakula e Ňägolo Bobomako t…®ne, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHosana! Ra taraweŇča Deivid Rumbuye,‚ÄĚ gharenji i gaith…®wana Jisas.   
\p
\v 16 Th…® dagewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare u loŇčwe, ŇčgoroŇčga gamagaiko th…®Ňča?‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye. Mbe hu ndevaona mun bukuke iya iŇčake, ‚ÄėO Loi, u vavaghareŇčgiya gamagai na mbala gamagai nanasiye th…® taraweŇčaŇčge.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 21:16 \xt Sam 8:2\x*   
\p
\v 17 Jisas i iteteŇčgi na i raŇčgi Jerusalem e t…®ne, i wa Betani ve ghenawe.   
\s1 Jisas i gura umbwa idae fig  
\r (Mak 11:12-14,20-24)  
\p
\v 18 MbaŇčambaŇča moli Jisas i njogha Jerusalem. E kamwath…® mborowa bada i ghar…®.  
\v 19 I thuweya umbwa regha e kamwath…®ko ghadidiye, idae fig, i ru na i yanyi, ko iyemaeŇčge ma e uneune mbe ndamwandamwae eŇčge. I dage weya umbwama iŇča, ‚ÄúMa tene mbaŇča reghava u rau!‚ÄĚ E mbaŇčako iyako umbwama i mareyawowo.   
\p
\v 20 MbaŇča gharaghambu th…® thuwe gharenji i yo. Th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMe ŇčgoroŇčga na umbwako le mare i maya?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, thoŇčgo hu loŇčweghath…® na ma hu numoghegheiwo, val…®kaiwamiya hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya ma vakatha weya umbwako. Ma mbe iyako eŇčge, val…®kaiwamiya ne hu dage weya ou, ‚ÄėU wa na vo dobu e njigh…®ko t…®ne,‚Äô ne i vakatha Ňčgoreiye.  
\v 22 ThoŇčgo hu loŇčweghath…®, the bigiya ne hu naŇčgo weya Loi ne hu vaidi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Th…® vaito Jisas le vur…®gheghe r…®ghe  
\r (Mak 11:27-33; Luk 20:1-8)  
\p
\v 23 MbaŇča Jisas i ru e Ňägolo Boboma ghayayao t…®ne na i vavaghare, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na randevivaŇčgi th…® menawe na th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU vata thela ele mbaro vwatae na u vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake? Thela i giya vur…®gheghe e ghen?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, wo ya vaitoŇčga vaito regha na thoŇčgo hu wogiya ghathombe e ghino, ghino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ne ya utuŇča e ghemi ya vata thela ele mbaro vwatae na ya vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake.  
\v 25 Jon le r…®ghe na i bap…®taiso, i mena weya Loi o i mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®?‚ÄĚ  
\p Mbe thiye eŇčge th…® veutu weŇčgi, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo raŇča, ‚ÄėI mena weya Loi‚Äô ne iŇča, ‚ÄėBuda kaiwae na mava hu loŇčweghath…®gha Jon?‚Äô  
\v 26 Ko thoŇčgo raŇča, ‚ÄėI mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®,‚Äô ra mararuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, kaiwae th…® ghareghare Jon iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 Iya kaiwae th…® gonjogha weya Jisas, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa wo ghareghare.‚ÄĚ  
\p I dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mane ya utuŇča e ghemi, ya vata thela e vwatae na ya vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i utuŇča amala le ŇčgaŇčga thenjighewo utuninji  
\p
\v 28 Jisas i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga lemi renuwaŇča? Amala regha le ŇčgaŇčga thenjighewo. I wa weya vir…®viva na ve dagewe, iŇča ‚ÄėNaruŇčgu, noroke u wa na vo kaiwo e uma.‚Äô  
\v 29 I gonjogha weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄėYa botewo,‚Äô ko va muyai i v…®va le renuwaŇča na i wa.  
\v 30 Amalama i wa weya nariyema regha na ve dagewe tembe Ňčgoreiyeva me dage weya vir…®vivama. Nariyema iŇča, ‚ÄėŇägoreiye Bwebwe, tene ya wa,‚Äô ko iyemaeŇčge ma va i wa.  
\v 31 Thenjighewoko, thela i vakatha Ňčgoreiya ramanji le renuwaŇča?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúIya vir…®vivama.‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, takis gharamban na wanakau th…® mbana riwanji modae, thiye hu rerenuwaŇča kaero th…® vur…®mban Loi le ghamba mbaro e ghakamwath…®. Val…®kaiwanjiya ne th…® ru ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi mane hu ru.  
\v 32 Kaiwae Jon Rabap…®taiso va i mena weŇčga, i vaghareŇčga thanavu thovuye ghakamwath…® na ma hu loŇčweghath…®, ko takis gharamban na wanakau th…® mbana riwanji modae, thiye eŇčge th…® loŇčweghath…®. Othembe va hu thuweŇčgi th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, ko mava hu v…®va ghamithanavu na hu loŇčweghath…®gha Jon le utuko.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Uma gharanjimbunjimbu raraithar…®  
\r (Mak 12:1-12; Luk 20:9-19)  
\p
\v 33 Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowo ya utuŇčava goghaimba regha na hu loŇčwe: Lolo regha va i kabu waen ghauma, i gana vagh…®liya, i vakatha doda waen ghamba i imb…®imb…®, na i vatada Ňčgolo regha, umako gharanjimbunjimbu lenji ghamba yaku. I vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, amba i vatomwe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana na th…® vakaiwoŇča amalagh…®niye kaiwae. Na amalagh…®niye i wa e val…®vaŇčga regha.\fig Waen ghauma na ghamba i imb…®imb…®|alt="vineyard and the wine press" src="lb00103c.tif" size="span" copy="BFBS(Bass)" ref="21:33" \fig*   
\p
\v 34 ‚ÄúMbaŇča kaero ghambaŇča th…® vu, umama tanuwagae i variyeŇčgiya le rakakaiwo weŇčgiya umama gharanjimbunjimbu na veth…® mbana uneune amalagh…®niye kaiwae.  
\v 35 Umama gharanjimbunjimbu thiya laweŇčgiya rakakaiwoma, th…® ŇčgeŇčgeŇča regha, th…® tagavamara regha na th…® biriya regha e var…®.  
\v 36 Amalama mbowo i variyeŇčgiva le rakakaiwo vavana, seiwo i kivwala me vivama. Th…® vakatha weŇčgi tembe Ňčgoreiyeva meth…® vivama.  
\v 37 Muyai moli i variya nariye weŇčgi na iŇča, ‚ÄėNe th…® yavwatatawana naruŇčguke.‚Äô  
\v 38 Ko mbaŇča ranjimbunjimbuma th…® thuweya nariyeko, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėUmake tanuwagae nariya iyako. Amalagh…®niye ne i rombaroŇča umake ramae e ghereiye. Hu mena ra tagavamare na mbalama ra mbaroŇčava iya le umake.‚Äô  
\v 39 Th…® yalawe, th…® wokiyathuraŇčgiya e gana ghereiye na th…® tagavamare.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 40 Jisas i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne umama tanuwagae i njoghama, ne i vakatha budakai weŇčgiya umako gharanjimbunjimbu?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 41 Jiu lenji randevivaŇčgima th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNe i gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko raraithar…® na i vatomweya le umako weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® totogha th…® njimbukiki, mbala i mweghe na th…® vu, th…® vakatha wagiyawe uneuneko amalagh…®niye kaiwae na veth…® giyawe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 42 Jisas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe hu ndevaona mun ŇčgoroŇčga Buk Boboma iŇča?  
\q1 Var…®ke iya Ňčgoloke gharavatavatad va th…® botewo na i tabo mbagh…®mbagh…®.  
\q1 Iyake Giya le vakatha, na ghathuwathuwa i thovuye na i wo nuwanda.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 21:42 \xt Sam 118:22-23\x*   
\p
\v 43 Jisas mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage e ghemi, Loi ne i wo le ghamba mbarona ghathovuye weŇčga na i wogiya weŇčgiya the vanautuma ghar…®ghar…®niye iya ne e yawalinjiko uneune i woraŇčgiya i thovuyeŇča Loi le ghamba mbaro.  
\v 44 Thela ne i dobu e var…®ke iyake vwatae ne i tagamunumunuwo, na thoŇčgo var…®ke iyake i dobu lolo regha e vwatae ne i tagavwathavwatha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 45 MbaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Parisi th…® loŇčweya Jisas le goghaimbaŇčgiko, th…® ghareghare i utuutu thiye kaiwanji.  
\v 46 Th…® mando na th…® munjeva th…® yalawe ko iyemaeŇčge th…® mararuŇčgiya wabwiko kaiwae th…®Ňča iye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.   
\c 22  
\s1 Goghaimba ghe ghathaga kaiwae  
\r (Luk 14:15-24)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas mbowo i goghaimbava weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma meth…® vaitoma iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúLoi le ghamba mbaro Ňčgoreiya kiŇč regha, i vakatha thaga nariye le ghe kaiwae.  
\v 3 I variyeŇčgiya le rakakaiwo, th…® wa na veth…® butu weŇčgiya thavala ghanjikula ina e gheko ghathaga r…®ghe, ko iyemaeŇčge th…® botewo na th…® rakamena.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 ‚ÄúMbowo i variyeŇčgiva le rakakaiwo vavana iŇča, ‚ÄėVou dage weŇčgiya thavala mendava ya mwanavathaŇčgi, vouŇča ghan…®Ňčga kaero i vivathavao, burumwaka va th…® vivatharawe thagake kaiwae kaero th…® gaboŇčgi na bigibigike wolagh…®ye kaero th…®ko. Ma hu mena eŇčge e thagake r…®ghe.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 ‚ÄúKo thiye ma va th…® goru weya renuwaŇčako iyako na th…® wa Ňčgoreiya lenji renuwaŇča. Regha i wa ele uma t…®ne, regha i wa ele sitowa  
\v 6 na vavana th…® yalaweŇčgiya rakakaiwoŇčgima, th…® gaboŇčgi, na th…® tagavamareŇčgi.  
\v 7 KiŇč…®ma i gaith…® lagh…®ye moli, i variyeŇčgiya le ragagaith…®, th…® gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava th…® gaboŇčgiya le rakakaiwoma na th…® woŇčambu ghambanjiko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 ‚ÄúAmba i dage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwo, iŇča, ‚ÄėGhe ghathaga kaero ya vivathavao, ko thavala mendava ya kula weŇčgi ma th…® goru weya lo kulake.  
\v 9 Hu wa e kamwath…® ghavwaghavwala na thavala hu vaidiŇčgi, hu dage weŇčgi na th…® mena e thagake r…®ghe.‚Äô  
\v 10 Rakakaiwoma th…® wa e kamwath…®Ňčgiko na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye iya th…® vaidiŇčgiko, thovuthovuye o raraithar…®, th…® vaŇčguŇčgi, gheko ghathaga ghaŇčgolo i riyevanjara.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúKo mbaŇča kiŇč…®ma i ru thagako e ghaŇčgolo t…®ne na i thuweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko, i njimbuvaidiya amala regha ma va i njimbo ghe ghakwama.  
\v 12 I vaito iŇča, ‚ÄėWou, ŇčgoroŇčga mo mena u ruke na ma mo njimbo ghe ghakwama?‚Äô Amalama ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčae.  
\v 13 Amba kiŇč…®ma i dage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwoma iŇča, ‚ÄėHu Ňčgara n…®man…®mae na gheghe na hu wokiyathuraŇčgiya eto e momouwoko t…®ne ve randarandawe na i r…®gh…®mbiya ŇčiŇčiye.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Jisas i govun iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi i kula weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo, ko mbe thegheviye eŇčge i tuthiŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Takis ghavamodo kaiwae  
\r (Mak 12:13-17; Luk 20:19-26)  
\p
\v 15 Amba Parisi th…® iteta Jisas na th…® raka veth…® rerenuwaŇča ŇčgoroŇčga ne th…®Ňča na th…® vakatha ghawonjowe ele utuutuko.  
\v 16 Parisi th…® variyeŇčgiya ghanjiraghambu vavanawe Jisas weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana thiye th…® ghambugha Herod le wabwi ghar…®ghar…®niye. Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, wo ghareghare u utuŇča emunjoru na len vavaghare Loi le renuwaŇča ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji i rumwaru. Ma u goru weya ŇčgoroŇčga ghar…®ghar…® lenji renuwaŇča kaiwae ma u goru weya ŇčgoroŇčga lolo le thimba o le lagh…®lagh…®ye.  
\v 17 ŇägoroŇčga ghen len renuwaŇča, wo u utugiyama weime. Mbaro i dage Ňčgoreiye na wo vamodo takisi weya Sisa o nandere?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 Jisas kaero i ghareghareya lenji renuwaŇčako raraithar…® iya kaiwae i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTaukwana ghemi! Buda kaiwae hu munjeva hu mando na hu wonjoweŇčgo.  
\v 19 Wo hu wovatomwe weŇčgo manike iya hu vavamodo takisikowe.‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…® wo geth…®ra na th…® mena th…® wogiyawe,  
\v 20 amba i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThela ŇčgaliŇčgaliya na idae iya e manike?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúSisa.‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúSisa le bigibigi hu giyawa Sisa na Loi le bigibigi hu giyawa Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 MbaŇča th…® loŇčweya iyake, gharenji i yo, th…® itete na th…® rakawa.   
\s1 Jisas i thombeya vaito thuweiru kaiwae  
\r (Mak 12:18-27; Luk 20:27-40)  
\p
\v 23 MbaŇčako iyako e t…®ne Sadusi, thiye ma th…® loŇčweghath…®gha ramaremare tene th…® thuweiruva, th…® mena weya Jisas na th…® vaito  
\v 24 th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, Mosese iŇča thoŇčgo amala regha i ghe, ma ele ŇčgaŇčga na i mare, ghaghae ma i rovaŇčguva gh…®mbwiyeko. ThoŇčgo i ghamb…® weiye, gamagaiko thiyako ghaghaeko va i mareko le ŇčgaŇčga.\x - \xo 22:24 \xt Mba 25:5-6\x*  
\v 25 Amala regha weiyaŇčgiya oghaghae, thenjighepir…® vara, t…®nanji na ramanji regha. Lagh…®yeninji va i ghe na i mare, ma ele ŇčgaŇčga na ghembwiyeko ghaghae kaero i rovaŇčguva.  
\v 26 Ghaghae theghewoniye te vambe Ňčgoreiyeva, theghetoninji Ňčgoreiye gheghada thenjighepir…®ko th…® vaidi Ňčgoreiye.  
\v 27 Muyai moli elagh…®niye i mare.  
\v 28 Ne mbaŇča ramaremare th…® thuweiru na e yawayawalinjiva, thela ne i ghe weiye, kaiwae mbe thenjighepir…®ko vara va th…® vaŇčgu?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero hu vur…®thavwiya kamwath…®, kaiwae ma hu ghareghareya Buk Boboma le woraŇčgiya ŇčgoroŇčga gharumwaru na budakaiya Loi val…®kaiwae i vakatha.  
\v 30 Kaiwae mbaŇča ne ramaremare th…® thuweiru na tembe e yawayawalinjiva vama tembene th…® gheva, thiye ne Ňčgoranjiya nyao thovuthovuye e buruburu.  
\v 31 Ramaremare lenji thuweiru na e yawayawalinji utuniye, ma hu vaona ŇčgoroŇčga Loi va i utuŇča weŇčga? IŇča,  
\v 32 ‚ÄėGhino Eibraham, Aisake na Jeikob lenji Loi.‚Äô\x - \xo 22:32 \xt RaŇč 3:6\x* Loi va iŇča Ňčgoreiyako mbala ra ghareghare ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake kaerova th…® mare ko iyemaeŇčge mbe e yawayawalinjiva. Loi, iye ma ramaremare lenji Loi Ňčgoreiye, nandere, mbe thiye eŇčge e yawayawalinji lenji Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 MbaŇča wabwiko th…® loŇčweya iyake, gharenji i yo le vavaghareko kaiwae.   
\s1 Mbaro lagh…®ye moli  
\r (Mak 12:28-34)  
\p
\v 34 Ko mbaŇča Parisi th…® loŇčweya Jisas i thombe Sadusi lenji vaito na i vakatha ma e ghal…®ghal…®Ňčanji, th…® mena th…® wabwi na regha.  
\v 35 Ghanjiu regha, mbaro gharavavaghare i munjeva i mando Jisas e vaito regha,  
\v 36 iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, the mbaro i lagh…®ye vara moli Mosese le mbaro e t…®ne?‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚Äú‚ÄėU gharethovu weya Giya len Loi e gharena lagh…®ye, e unena lagh…®ye na e len renuwaŇčana lagh…®ye.‚Äô\x - \xo 22:37 \xt Mba 6:5\x*  
\v 38 Iyake mbaro lagh…®ye na iviva moli.  
\v 39 Mbaro theghewoniye mbe lagh…®yeva Ňčgora iyake, iŇča, ‚ÄėU gharethovu weya ghanu Ňčgoreiya u gharethovu e ghen.‚Äô\x - \xo 22:39 \xt Liv 19:18\x*  
\v 40 Mosese le mbaroko wolagh…®ye na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu lenji vavaghareŇčgi, th…® ndeghath…®we iya mbaroke theghewoke thiyake.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Mesaiya iye Deivid rumbuye tembe Ňčgoreiya Deivid ghagiya  
\r (Mak 12:35-37; Luk 20:41-44)  
\p
\v 41 MbaŇča Parisi th…® megh…®liŇča Jisas, amba i vaitoŇčgi iŇča,  
\v 42 ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga lemi rerenuwaŇča Mesaiya kaiwae? Iye thela rumbuye?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúIye Deivid rumbuye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 43 Jisas mbowo i vaitoŇčgiva iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčgaeŇčge na Nyao Boboma i vakatha Deivid i wovagiyagiyaŇča Mesaiya? Kaiwae Deivid iŇča,  
\v 44 ‚ÄėGiya Loi i dagewe wo Giya iŇča: U yaku val…®vaŇčga e uneŇčguke ghaghad ne ya biginjoŇčaŇčgiya ghan…®th…®gh…®ya e gheghen raberabe.‚Äô\x - \xo 22:44 \xt Sam 110:1\x*   
\p
\v 45 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo Deivid i una Mesaiya ‚Äėwo Giya,‚Äô ŇčgoroŇčgaeŇčge na Mesaiya iye Deivid rumbuye?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 46 Ma te lolo reghava val…®kaiwae i thombewe na kaiwae th…® ghareghare ma val…®kaiwae th…® kwan…®yaro, ma te mbaŇča reghava lolo regha i giya vaito weya Jisas.   
\c 23  
\s1 Jisas i wonjoŇčaŇčgiya Jiu lenji randeviva  
\r (Mak 12:38-40; Luk 11:37-52; 20:45-47)  
\p
\v 1 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgiya wabwima na gharaghambuma, iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúMbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi thiye th…® ghareghare wagiyawe Mosese le mbaro na val…®kaiwanjiya th…® vamanjamanjalaŇča.  
\v 3 Iya kaiwae, hu vandeŇčekikiya ghal…®Ňčanjiko na hu ghambugha lenji utuko wolagh…®ye, ko iyemaeŇčge thava hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya lenji vakathako kaiwae budakaiya th…® vakatha, ma mboromboro weiye lenji utuko.  
\v 4 Lenji mbaro i ghanagha moli ne th…® giya weŇčga na hu bigi, ko iyemaeŇčge thiye mane n…®manji g…®g…®ra regha i nja na i thalavuŇčga na hu wo vuyowoko iyako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 ‚ÄúTh…® vakathaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye mbala ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuweŇčgi. Nambonambo Ňčgamwaiwo, th…® vakathaŇčgi na i lagh…®ye moli, Buk Boboma r…®gher…®ghe vavana inanjiwe. Ňägamwara th…® Ňčgar…® e ghamwanji na Ňčgamwara e n…®manji mborowa. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, ghanjikwama mbothiye ghabithabitha th…® vakathaŇčgi na molamolao.  
\v 6 Thaga e t…®ne nuwanjiya veth…® yaku Ňčgora ghar…®ghar…®ko lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghamba yaku na e lenji Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne veth…® yaku e ghamba yaku thovuye ghar…®ghar…® e ghamwanji.  
\v 7 ThoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® th…® vaidiŇčgi e kamwath…®, nuwanjiya ghar…®ghar…®ko weiye lenji yavwatata th…® dage mwaewo weŇčgi na th…®Ňča ‚ÄėRavavaghare‚Äô weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ\fig Parisi th…® Ňčgar…® nambonambo e ghamwanji na e n…®manji na ghanjikwama mbothiye e ghabithabitha molamolao|alt="a pharisee" src="lb00276c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="23:1-7" \fig*   
\p
\v 8 ‚ÄúThava ghamunena th…® dage weŇčga na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėRavavaghare‚Äô kaiwae ghami Ravavaghare mbe ghambereghaeŇčge na taulagh…®na ghemi mbe oghaghami eŇčge iya ghamunena.  
\v 9 Tha hu una lolo regha e yambaneke na huŇča ramami kaiwae Ramami mbe ghambereghaeŇčge ina e buruburu.  
\v 10 Thava ghar…®ghar…® th…® dage weŇčga na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėRandeviva‚Äô kaiwae lemi randeviva ghamberegha, iye Mesaiya.  
\v 11 Thela thoŇčgo iye i lagh…®ye e t…®nemina, iye i tabo na lemi rakakaiwo.  
\v 12 Thela thoŇčgo ghamberegha tembe i wovoreŇča Loi ne i wonjoŇča, na thela i wonjoŇča ghamberegha, Loi ne i wovoreŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Parisi lenji kwan kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo  
\r (Mak 12:40; Luk 11:39-42,44,52; 20:47)  
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona, kaiwae hu kiya Loi le ghamba mbaro ghakamwath…® ghar…®ghar…® e ghamwanji na hu botewo hu ru na thavala nuwanjiya th…® ru hu ndegana lenji kamwath…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Hu bigiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye weŇčgiya wambwiwambwi na hu mbaroŇčaŇčgi. Lemi naŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® e maranji i molao mbala th…® vandeŇčeŇčga. Lemi vakathake thiyake kaiwanji ne hu vaidiya lith…® lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Vou gh…®nagha na hu loŇčgatakweya vanautumake wolagh…®ye. Hu mando na hu utuv…®va lolo regha nuwae na i kururu weya Loi Ňčgoreiya lemi kamwath…®na. MbaŇča i loŇčweghath…®Ňčga, hu vakatha na i tabona Gehena loloniye moli Ňčgoreiye ghemi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 ‚ÄúAleu, ghemi randeviva raraithar…® na marami i kwaghe! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Ghemi huŇča, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una Ňägolo Boboma, i thovuye eŇčge thoŇčgo ma i ghambugha dageraweko iyako; ko thoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una gol…®ko e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne, ma i thovuyewe thoŇčgo ma i ghambugha dageraweko iyako.‚Äô  
\v 17 Unouna ghemi na marami i kwaghe! IyaŇčganiya bigi lagh…®ye, gol o Ňägolo Boboma iya i vakatha gol…®ko na i boboma?  
\v 18 Ghemi tembe huŇčava, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una var…®ko iya ghamba vowoko, i thovuyewe eŇčge thoŇčgo ma i ghambugha dageraweko iyako; ko thoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una wogiyako iya vowoko kaiwae, ma i thovuyewe thoŇčgo ma i ghambugha dageraweko iyako!‚Äô  
\v 19 Ghemi marami i kwaghe! IyaŇčganiya bigi lagh…®ye wogiya o ghamba vowoko iya i vakatha wogiyako na i boboma.  
\v 20 Iya kaiwae, mbaŇča thoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una ghamba vowoko, i tholo e ghamba vowoko weiye wogiyako iya vowoko kaiwae.  
\v 21 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mbaŇča thoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una Ňägolo Boboma, i tholo e Ňägolo Boboma na Loi, ina i yaku gheko.  
\v 22 Na mbaŇča thoŇčgo lolo regha i tholo na i una buruburu, i tholo ele ghamba yaku thovuye na weiye Loi ghamberegha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Ghan…®Ňčga Ňčgoreiya utha, njambao na sele,\f + \fr 23:23 \ft Buk Boboma Togha ma iŇča, ‚Äúutha, njambao na sele.‚ÄĚ Wo vaghagh…®le ‚Äúmint, dill and cummin,‚ÄĚ thiye umbwaumbwa ndamwandamwa o mbombouye Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…® vakatha gham…®nae thovuye weŇčgiya ghan…®Ňčga vavana. R…®ghethoruke iyake gharumwaru ma i gharav…® kaiwae wo vakaiwoŇča ‚Äúutha, njambao na sele.‚ÄĚ\f* hu vakatha wabwi na wabwiyaworo na hu giya wabwira weya Loi lemi mwaewo, Ňčgoreiya mbaro i woraŇčgiya. Othembe hu ghambu wagiyawe mbaroko iyako, ko iyemaeŇčge hu renuwaŇča valaweya mbaro lagh…®lagh…®ye na ma hu ghambuŇčgi. Mbaro Ňčgoranjiya thiyake: la vakatha i rumwaru weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, gharenda i njaweŇčgiya ghandaune na ra ghambuvao Loi. Mbala hu ghambuŇčgiya mbaroke thiyake na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghan…®Ňčga ghanjimbaro hu ghambuŇčgi.  
\v 24 Ghemi randeviva raraithar…® na marami i kwaghe! Mbaro nanasiye hu ghambu wagiyaweŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaro lagh…®lagh…®ye hu renuwaŇča valaweŇčgi. Hu woraŇčgiya mbilambila e ghamimbwana, ko iyemaeŇčge ma hu thuwe kamel mbe umbwara vara hu kovululu weiye ghamimbwana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Ghemi Ňčgoramiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® thavwi wagiyawe kom na gaeba vwatanji, ko iyemaeŇčge ma th…® thavwiya t…®nenji. Hu vakatha wagiyaweya vwatanji ko votha na kurakura th…® riyevanjaraŇčgo.  
\v 26 Ghemi Parisi marami i kwaghe! I viva wo hu thavwi wagiyaweya kom na gaeba t…®nenji ambane vwatanji i th…®na.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Ghemi Ňčgoramiya ghabubu, th…® vanamwe vwatae na th…® kabu jin. Ghayamoyamo i thovuye, ko e t…®neko kaka wokiwokiniye na vwatha i riyevanjara.  
\v 28 Ghemi Ňčgoreiye, eto ghar…®ghar…® th…® thuweŇčga Ňčgoreiya ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye, ko e gharemina kwan na thanavu raraithar…® i riyevanjara.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúAleu, mbaro gharavavaghare na Parisi! Taukwana ghemi! Nevole hu thovuyaona! Hu vatad…®Ňčgiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu ghabubunji na hu vabithabithaŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko me vivako, thiye ghanjithanavu va i rumwaru, ghabubunji,  
\v 30 na huŇča thoŇčgova hu yaku orumburumbunda e ghanjimbaŇča, mbala mava hu vakatha Ňčgoreiya va th…® vakatha na ma hu gaboŇčgiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautuŇčgi.  
\v 31 Ko iyemaeŇčge tembe ghamimberegha hu woraŇčgiyaŇčga, mbema gheminani orumburumbumiŇčgiya iya thiye va th…® gaboŇčgiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu.  
\v 32 Ko mbema hu rombele eŇčge iya thanavuna orumburumbumi va th…® vakavakathanawe. Na ne hu vaidiya ghamilith…®we.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 ‚ÄúGhemi Ňčgoramiya mwata na mwata le ŇčgaŇčga ghemi! Ma tene hu ghaeruva, ghemi kaero inami Gehena.  
\v 34 Iya kaiwae ya dage e ghemi, ne ya variyeŇčgiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, rathimbathimba lagh…®lagh…®ye na ravavaghare e ghemi. Ne hu gaboŇčgiya vavana, hu rokrosiŇčgiya vavana, hu yab…®b…®Ňčgiya vavana e Ňčgolo kururu t…®ne na hu vagevagege loloŇčga weŇčgi e ghemba na ghemba.  
\v 35 Iyake kaiwae, ne hu vaidiya lith…® gabo ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye kaiwanji. Va th…® un…®gh…®kaivara Eibol na i mena le ghambako ghemi Jiu hu un…®gh…® Sakaraiya Barakaiya nariye, e Ňägolo Boboma na ghamba vowo ghanjilughawoghawo e t…®ne.  
\v 36 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, vakathako thiyako wolagh…®ye ghalith…® ne i nja weŇčga, ghemi thake iyake.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas i gharaewo Jerusalem  
\r (Luk 13:34-35)  
\p
\v 37 ‚ÄúO, o Jerusalem ee Jerusalem! Ghemi va hu gaboŇčgiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu na hu tagavavamareŇčgi e var…® thavala Loi va i variyeŇčgi weŇčga. MbaŇča i ghanagha nuwaŇčguiya ya mbanvathavathaŇčgiya ghan…®rayakuyaku Ňčgoreiya kamkam man…®wevo i thogaramuramuŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga e vineiye, ko iyemaeŇčge ma nuwamiya ya vakatha weŇčga.  
\v 38 Loi ne i garaiteta ghambami na ma kokowa eŇčge.  
\v 39 Kaiwae ya dage e ghemi, ma tene hu thuweŇčgova gheghada mbaŇča ne huŇča, ‚ÄėLoi ghare weya loloke iya i mena Giya Loi e idaeke.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 23:39 \xt Sam 118:26\x*   
\c 24  
\s1 Jisas iŇča nevole th…® raka Ňägolo Boboma  
\r (Mak 13:1-2; Luk 21:5-6)  
\p
\v 1 Jisas vama i iteteŇča Ňägolo Boboma ghayayao mbaŇčaniye gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…® vatomweya Ňägolo Bobomako ŇčgoloŇčgoloniyeŇčgi.  
\v 2 IŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, iya hu thuweŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, mavole var…® regha ne i ndeghath…® ele ghamba ndeghath…®ko, wolagh…®yeko nevole th…® bigiyathuvao bode.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Jisas iŇča gharaghambuko nevole th…® vaidiŇčgiya vuyowo lagh…®ye moli  
\p
\v 3 Jisas va i yaku Oliv…® e ghanji Ou mbe ghambereghaeŇčge na gharaghambu th…® rakamenawe. Th…® vaito, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU utugiya weime ne thembaŇča bigibigike thiyake iya mo utuŇčama weime th…® yomara na thambo nono ne i woraŇčgiya weime mbaŇča ne len mena na yambaneke le ghambako?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčga, tha lolo regha i yaroŇčga.  
\v 5 Kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® i ghanagha ne th…® mena e idaŇčgu na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėGhino Mesaiya!‚Äô na ne th…® yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® i ghanagha.  
\v 6 Ne hu loŇčweŇčgiya vanautuma lenji gaith…® utuniye na toto gaith…® kaiwae, ko ne hu ndemararu. Bigibigike thiyake ne th…® yomara, ko ma ghanjirumwaru Ňčgoreiye mbaŇča kaero le ghambako.  
\v 7 Vanautuma ne th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi; rambarombaro ne th…® vegaith…® weŇčgi. Nevole vunuvu na ragheragheghe lemoyo e yambaneke lagh…®ye.  
\v 8 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake Ňčgoreiya wevo Ňčgamoiye i njivun…®kai vara ghamb…® kaiwae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúNevole th…® laweŇčga na th…® vaŇčgugiyaŇčga weŇčgiya rambarombaro na th…® gaboŇčga. Ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® botewoyathuŇčga idaŇčgu kaiwae.  
\v 10 E mbaŇčako iyako ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo ne th…® botewo lenji loŇčweghath…® na ne th…® vevatomweŇčgi na th…® vebotewoŇčgi.  
\v 11 Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan lemoyo ne th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® yaroŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo.  
\v 12 Kaiwae thar…® ghavakatha ne i mbuthu na i yala, ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo lenji gharethovu ne i nasiye weŇčgiya lenji val…®ghar…®ghar…®.  
\v 13 Ko thela ne i ghataŇčaghath…®Ňčgiya vuyowoke thiyake na gheghada le ghambako ne i vaidiya vamoru.  
\v 14 Na Totoke Thovuye iyake Loi le ghamba mbaro utuutuniye ne th…® vavaghareŇča e yambaneke lagh…®ye na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye th…® ghareghare amba muyai mbaŇča le ghambako i mena.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Vuyowo lagh…®ye tene i mena  
\r (Mak 13:14-20; Luk 21:20-24)  
\p
\v 15 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu thuweya bigiko i vamb…®gh…®ya Ňägolo Boboma na i vakatha ghar…®ghar…® th…® roitetako, na i ndeghath…® Ňčgoreiye ma val…®kaiwae i ndeghath…®we, iya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu Daniyel va i utuŇčama.\x - \xo 24:15 \xt Dan 9:27; 11:31; 12:11\x* (Ghemi bukuke iyake gharavavaona wo hu rerenuwaŇča ghaghad…® nuwamina i rumwaruŇča utuke iyake!)  
\v 16 E mbaŇčako iyako thavala inanji Judiya e t…®ne th…® rakavo na th…® wa e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji.  
\v 17 Lolo ina ele Ňčgolo vwatae na i nja thava i ru e Ňčgolo t…®ne na i wo bigi regha. Mbema i vo eŇčge.  
\v 18 Na lolo i kakaiwo e uma t…®ne ne i ndenjogha e ghemba na i liya ghakwama ghayaboyabo.  
\v 19 Ne e mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako, ne i vuyowo lagh…®ye moli weŇčgiya wanakau maramarabo na wanakau weinjiyaŇčgiya gamagai amba th…® thuthu!  
\v 20 Hu naŇčgo weya Loi mbala ma hu vo mbaŇča ne njigh…®njigh…® ghambaŇča o ne Sabat.  
\v 21 Vuyowo ne e mbaŇčako iyako ne i lagh…®ye, i lagh…®ye moli. Na vuyowoko Ňčgoranjiyako ma mbaŇča regha i yomara e yambaneke va i rikowe gheghada noroke, na ma tene Ňčgoreiyeva mbaŇča muyai.  
\v 22 ThoŇčgo ma Loi i wonjoŇča mbaŇča le molamolao, mbala ma lolo regha i moru. Ko le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwae, Loi ne i wonjoŇča vuyowo ghambaŇča le molamolao.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo regha i dage e ghemi iŇča, ‚ÄėWo hu thuwe, Mesaiya maiya!‚Äô o ‚ÄėMaiyako!‚Äô ne hu ndeloŇčweghath…®.  
\v 24 Kaiwae Mesaiya kwan…®kwan na Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu kwan…®kwan ne th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® vakathaŇčgiya vakatha ghamba rotaele i ghanagha na th…® wo ghar…®ghar…® nuwanji, na th…® munje tembe th…® wova Loi le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye nuwanji.  
\v 25 Wo hu thuwe, amba ŇčgaŇčgagha kaero ya giya yanawami.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo regha i dage weŇčga iŇča, ‚ÄėMaiyako, e njamnjam bwaga!‚Äô Thava hu wa gheko. O thoŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄėMbeiya e Ňčgoloke,‚Äô ne hu ndeloŇčweghath…®.  
\v 27 Kaiwae Lolo Nariye le mena ne Ňčgoreiya i vilamema, i vilame yavorowoko na manjamanjalawae i wa ve wo bodeoko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúBigi maremare aŇčga inae ma rawowoidi th…® rakavathavathawe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Lolo Nariye le mena  
\r (Mak 13:24-27; Luk 21:25-28)  
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúVuyowo e mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako e ghereiye varae mara ne i momouwo, manjala mane i mb…®le, gh…®tara ne th…® dobu e buruburu na buruburu matemate ne thiya nyiv…®vao.\x - \xo 24:29 \xt Ais 13:10; 34:4\x*  
\v 30 Amba Lolo Nariye le mena ghanono ne i yomara e buruburu, na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke thiya randa, mbaŇča ne th…® thuweya Lolo Nariye i njama e Ňčgal…®l…® vwatanji, weiye le vur…®gheghe na vwenyevwenye lagh…®ye.\x - \xo 24:30 \xt Dan 7:13\x*  
\v 31 Ne th…® wiya mema na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye moli amba i variyeŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye e yambaneke ghadidiye geth…®var…® na th…® vaŇčguvathavathaŇčgiya le tututhi ghar…®ghar…®niye e yambaneke mbothiye regha gheghada val…®mbothiye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Hu wo vavaghare weya fig  
\r (Mak 13:28-31; Luk 21:29-33)  
\p
\v 32 ‚ÄúLemi ghamba ghareghare thovuye hu wo weya umbwa fig. MbaŇča hu thuwe ndamwandamwa th…® thalavwara, hu ghareghareya mbaŇča nasiye thuwai ghambaŇča.  
\v 33 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mbaŇča ne hu thuweŇčgiya bigibigike thiyake th…® yoyomara, hu ghareghare le njoghama ghambaŇča ma bwagabwaga, maiyavara.  
\v 34 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi thake iyake mamba ne thiya marevao ghaghad bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake th…® yomara.  
\v 35 Buruburu na yambane ne th…®ko, ko ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke mane iko.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Ma lolo regha i ghareghare thembaŇča Lolo Nariye ne i mena  
\r (Mak 13:32-37; Luk 17:26-35)  
\p
\v 36 ‚ÄúMa lolo regha i ghareghare thembaŇča na the lughawoghawo Lolo Nariye ne i menawe. Nyao thovuthovuye e buruburu ma th…® ghareghare, Nariye ma i ghareghare, mbe Ramae ghamberegha eŇčge i ghareghare ne thembaŇča.  
\v 37 Ghaghad thembaŇča Lolo Nariye ne i mena, ghar…®ghar…® ne lenji vakatha Ňčgoreiya th…® vakatha Nowa va ghambaŇča.  
\v 38 Va e mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako amba muyai ŇčgonuŇčgo i voru na i thotho, ghar…®ghar…® th…® ghan…®Ňčga na th…® munumu, gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau th…® ghe, ghaghad vara e mbaŇčaniye Nowa i tha e waŇčgama.  
\v 39 Ma va th…® ghareghare, ŇčgonuŇčgo na thotho raithar…® regha maiyavara e ghamwanjina. I mena na i gabovaoŇčgi. Iyako ne Ňčgoreiye mbaŇča Lolo Nariye ne le mena.  
\v 40 E mbaŇčako iyako gh…®mogh…®moru thenjighewo ne th…® kaiwo e uma t…®ne: regha ne th…® yovaŇčgu, na regha ne th…® itete.  
\v 41 Wanakau theunyiwo ne inanji wit ghamba vakatha th…® vwaŇčgoŇčgo wit: eunda ne th…® yovaŇčgu na eunda ne th…® itete.  
\v 42 Iya kaiwae hu njaŇčanja, kaiwae ma hu ghareghare thembaŇča ghami Giya ne i mena.  
\v 43 Hu renuwaŇčakikiya iyake: thoŇčgo Ňčgolo tanuwagae va i ghareghareya thembaŇča ghalughawoghawo rakaiv…® ne i vuthawe, ne i njaŇčanjaŇča ele Ňčgoloko na rakaiv…®ko tha i ruwe.  
\v 44 Ghemi tembe Ňčgoreiyeva hu vivatha na mbema hu roroghagha eŇčge, kaiwae Lolo Nariye ne i mena e lughawoghawo, ma hu ghareghare ne i menawe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Rakakaiwo thovuye na rakakaiwo raithar…®  
\r (Luk 12:41-48)  
\p
\v 45 ‚ÄúGhemi mbala Ňčgoramiya rakakaiwo i manabu na e ghavareminje iya ghagiya i worawe na i njimbukikiŇčgiya rakakaiwo na i giya ghanji, ghan…®Ňčga e ghambaŇča moli.  
\v 46 Ne i thovuye moli weya rakakaiwoko iyako thoŇčgo ghagiya i vutha na i vaidiya i vakatha Ňčgoraiyako.  
\v 47 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, ne i worawe na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye.  
\v 48 Ko thoŇčgo iye rakakaiwo raithar…® ne i renuwaŇča e ghare na iŇča, ‚ÄėO giyama mane i vutha rukuruku,‚Äô  
\v 49 amba i yab…®b…®Ňčgiya le val…®rakakaiwoko na i ghan…®Ňčga na i munumu weiyaŇčgiya ramunumu.  
\v 50 MbaŇča regha rakakaiwoma ghagiya i njoghama, i vath…®na ghare kaiwae rakakaiwoma mane i ghareghare thembaŇča na the lughawoghawo giyama ne i njoghamawe.  
\v 51 Ghagiya ne i vutha i Ňčge na i tagavotagamenawe, na i vaŇčgurawe ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…® na rakwan…®Ňčgi e lenji lith…® ghembaniye, ghakaiwo randa na th…® r…®gh…®mbiya ŇčiŇčiye.‚ÄĚ   
\c 25  
\s1 Gagamaina theuyawora utuninji  
\p
\v 1 Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčako iyako Loi le ghamba mbaro le mena ne Ňčgoreiyake. Gagamaina theuyawora th…® bigiya lenji lemp, th…® wa na veth…® roghagha ragheghe gh…®moru ele Ňčgolo ghadidiye. Th…® roroghaghawe gheghada ragheghe gh…®moru i njoghama weiye ragheghe wevo na i vaŇčguruwoŇčgi e Ňčgolo t…®ne.  
\v 2 Theulima unounoŇčgi na theulima th…® manabu.  
\v 3 UnounoŇčgima th…® bigiya lenji lemp, ko ma va th…® guda ghembwa seiwova,  
\v 4 ko iyemaeŇčge manabuŇčgima va th…® bigiŇčgiya lenji lemp weiye ghembwa e variye.  
\v 5 Ragheghe gh…®moru le vutha va i vuyowo iwaeŇčge wanakauma maranji i gaboŇčgi na thiya ghenelaŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúVama gougou mboro amba lolo regha i mena i kula iŇča, ‚ÄėRagheghe gh…®moru ma iyake! Hu mena na hu thuwe.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 ‚ÄúGagamainama th…® rakathuweiru na th…® vakatha wagiyaweŇčgiya lenji lemp.  
\v 8 Amba unounoma th…® dage weŇčgiya manabuma th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėHu giyama lemi mbwana seiwo weime kaiwae lama lemp…®Ňčgike ma ma e ghanjimbwa na kaero iya vara thiya mareke.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 ‚ÄúTh…® gonjogha weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėNandere. Ghemi na ghime ma val…®kaiwanda. Wo hu wa e ghamba vamodoko na vou vamodo kaiwami.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 ‚ÄúKo vamba th…® loŇčgaloŇčga mbwa ghavamodo kaiwae, ragheghe gh…®moru kaero i vutha. Gagamainama va th…® vivatha wagiyawema th…® ru weinji ragheghema e thaga t…®ne, amba th…® kiya th…®n…®mba.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 ‚ÄúMuyai gagamaina unounoma th…® vutha na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėAmalana, amalana, u vugha th…®n…®mbana wo ruwo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúAmalama i gonjogha weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄėYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, ma ya ghareghareŇčga.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae hu njimbukikiŇčga, kaiwae ma hu ghareghare thembaŇča o the lughawoghawo ghamigiya ne i menawe.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Rakakaiwo thovuye na rakakaiwo raithar…®  
\r (Luk 19:11-27)  
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúE mbaŇčako iyako Loi le ghamba mbaro le mena ne Ňčgoreiya amala regha i wareriŇča val…®vaŇčga regha. I kula vathaŇčgiya le rakakaiwo na i giya le bigibigiko weŇčgi th…® njimbukiki.  
\v 15 I giyawa regha paeb tausan kina, theghewoniye tu tausan kina na theghetoniye wan tausan kina. I giya Ňčgoreiya regha na regha le ghareghare le lagh…®lagh…®ye, amba muyai i wareri.  
\v 16 Amalama me mbana paeb tausan…®ma i wa e mbaŇčako iyako na ve vakaiwoŇča na tembe i vaidiva paeb tausan kina.  
\v 17 Amalama me mbana tu tausan…®ma i vakatha Ňčgoreiye na tembe i vaidiva tu tausan kina.  
\v 18 Ko amalama me mbana wan tausan…®ma, i wa ve t…®gha doda e thelau na i beku ghagiyama le maniwe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 ‚ÄúVama mbaŇča molao amba giyama i njogha, i dage weŇčgi na th…® utugiyawe ŇčgoroŇčga va th…® vakaiwoŇča na th…®Ňča le maniko.  
\v 20 Amalama iyava i mbana paeb tausan…®ma weiye mbowo paeb tausan…®va e vwatae i mena i giyawe na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄėAmalana, va u giya paeb tausan e ghino. Wo u thuwe, vama ya vaidiva paeb tausan.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 ‚ÄúGiyama i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄėI thovuye moli! Rakakaiwo thovuye na emunjoru ghen. Bigibigi ma th…® ghanagha u njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčgi. Ne ya woraweŇčge na u njimbukikiŇčgiya bigibigi th…® ghanagha. U mena weiŇčgu ghen ra warari.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 ‚ÄúAmalama va i mbana tu tausan…®ma i mena na iŇča, ‚ÄėAmalana, va u giya tu tausan e ghino. Wo u thuwe, vama ya rovaidiva tu tausan.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 ‚ÄúGiyama i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄėI thovuye moli! Rakakaiwo thovuye na emunjoru ghen. Bigibigi ma th…® ghanagha u njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčgi. Ne ya woraweŇčge u njimbukikiŇčgiya bigibigi th…® ghanagha. U mena weiŇčgu ghen ra warari.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúAmba amalama va i mbana wan tausan…®ma i mena iŇča, ‚ÄėAmalana, ya ghareghare len mbaro i vur…®gheghe kaiwae thebigiya ma va u ghavo u t…®gh…® na u vathe e len Ňčgolo. Ghar…®ghar…® vavana lenji kaiwo une ghen u mban.  
\v 25 Iya kaiwae va ya mararu na ya wa na va beku len manina e thelau. Wo u thuwe len manima mbe iya, ya biginjogha e ghen.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúGiyama i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄėRakakaiwo raithar…® na njavovo ghen. Kaero u ghareghare, thebigiya ma va ya ghavo ya t…®gh…® na ya vathe elo Ňčgolo na ghar…®ghar…® vavana lenji kaiwo une ghino ya mban.  
\v 27 Ko iyake, mbalava vo bigiraweya lo manike e beŇč…®k na th…® vakaiwoŇča na mbaŇča ya njoghama ya mban njogha weiye vavanava e vwatae.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúI dage weŇčgiya rakakaiwo vavanava, iŇča, ‚ÄėHu bigiya maninawe na hu bigigiya weya amalana iya ten tausana inawe.  
\v 29 Thela i vakaiwoŇča wagiyaweya ghabebeko, ghino ya vatabowe na iye veimaima. Ko iyemaeŇčge weya thela ma e ghavareminje, othembe nasiye moli inawe, ya bigivaowe.  
\v 30 Ko iya rakakaiwoke raithar…® iyake, hu wokiyathu eto, e mouwoko t…®ne na ghakaiwo randa na i r…®gh…®mbiya ŇčiŇčiye.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Lolo Nariye ne i ghathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye  
\p
\v 31 ‚ÄúMbaŇča Lolo Nariye ne i mena weiyaŇčgi nyaoko thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye, na amalagh…®niye i tabo na kiŇč, ne i yaku ele ghamba yaku thovuye na i mbaro.  
\v 32 Yambaneke lagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…®niye ne th…® mevathavatha e marae na i vaghathaŇčgi na wabwi theghewo, Ňčgoreiya sip gharanjimbunjimbu i ghathaŇčgiya sip na gout tomethi lenji yaku.  
\v 33 Ne i bigiraweŇčgiya sip e une na gout e moiye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 34 ‚ÄúAmba KiŇč i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® inanji e uneko iŇča, ‚ÄėHu rakamena, thavala ghemi Bwebwe i mwaewo weŇčga. Hu mena hu rakaru ele ghamba mbaroke, iyava i vivatharaweke kaiwami mbaŇča va i vakatha yambaneke.  
\v 35 Kaiwae bada i ghar…®Ňčgo na hu giya ghan…®Ňčga e ghino, mbwa i ghar…®Ňčgo na hu giya e ghino na ya mun, bobwariya ghino na hu kulavoreŇčaŇčgo e lemi Ňčgolo,  
\v 36 ya bukabuka na hu giya kwama weŇčgo, ya ghambwera na hu njimbukikiŇčgo, inaŇčgu e thiyo na hu mena hu thuweŇčgo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 37 ‚ÄúAmba ghar…®ghar…®ko thovuthovuye ne th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėAmalana, thembaŇča va wo thuweŇčge bada i ghar…®Ňčge na wo giya ghan…®Ňčga na u ghan, o mbwa i ghar…®Ňčge na wo giya mbwa e ghen?  
\v 38 Na thembaŇča va wo thuweŇčge u mebobwari na wo kulavoreŇčaŇčge, o u bukabuka na wo ligiya kwama na u njimbo?  
\v 39 Na va thembaŇča wo thuweŇčge u ghambwera o inan e thiyo na wo ghaona wo thuweŇčge?‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 40 ‚ÄúKiŇč ne i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄėYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, thembaŇča thoŇčgo hu vakatha bigi regha weya oghaghaŇčguŇčgike regha iya idae ma i lagh…®ye, Ňčgoreiya hu vakatha weŇčgo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 41 ‚ÄúAmba ne i dage weŇčgiya thiye inanji e moiyeko iŇča, ‚ÄėHu rakaiteteŇčgo, ghemi iya val…®kaiwae hu vaidiya lith…® weya Loi. Hu rakawa e nd…®gheko une iya memeghabananiyeko, iyava Loi i vivatharaweko Seitan na le nyao kaiwanji.  
\v 42 Kaiwae bada i ghar…®Ňčgo na ma hu giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgo, mbwa i ghar…®Ňčgo na ma hu giya mbwa weŇčgo,  
\v 43 bobwariya ghino na ma hu kulavoreŇčaŇčgo e lemi Ňčgolo, ya bukabuka na ma hu giya kwama weŇčgo, ya ghambwera na inaŇčgu e thiyo na ma hu mena hu njimbukikiŇčgo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 44 ‚ÄúThiye tembe th…® thombeweva th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėAmalana, va thembaŇča wo thuweŇčge bada o mbwa i ghar…®Ňčge, o u mebobwari o u bukabuka o inan e thiyo, na ma wo thalavuŇčge?‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 45 ‚ÄúNe i thombe weŇčgi na iŇča, ‚ÄėYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, thembaŇča hu botewo hu thalavugha oghaghaŇčguŇčgike iya nanasiyeke thiyake iya hu yaŇčgiwanaŇčgike regha Ňčgoreiya hu botewo hu thalavuŇčgo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 46 ‚ÄúThiyake ne veth…® vaidiya vuyowoko iya ma mbaŇča regha ne i koko na ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye ne veth…® vaidiya yawal…® moli.‚ÄĚ   
\c 26  
\s1 Th…® tamweya kamwath…® na th…® yalaweya Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:1-2; Luk 22:1-2; Jon 11:45-53)  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Jisas i utuvao utuutuko wolagh…®ye, i dage weŇčgiya gharaghambu, iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúKaero hu ghareghare, mbaŇča ma theghewo eŇčge kaero Thaga ValaŇčani ghambaŇča, na ne e mbaŇčako iyako t…®ne th…® vaŇčgugiya Lolo Nariye na th…® Ňčge e kros.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 E mbaŇčako iyako ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Jiu lenji randevivaŇčgi th…® mevathavatha ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva idae Kaiyapas ele Ňčgolo  
\v 4 na th…® vona Jisas ghae ŇčgoroŇčga ne th…®Ňča na th…® yalawe thuwele na th…® tagavamare.  
\v 5 Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThava ra vakatha e thagake iyake t…®ne, ne iwaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® gharenji i muru na th…® gaith…®.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Wevo eunda i varuvo Jisas e bunama  
\r (Mak 14:3-9; Jon 12:1-8)  
\p
\v 6 Jisas vamba i yaku Betani Saimon ele Ňčgolo, iye va i ghataŇča lepelo.  
\v 7 Wevo eunda i menawe, i th…®na bod…®la alabasita vwarara, bunama butiye thovuye na modae lagh…®ye inawe. MbaŇča Jisas vamba i ghan…®Ňčga, i liŇčgiya bunamama e umbaliye.   
\p
\v 8 Ko mbaŇča gharaghambuko th…® thuweya iyako gharenji i gaith…®. Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae i vakowana bunamako?  
\v 9 ThoŇčgo ra vakuneŇča bunamako iyako ne ra vaidiya mani lagh…®ye na ra giya weŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 Jisas i ghareghareya lenji renuwaŇčako, amba i dage weŇčgi, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu liya wevoke ghautu? Vakatha thovuye moli iya me vakathake weŇčgo.  
\v 11 MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne weimiyaŇčgiya mbinyembinyeŇčgu ko ghino mane weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.  
\v 12 Me ruvuya bunamake iyake e riwaŇčgu. Iyako Ňčgoreiye kaero me vivatha riwaŇčgu beku kaiwae.  
\v 13 Ya dage emunjoru e ghemi, nevole thembaŇča th…® vavaghareŇča Totoke Thovuye iyake e yambaneke lagh…®ye, budakaiya wevoke iyake me vakatha ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® utuŇča na th…® renuwaŇčakikiya elagh…®niye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Judas iŇča ne i vatomweya Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:10-11; Luk 22:3-6)  
\p
\v 14 Amba gharaghambuko theyaworo na theghewoko regha, idae Judas Isakariyot, i wa weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye  
\v 15 na iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu wogiya budakai weŇčgo thoŇčgo ya vatomweya Jisas weŇčga na hu yalawe?‚ÄĚ Th…® vaona silva geth…®yeto (30) na mbala th…® giya modae.  
\v 16 E mbaŇčako iyako na i voro Judas i tamwetamweya kamwath…®, ŇčgoroŇčga ne iŇča na i vatomwe weŇčgi na th…® yalawe.   
\s1 Jisas na gharaghambu th…® vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani  
\r (Mak 14:12-21; Luk 22:7-13,21-23; Jon 13:21-30)  
\p
\v 17 MbaŇča iviva moli Bred ma weiye is…®t ghathaga ghambaŇča, gharaghambu th…® menawe na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNuwaniya wo wa e the val…®vaŇčga na vo vivatharaweya Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiye kaiwan?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 18 I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa vohu ru Jerusalem e t…®ne, weya amala regha, na hu dagewe huŇča, ‚ÄėRavavaghare iŇča: WombaŇča maiyavara. WeiŇčguyaŇčgiya woraghambuke wo vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiye e len Ňčgolona.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Gharaghambuma th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya me dagema weŇčgi na th…® vivatharaweya Thaga ValaŇčani ghan…®Ňčganiyewe.   
\p
\v 20 Vama gougou amba Jisas weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambuma theyaworo na theghewoma thiya yaku na thiya ghan…®Ňčga.  
\v 21 Ghan…®Ňčga e t…®ne Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghemi, regha ina e t…®nemike ne i vatomweŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Gharenji i v…®r…® lagh…®ye na th…® dagewe, regha na regha iya i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ma ghino Ňčgoreiye, ae?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Jisas i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemina regha iya me wouta ghabred…®na weiŇčgu e gaeba regha, iye ne i vatomweŇčgo.  
\v 24 Lolo Nariye ne i mare Ňčgoreiya Buk Boboma le woraŇčgiya, ko loloko iya ne i vatomweya Lolo Nariye ne i vaidiya vuyowae. I thovuye moliwa loloko iyako thoŇčgo t…®nae ma va i ghamb…® eŇčge.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 Amba Judas, iya ne i vatomweya Jisas, iŇča, ‚ÄúRavavaghare, ma ghino Ňčgoreiye, ae?‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero mo utuŇča na len utuna emunjoru.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Giya le ghan…®Ňčga  
\r (Mak 14:22-26; Luk 22:14-20; 1Kor 11:23-25)  
\p
\v 26 MbaŇča thiya ghan…®Ňčga, Jisas i wo bred mbumbura, i vata ago weya Loi, i njiviyaviya na i giya weŇčgiya gharaghambuma, na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wo na hu ghan. Iyake riwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 Amba i th…®na kom na tembe i vata ago weva Loi, i th…®n…®giya weŇčgi, na iŇča, ‚ÄúTaulagh…®na ghemi hu mun,  
\v 28 waen…®ke iyake mad…®baŇčgu iye i vaemunjoruŇča dagerawe togha. I voruraŇčgi na mbala Loi i numotena ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo lenji thar…®.  
\v 29 Ya dage e ghemi, ma tene ya mun…®va waen…®ke iyake gheghada ne ya mun…®va waen togha weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi Bwebwe ele ghamba mbaro t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\fig Jisas i naŇčgo weya Loi na i vata agowe bred na waen kaiwanji|alt="last supper Jesus giving thanks" src="IB04149bw.tif" size="span" copy="Faadil" ref="26:26-29" \fig*   
\p
\v 30 MbaŇča th…® wothuvao wothu yaŇčgara, th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® raka Oliv…® e ghanji Ou.   
\s1 Pita iŇčava mane i roro Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:27-31; Luk 22:31-34; Jon 13:36-38)  
\p
\v 31 Amba Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGougouke noroke taulagh…®na ghemi ne hu vo iteteŇčgo, kaiwae Buk Boboma iŇča, ‚ÄėNe ya un…®gha sip ghanjiranjimbunjimbu na sip th…® rakavo.‚Äô\x - \xo 26:31 \xt Sak 13:7\x*  
\v 32 Ko amba Loi ne i vakathaŇčgo na ya thuweiru na e yawayawaliŇčgu, ne ya viva e ghamwami Galili.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 33 Pita i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúOthembe taulagh…®ke ne th…® rakavo, ghino mane ya voiteteŇčge.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 34 Jisas i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru e ghen, noroke gougou amba muyai kamkam i dage mbaŇčaiwo, mbaŇčato ne uŇča ma u ghareghareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 35 Pita i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMane yaŇča ma ya ghareghareŇčge, othembe thoŇčgo ne ya mare weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ Gharaghambuko wolagh…®ye th…® gorereya.   
\s1 Jisas ve naŇčgo Getesemani  
\r (Mak 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46)  
\p
\v 36 Jisas weiyaŇčgiya gharaghambu th…® wa e val…®vaŇčga idae Getesemani, amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHuya yaku gheke, na ya wa na va naŇčgo gheko.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 I vaŇčguŇčgiya Pita na Sebedi le ŇčgaŇčgama thenjighewoma. Ghare i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli.  
\v 38 Amba i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúGhareŇčgu i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli, mbalama i tagavamareŇčgo. Hu yaku gheke na hu njaŇčanjaŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 39 I loŇčga ghaova seiwo, i dipoumu e thelauko vwatae na i naŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe, thoŇčgo val…®kaiwae, u vakathaŇčgo na vuyowoke ghandegh…® iyake thava i mena weŇčgo. Ko iyemaeŇčge thava u vakatha ghino lo renuwaŇča, u vakatha eŇčge ghen len renuwaŇča.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 40 Amba i njogha weŇčgiya gharaghambuma thenjighetoma na i vaidiŇčgi thiya ghena. I dage weya Pita, iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ma val…®kaiwae hu njaŇčanjaŇča lughawoghawo regha?  
\v 41 Hu njaŇčanjaŇča na hu naŇčgo, mbala ma hu ru tanathetha e t…®ne. Ghare nuwaiya, ko ririwo i njavovo.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 42 Mbowo i wava mbaŇčaiwoniye na ve naŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe, thoŇčgo len renuwaŇča ya muna vuyowoke ghakom iyake na ma val…®kaiwae i iteteŇčgo, ko mbema u vakatha Ňčgoreiye iya len renuwaŇčana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 43 MbaŇča i njoghama, tembe i vaidiŇčgiva th…® ghenelaŇča, kaiwae mara ghenaghena i gaboŇčgi.  
\v 44 I iteteŇčgi na mbowo ve naŇčgova mbaŇčatoninji. I naŇčgo na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva me naŇčgoma.   
\p
\v 45 Mbowo i njogha weŇčgiva gharaghambuma na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo amba hu ghenaghena vara mbaŇčake molao? Wo hu thuwe, mbaŇča kaero iko; e mbaŇčake vara th…® vaŇčguraweya Lolo Nariye thar…® gharavakatha e n…®manji ghare.  
\v 46 Hu yondo na ra raka. Wo hu thuwe, loloma wolilivama maiyavara i menana!‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Th…® yalawe Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:43-50; Luk 22:47-53; Jon 18:3-12)  
\p
\v 47 Jisas vamba i utuutu kaero Judas, gharaghambuma theyaworo na theghewoma regha, i vutha weiyaŇčgiya wabwi lagh…®ye regha, th…® mban…®Ňčgiya gaith…® ghaghalith…® na umbwaumbwa uboubotu. Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Jiu lenji randeviva meth…® variyeŇčgi.  
\v 48 Lilivama vama i giya nono weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúThe lolo ne ya vandamo, ee amalagh…®niye; hu yalawe.‚ÄĚ  
\v 49 Judas i vamwand…® weya Jisas na iŇča, ‚ÄúAgo lagh…®ye Ravavaghare!‚ÄĚ Na i vandamo.   
\p
\v 50 Jisas i dagewe, ‚ÄúWou, budakai kaiwae mo menake u vakatha.‚ÄĚ Ghar…®ghar…®ma th…® rakamena na th…® yalawe.   
\p
\v 51 Gharaghambuma regha i mwanagita le gaith…® ghaghalith…® e ghambae na i gothethe ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva le rakakaiwo regha yanawae.  
\v 52 Jisas i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU woraweya len gaith…®na ghaghalith…® e ghambae, kaiwae thela thoŇčgo i gaith…® e ghalith…® ne th…® un…®gh…® e ghalith…®.  
\v 53 Ko ma hu ghareghare val…®kaiwaŇčgu moli ya kula weya Bwebwe thalavu kaiwae na e mbaŇčako iyako, i variyeŇčgiya le nyao thovuthovuye ghanjiwabwi lagh…®lagh…®ye kaiwaŇčgu?  
\v 54 Ko thoŇčgo ya vakatha Ňčgoreiyako mane i vaemunjoruŇča Buk Boboma le utu, iya i woraŇčgiya budakaiya kaero i yomara e mbaŇčake iyake.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 55 E mbaŇčako iyako Jisas i dage weŇčgiya wabwima iŇča, ‚ÄúMouŇča eŇčge rakaiva ghino iya mohu mban…®Ňčgiya gaith…® na ghaghalith…® na umbwaumbwa uboubotu na hu mena hu yalaweŇčgo? MbaŇča regha na regha ya yaku e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne na ya vavaghare, ma va hu yalaweŇčgo.  
\v 56 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake th…® yomara na th…® vaemunjoruŇča budakaiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu va th…® rori Buk Boboma e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ  
\p E mbaŇčako iyako gharaghambu th…® voiteteŇča.   
\s1 Jisas i utu Jiu e lenji kot lagh…®ye  
\r (Mak 14:53-65; Luk 22:54-55,63-71; Jon 18:13-14; 19:24)  
\p
\v 57 Thiyema meth…® yalawe Jisas th…® yovaŇčgu Kaiyapas ele Ňčgolo, iye ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva. Mbaro gharavavaghare na Jiu lenji randeviva vama th…® mevathavatha gheko.  
\v 58 Pita i rereghamba weya Jisas, vambe ina bwagabwaga, ghaghad th…® vutha ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva e ghayayao. Pita i ru e yayaoko t…®ne na i yaku weiyaŇčgiya ragat…®gat…®. Nuwaiya i thuwe ne th…® vakatha budakai weya Jisas.   
\p
\v 59 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye weinjiyaŇčgiya Jiu lenji rambarombaro Jiu e lenji kot lagh…®ye t…®ne, th…® tamweŇčgiya utu kwan…®kwan Jisas ghawonjowe kaiwae, mbala lenji r…®ghe na th…® un…®gha Jisas.  
\v 60 Ko iyemaeŇčge ma th…® ndevaidi mun, othembe rautu kwan…®kwan vavana th…® mena th…® utuŇčaŇčgiya lenji kwan…®Ňčgi.  
\p Muyai amba thenjighewo th…® mena,  
\v 61 na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalake iyake iŇčava val…®kaiwae ne i rakayathu Loi le Ňägolo Boboma na mbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne kaero i vatad…®va.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 62 Amba ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i yondovir…® na i dage weya Jisas iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mane u gonjogha lenji utuko ghath…®th…®? ŇägoroŇčga lenji utuko gharumwaru e ghen?‚ÄĚ  
\v 63 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas ma i ndeutu mun. Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi e yawayawaliye e idae ya naŇčgo e ghen na u dage weime, thoŇčgo emunjoru ghen Mesaiya, Loi Nariye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 64 Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye iya moŇčana. Ko ya dage e ghemi, mbaŇča i menamenako ne hu thuwe Lolo Nariye, ne i yaku Loi Vur…®gheghe e une na i njama e Ňčgal…®l…®ko e buruburu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 26:64 \xt Sam 110:1; Dan 7:13\x*   
\p
\v 65 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji randeviva i mwanathethe ghakwama ghatemuru kaiwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúI utuvathar…® Loi kaiwae. Ma te nuwandaiyava ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® utu kaiwae. Kaero mohu loŇčweya le utuko, me utuvathar…® weya Loi.  
\v 66 ŇägoroŇčga lemi renuwaŇča?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVal…®kaiwae moliya i mare!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 67 Amba th…® njoŇčgovuna ghamwae na th…® Ňčge. Vavana th…® tagaleva  
\v 68 na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMesaiya ghen? U dage weime thoŇčgo Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu ghen, thela me ŇčgeŇčgeŇčaŇčgena.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Pita iŇča ma i ghareghare Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:66-72; Luk 22:54-62; Jon 18:15-18,25-27)  
\p
\v 69 Pita vambe ina e yayaoko t…®ne amba rakakaiwo eunda i menawe na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Ňčgoreiye, vambe wein…®va Jisas rara Galili.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 70 Ghar…®ghar…®ko taulagh…® e maranji i roro iŇča, ‚ÄúMa ya ghareghare budakaiya utuniye u utuutuna.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 71 Seiwo i loŇčgaraŇčgi Ňčgoreiya yayaoko ghaghamba ru, rakakaiwo eunda i thuweya Pita i amba i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko inanjiko gheko iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalake iyake va weiye Jisas rara Nasaret.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 72 MbaŇčaiwoniye Pita i roro iŇča ma i ghareghare Jisas. I tholo iŇča, ‚ÄúMa ya ghareghare iya lolona iyana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 73 MbaŇča ma molao, ghar…®ghar…®ma thiya ndeghath…®ma gheko th…® mena weya Pita na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru Jisas ghauneko regha ghen, kaiwae ghal…®Ňčan…®na ghaŇčgumi i woraŇčgiya, ghen rara Galili.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 74 Pita i tholomundu iŇča, ‚ÄúYa dage emunjoru. Loloko iyako ma ya ghareghare. Loi i lith…® e ghino thoŇčgo ma ya utuŇča emunjoru.‚ÄĚ  
\p E mbaŇčako iyako kamkam i kula,  
\v 75 amba Pita i renuwaŇčakiki Jisas ghal…®Ňčaema: ‚ÄúAmba muyai kamkam i kula; mbaŇčato ne uŇča ma u ghareghareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ  
\p Pita i raŇčgi eto na ve randa lagh…®ye.   
\c 27  
\s1 Th…® yovaŇčguya Jisas weya Pailat  
\r (Mak 15:1; Luk 23:1-2; Jon 18:28-32)  
\p
\v 1 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča moli ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Jiu ghanjigiyagiya th…® vakatha lenji mbaro Jisas le mare kaiwae.  
\v 2 Th…® Ňčgar…® na th…® yovaŇčgu weya Pailat, Rom ghagawana.   
\s1 Judas le mare  
\r (Vak 1:18-19)  
\p
\v 3 MbaŇča Judas, Jisas ghaliliva, i loŇčwevaidiya Jisas vama th…®Ňča ne i mare, i nuwonjogha na i biginjogha mani gethiyeto weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na giyagiya vavana.  
\v 4 Judas i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúMa vakatha thar…® kaiwae ma vatomweya amala ma ele thar…® na th…® un…®gh…®.‚ÄĚ Th…® dagewe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa wo rerenuwaŇča kaiwae. Tembe ghen ghan…®mberegha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Judas i bigiyathu manima e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne na i wa na ve gadesowo.   
\p
\v 6 Amba ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® mbana manima na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúManike iyake madibe inawe na la mbaro i dageten ra bigirawe weiye Ňägolo Boboma ghamani.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Th…® vakatha manima ghambaro, th…® mban na th…® vamodo thelauwe bobwari lenji ghabubu kaiwae. Th…® vamodo weya uye gharamonjemonje.  
\v 8 Iya kaiwae thelauko iyako th…® una idae Madibe Thelauniye gheghada noroke.  
\v 9 MbaŇča va th…® vakatha iyako, Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharautu, Jeremaiya, le utu i tabo na emunjoru, iŇča, ‚ÄúTh…® mbana silva geth…®yeto (30), Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vavana va th…® vatomwe na loloko iyako ghavanjo  
\v 10 na th…® vamodo uyema gharamonjemonje le thelauwe, Ňčgoreiya Loi le utu weŇčgo.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 27:10 \xt Sak 11:12-13; Jer 19:1-13; 32:6-9\x*   
\s1 Jisas i kot weya Pailat  
\r (Mak 15:2-5; Luk 23:3-5; Jon 18:33-38)  
\p
\v 11 Jisas i ndeghath…® Pailat e ghamwae, iye Rom ghagawana, amba i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Jiu lenji kiŇča ghen?‚ÄĚ  
\p Jisas i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiya iya moŇčana.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Jiu ghanjigiyagiya meth…® wonjowe ma me ndegolambo mun.  
\v 13 Amba Pailat i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThare u loŇčwe bigibigi lemoyo kaiwanji iya th…® wonjoweŇčgenawe?‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 Ko Jisas mava i gonjogha lenji utuko mun, iya kaiwae Pailat ghare va i yo.   
\p
\v 15 Theghathagha regha na regha Thaga ValaŇčani e t…®ne, rayakuyaku e thiyo regha iya ghar…®ghar…® th…® tuthigiya weya Pailat na i vaŇčguraŇčgiya kaiwanji.  
\v 16 E mbaŇčako iyako amala regha va ina e thiyo, idae Barabas, amalagh…®niye ghathanavu raithar…® moli.  
\v 17 MbaŇča wabwi lagh…®ye th…® mevathavatha amba Pailat i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThela nuwamiya ya rakayathu kaiwami? Barabas o Jisas iya th…®Ňčake Mesaiya?‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 I dage Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae va i ghareghare wagiyawe Jiu lenji randeviva th…® yamwakabu Jisas kaiwae iyava th…® vaŇčgugiyakowe.   
\p
\v 19 Pailat vamba ina e ghamba kot kaero levo i variya toto iŇča: ‚ÄúLolona iyana ma ele thar…®. Ne u ndevakatha bigi reghawe kaiwae me gougou ma ghenelola gheneloloniye na i vakathaŇčgo ya mararu lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Jiu ghanjigiyagiya th…® vokomukomuŇčgi wabwiko lagh…®ye na th…® naŇčgo weya Pailat i rakayathu Barabas na iŇča na th…® un…®gha Jisas.   
\p
\v 21 Pailat i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúIya thenjighewoke, thela nuwamiya ya rakayathu kaiwami?‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBarabas.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Mbowo i vaitoŇčgiva iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha budakai weya Jisas iya th…®Ňčake Mesaiya?‚ÄĚ  
\p Taulagh…®ko th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU rokros!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Pailat i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKo loloke iyake va i vakatha vara thambo thar…®?‚ÄĚ  
\p Ma th…® kula na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye eŇčge th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU rokros!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Pailat vama i ghareghare ma te val…®kaiwaeva i vakatha renuwaŇča regha na wabwiko lagh…®ye mbalavama th…® vakatha gaith…®, amba i th…®na mbwa na i thavwiya n…®mae wabwiko lagh…®ye e maranji na iŇča, ‚ÄúLoloke iyake le mare wonjoweniye thava ne i mena weŇčgo. Tembe hu kwalavi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 Taulagh…®ko th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLe marena wonjoweniye i mena weime na lama ŇčgaŇčga weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 Amba Pailat i rakayathu Barabas kaiwanji na iŇča na ragagaith…® th…® liya thiyo weiye bigibigi vur…®gheghe nanji e thiyoko na th…® yab…®b…®we amba i vaŇčgugiya weŇčgi na th…® Ňčge e kros.   
\s1 Ragagaith…® th…® vatabweruŇča Jisas  
\r (Mak 14:65; 15:16-20; Luk 22:63-65; Jon 19:2-3)  
\p
\v 27 Pailat le ragagaith…® th…® yovaŇčguya Jisas e gawana ele Ňčgolo ghayayao amba ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® mevathavatha na th…® megh…®liŇča Jisas.  
\v 28 Th…® bigiraŇčgiya ghakwama na th…® vanjimbo e kwama sosoro na molao, Ňčgoreiya kiŇč ghakwama.  
\v 29 Th…® vona umbwa ele kinkin yaŇčgae na th…® th…®n…®rawe e umbaliye na th…® wo umbwa na th…® worawe e n…®maeko e uneko, Ňčgoreiya kiŇč ghavakavakatha amba th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye na th…® vatabweruŇča th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúO Jiu lenji KiŇč, len mbaro ne i meghabana!‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 Th…® njoŇčgovun…®vun na th…® wo umbwama na th…® ŇčgeŇčgeŇča umbaliye.  
\v 31 MbaŇča th…® vatabweruŇčako na e ghereiye, th…® liraŇčgiya kwamama sosoroma na th…® vanjimbo amalagh…®niye e ghakwamaŇčgima. Amba th…® vaŇčguraŇčgiya na th…® yovaŇčgu veth…® rokros.   
\s1 Th…® Ňčge Jisas e kros vwatae  
\r (Mak 15:21-32; Luk 23:26-43; Jon 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 32 MbaŇča vama veth…® vaŇčguraŇčgiya na ma veth…® loŇčgaloŇčga amba th…® lavolevola lolo regha, rara Sairin idae Saimon. Ragagaith…®ma th…® vavur…®ghegheŇča na i wo Jisas ghakros.  
\v 33 Th…® vutha e val…®vaŇčga regha idae Golgota. Golgota gharumwaru Ňčgoreiya ‚ÄúBoutouto Ghambae‚ÄĚ.  
\v 34 Bigi regha iye i maŇčge th…® liŇčgirawe weiye waen th…® th…®n…®giya weya Jisas na i mun. MbaŇča i gham…®no na i maŇčge, i botewoyathu.  
\v 35 MbaŇča th…® Ňčge e kros…®ko vwatae, amba th…® wobwiya ghakwamakwamama. Th…® mbana var…®var…® na th…® mwadiwo mwadiwo reghawe. Thela thoŇčgo i wo var…®ko iya e ghanonoko amba i tuthi iyaŇčganiya i bigi.\x - \xo 27:35 \xt Sam 22:18\x*  
\v 36 Amba thiya yaku gheko na th…® njimbukiki.  
\v 37 Th…® liya ghawonjoweko, vama th…® rori, na th…® Ňčge e umbaliye na yavoro, iŇča, \sc Iyake Jisas, Jiu lenji KiŇč\sc*.  
\v 38 Th…® rokrosiŇčgiya rakaiv…® thenjighewo weiyaŇčgi, regha e une na regha e moiye.\fig Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye, mbaro gharavavaghareŇčgi na Jiu ghanjigiyagiya th…® goviyeviye ghamwae|alt="Jesus on cross and the two others" src="IB04166bw.tif" size="span" copy="Faadil" ref="27:32-44" \fig*   
\p
\v 39 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® rakarakareŇča evasiwae th…® wovanukunukuya umbalinji na th…® goviyaviya ghamwae,  
\v 40 th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVa uŇča ne u tagarakaraka Ňägolo Boboma na mbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne kaero u vatad…®va. ThoŇčgo Loi Nariya ghen, tembe u vamora ghan…®mberegha. U roiteta kros…®na na u njama.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 41 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye, mbaro gharavavaghareŇčgi na Jiu ghanjigiyagiya vambe th…® goviyaviyava ghamwae Ňčgoreiyake.  
\v 42 Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúI vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® mbe vavana, ko ma val…®kaiwae i vamoru ghamberegha! Iye Israel lenji KiŇč, ae? Tembe ghamberegha i njama e kros…®ko, ambane wo loŇčweghath…®.  
\v 43 I vareminja Loi. Wo ra thuweno, thare Loi ne i thalavu, kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄėLoi Nariya Ghino!‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 44 Rakaiv…®Ňčgiko iyava th…® rokrosiŇčgiko weiyaŇčgi, thiye vambe th…® yaŇčgiwanava Ňčgora iyako.   
\s1 Jisas i mare  
\r (Mak 15:33-41; Luk 23:44-49; Jon 19:28-30)  
\p
\v 45 Ghararagh…®ye mboro ghaghad t…®ri klok, vanautumako lagh…®ye i mouwo.  
\v 46 T…®ri klok ele val…®vaŇčga Jisas i kula na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúEloi, Eloi, lama sabak…®tani?‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 27:46 \xt Sam 22:1\x* gharumwaru ‚ÄúLo Loi, Lo Loi, buda kaiwae u iteteŇčaŇčgo?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 47 Ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava thiya ndeghath…®ko gheko th…® loŇčweya iyako na vavana th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúI kula weya Ilaija iyako.‚ÄĚ  
\v 48 E mbaŇčako iyako, regha i ruku na i liya vune i liutu e waen monyomonyo na i lira e umbwa mbothiye, amba i livoreŇča na Jisas i mun.  
\v 49 Ko iyemaeŇčge vavana th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo ra roroghagha! Wo ra thuweno, mbwata ne Ilaija i mena na i vamoru.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 50 Jisas mbowo i kulava na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye amba i vatomweya yawaliye na i mare.   
\p
\v 51 Amba kwama va i ganatena woluwolu bobomako moli e Ňägolo Boboma t…®ne, i mathethe wa yavoro na ve wo bode, thelauko i mbarimbariri na var…®var…® th…® raraviyaviya.  
\v 52 Ghabughabubu th…® mavu na Loi le ghar…®ghar…® vama thiya marekai th…® rakathuweiru na e yawayawalinji.  
\v 53 Th…® rakaiteteŇčgiya ghabughabubu na Jisas le thuweiru mare e ghereiye, veth…® rakaru Jerusalem na veth…® rakaraŇčgi weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo.\fig Kwama i mathethe wa yavoro na ve wo bode|alt="Temple curtain torn" src="lb00265c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="27:51" \fig*   
\p
\v 54 MbaŇča ragagaith…®ko na lenji randeviva, va inanji gheko th…® njimbukikiya Jisas, th…® gham…®nogha ghembako i ragheghe na th…® thuweŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye iyava th…® yomarako, th…® mararu lagh…®ye na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru iye Loi Nariye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 55 Wanakau i ghanagha vambe inanjiva gheko. Vambe th…® ndeghath…® bwagabwaga na th…® ghewoŇča Jisas. Thiye va th…® ghambugha Jisas Galili na th…® njimbukiki.  
\v 56 E t…®nenji Meri t…®nan Magadala, Meri Jemes na Josep t…®nanji na Sebedi le ŇčgaŇčga t…®nanji.   
\s1 Th…® beku Jisas  
\r (Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Jon 19:38-42)  
\p
\v 57 MbaŇča vama yegh…®yegh…®ye amba amala ragogomwau regha i vutha, idae Josep. Amalake iyake i mena Ar…®mathiya na iye vambe Jisas gharaghambuva.  
\v 58 I wa weya Pailat na ve naŇčgo Jisas riwaekowe. Amba Pailat iŇča na th…® wogiyawe.  
\v 59 Josep i wo na i liya kwama togha i ghavowe,  
\v 60 amba i worawe ele ghabubu togha t…®ne, vamba i t…®gh…®ruwoeŇčge e var…® e bobokulu regha. I vabulaleya var…® lagh…®ye regha na i rogana ghaekowe, amba i iteteŇča.  
\v 61 Meri t…®nan Magadala na le ghaida Meri eundava inanji gheko, th…® yaku na ghamwanji i ghemba ghabubuko.   
\s1 Ragagaith…® th…® njimbukikiya ghabubuko  
\p
\v 62 MbaŇčambaŇča Satade, Jiu lenji Sabat, ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye na Parisi lenji wabwi th…® rakawa Pailat.  
\v 63 Th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, wo renuwaŇčakikiya rakwan…®ko iyako, mbaŇča vamba e laghalagha va iŇča, ‚ÄėMbaŇča thegheto e ghereiye kaero ya thuweiruva.‚Äô  
\v 64 U dage na ragagaith…® veth…® njimbukikiya ghabubuko ghaghad mbaŇča thegheto, mbala gharaghambuŇčgiko ma val…®kaiwanji th…® wa na veth…® wokava riwaeko, na th…® dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėKaero me thuweiruva e mare.‚Äô Kwan…®ke iyake ne i lagh…®ye kivwala kwan…®ma i vivama.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 65 Pailat i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye, hu vaŇčguŇčgiya lo ragagaith…®na vavana na vou vaŇčguraweŇčgi na th…® njimbukiki wagiyaweya ghabubuko.‚ÄĚ  
\v 66 Th…® wa na veth…® liya thiyo yaŇčgara na th…® Ňčgar…®ghath…®gha var…®ko weiye ghabubuko ghadidiye na lenji nono ambama th…® vaŇčguraweŇčgiya ragagaith…® na th…® njimbukiki.   
\c 28  
\s1 Jisas i thuweiru e mare na e yawayawaliye  
\r (Mak 16:1-8; Luk 24:1-12; Jon 20:1-10)  
\p
\v 1 Jiu lenji Sabat kaero iko na Sande mbaŇčambaŇča moli, Meri t…®nan Magadala na le ghaida Meri reghava th…® wa veth…® kela e ghabubuko.   
\p
\v 2 Ragheragheghe lagh…®ye regha i yomara, na Loi le nyao thovuye regha i mena e buruburu, i vabulaleyathu var…®ma na i yaku e vwatae.  
\v 3 Ghamwae va i ndalandala Ňčgora i vilamema na ghakwama i kakaleva Ňčgora ghinama ree.  
\v 4 Ghabubuko gharagat…®gat…® th…® mararu lagh…®ye na th…® tage th…® dobu e thelauko vwatae, ma e laghalaghanji Ňčgoranjiya th…® marema.\fig Loi le nyao thovuye regha i vabulaleyathu var…®ko|alt="angel moves the stone" src="IB04171bw.tif" size="span" copy="Faadil" ref="28:1-4" \fig*   
\p
\v 5 Ko nyaoma thovuye i dage weŇčgiya wanakauma iŇča, ‚ÄúTha hu mararu! Ya ghareghare hu tamweya Jisas, iya mendava th…® rokros.  
\v 6 Ma ina gheke, kaero me thuweiru, Ňčgoreiya va le dagerawema. Wo hu mena hu thuwe menda th…® worawemawe.  
\v 7 Hu rukunjogha na vou dage weŇčgiya gharaghambuma, vouŇča, ‚ÄėJisas kaero me thuweiru e mare na i viva weŇčga Galili. Ne vou vaidi gheko‚Äô. Hu renuwaŇčakikiya ŇčgoroŇčga maŇčama e ghemi!‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Wanakauma th…® yoruku na th…® iteta ghabubuma weinji lenji mararu, ko iyemaeŇčge warari lagh…®ye i riyevanjaraŇčgi. Th…® ruku na veth…® utugiya weŇčgiya gharaghambuma.  
\v 9 E kamwath…® mborowa Jisas i vwara weŇčgiya wanakauma na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúAgo lagh…®ye weŇčga.‚ÄĚ Th…® menawe, th…® ronja e ghenji vuvuye, th…® v…®ghath…®gha gheghe na th…® kururuwe.  
\v 10 Jisas i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTha hu mararu. Hu wa na vou dage weŇčgiya oghaghaŇčguna na th…® raka Galili, tene veth…® thuweŇčgo gheko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 11 Wanakauma vama inanji e kamwath…® mborowa, amba ragagaith…®ma iyava th…® njimbukikiya ghabubukoma, vavana th…® njogha Jerusalem na veth…® utugiya weŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye bigibigiko wolagh…®ye iya meth…® yomarako.  
\v 12 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® niva weinjiyaŇčgiya Jiu lenji randeviva na th…® vakatha lenji mbaro regha na th…® giya mani lagh…®ye weŇčgiya ragagaith…®.  
\v 13 Na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHu dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® huŇča, ‚ÄėMo ghenelaŇča gougou na gharaghambu th…® mena th…® wokaiva Jisas riwae.‚Äô  
\v 14 ThoŇčgo Pailat i loŇčweya totoke iyake, ghime tene wo varumwara nuwae na ghemi mane hu vaidiya vuyowae.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Ragagaith…®ma th…® mbana manima na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya meth…® dagema weŇčgi. Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® ndeth…®na utuke iya th…®Ňčake, Jisas, gharaghambu th…® wokava riwae, ghaghada noroke.   
\s1 Jisas i vwara weŇčgiya gharaghambu  
\r (Mak 16:9-11,12-13,14-18; Luk 24:13-49; Jon 20:11-23; Vak 1:6-8)  
\p
\v 16 Jisas gharaghambu theyaworo na regha veth…® voro e ou regha Galili Ňčgoreiya Jisas va i dagema weŇčgi na th…® wawe.  
\v 17 MbaŇča th…® thuwe th…® kururuwe, vavana th…® numoghegheiwo.  
\v 18 Jisas i mena na i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe vama i woveŇčgo vur…®gheghe na ya mbaroŇčaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye e buruburu na e yambaneke.  
\v 19 Iyake kaiwae hu wa weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e vanautumake wolagh…®ye na hu vakathaŇčgi na woraghambuŇčgi, hu bap…®taisoŇčgi Ramanda e idae, Nariye na Nyao Boboma e idae.  
\v 20 U vavaghareŇčgi na th…® ghambugha bigibigike wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya va ya dagema weŇčga. Na hu renuwaŇčakiki iyake, ghino weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye gheghada yambaneke le ghambako.‚ÄĚ   